research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0153.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r150-r152 的 matched architecture probes 已经依次表明去掉 second stage、去掉 soft-codebook、退回 topk 都会明显恶化 FVU，因此当前问题不再是 family 本身值不值得继续，而是回到主线后重新建立一个干净的运行时与曲线锚点：在保持主线参考配方 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / K=128 / EF=2 / signum / LR=3.0e-3 不变的前提下，确认其 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens 是否仍稳定可复现，从而为后续单变量 recipe 决策提供可信基线。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 复现 0.0581 左右的终点且吞吐恢复到正常区间，则下一轮再进入单变量学习率或优化器判断。","若 clean baseline 仍出现明显慢速但终点稳定，则把近期问题归因为运行时吞吐波动而非架构退化，后续 recipe 评估必须继续把总耗时与 tokens_per_sec 作为硬约束。","若 clean baseline 自身终点或曲线形状发生漂移，则先停止扩展 recipe 搜索，优先确认主线锚点后再做下一步单变量扰动。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 已满足选择成本预算，K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与主线复验混杂。","r150-r152 的架构探针已经说明主线 family 相对近邻与简单 baseline 都有真实结构收益，本轮按规则回到主线。","评估本轮时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，区分是训练更长还是吞吐更慢导致耗时上升。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"本轮不新开 family，回到主线参考配方做 clean baseline 复验，符合当前主线推进顺序。虽然这一步不直接追求更低 FVU，但在近期多轮 probe 与明显运行时波动后，先恢复可信锚点比继续做难归因的 recipe 扰动更稳妥。","summary":"回到主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，固定 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3，不引入任何新结构或 recipe 变化，先做一轮干净 baseline 复验，确认当前主线的真实训练曲线与运行代价。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/history_20260320_152535/logs/agent_action_0003.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"At fixed K=128, a Hadamard-rotated gated SAE will beat rotated topk on proxy FVU by decoupling support selection from coefficient magnitude, giving the encoder a more expressive and fully differentiable routing mechanism than the failed rotated JumpReLU prototype.","summary":"Run a proxy prototype for a rotated gated SAE at K=128. This is a quality-first architecture exploration step that keeps the improved Hadamard preprocessing from the current anchor while testing whether independent gate and magnitude branches can materially improve reconstruction before any effort is spent on smaller K or cost reduction.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"rotated_gated","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This respects the fixed execution layer, uses only supported env overrides, and makes one coherent bet: stronger encoder expressivity at the same K=128 quality anchor. Gated is a better next family than group_topk because its selector is differentiable, whereas the current group_topk implementation explicitly notes ineffective router training. The main risk is that sigmoid gating may need optimizer retuning or longer warmup, so a weak proxy result would not fully rule the family out.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Read research/program.md before deciding; it reinforces a quality-first proxy default and encourages architecture exploration when local parameter search is not closing the gap.","The current sparsify code already supports gated SAE through env overrides, so this family can be tested without touching the execution layer.","GroupTopK is currently implemented with hard non-differentiable routing, so gated is the cleaner next routing-style family to test for quality."],"next_hypotheses":["If rotated gated shows promising proxy FVU but unstable optimization, keep the family alive with an optimizer-focused stabilization pass such as Adam or LR retuning.","If rotated gated improves quality but remains far from the aggressive target, sweep its regularization or related training settings before considering smaller K.","If rotated gated fails to show useful quality signal, escalate to a more novel encoder family or code-level architecture change rather than returning to weak local topk tuning."]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0160.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终重构仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.62x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，并且显著低于当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x。r159 已经用 matched probe 说明去掉第二阶段 refinement 会从 0.0581 退化到约 0.0647，因此本轮只回答另一个互补的问题：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主要 recipe 完全不变时，进一步去掉 soft-codebook coarse branch、退回到 lowrank_residual，是否仍值得继续，还是 soft-codebook 分支本身就是当前低 EF 可部署 regime 的必要结构增量。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_residual 明显落后于当前主线，则说明 soft-codebook coarse branch 在当前低 EF regime 下仍然是必要结构，不应继续回退。","若 lowrank_residual 与当前主线接近且成本明显更低，则记录其为更激进低成本备选，但下一轮仍按要求回到主线。","若 lowrank_residual 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 的 coarse branch 价值需要重新审视，但本轮仅做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_residual 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为扩展兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","r159 已检验 two-stage 相对单阶段 soft-codebook 的结构价值；本轮补充检验 soft-codebook coarse branch 本身是否值得保留。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把架构质量与吞吐波动混淆。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 lowrank_residual 而不是更远的 topk 或 factorized_topk，是因为它是当前主线去掉 soft-codebook 分支后的最近父节点，能最干净地隔离“soft-codebook coarse branch 本身是否值得”这个单一问题，同时提供显著更低 selection_cost 的直接对照。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为 lowrank_residual，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断 soft-codebook coarse branch 在当前低成本 regime 下是否仍然值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0131.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态向量库，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮只回答一个问题：在 clean baseline 已稳定复现且 signum 连续多轮无改进后，改用 adam 并将 LR 联动下调到 1.0e-3，是否能带来更平滑的训练曲线和更低的最终 FVU，同时不显著恶化 tokens_per_sec 与总耗时。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 adam@1.0e-3 曲线更稳且终点更好，可继续在同 family/EF=2/K=128 上细调 LR（如 7.0e-4 或 1.3e-3）。","若 adam@1.0e-3 终点接近但明显更慢，应把它视为负面信号并回到 signum 主线。","若 adam@1.0e-3 明显欠收敛或发散，则结束 optimizer 分支，下一轮再考虑 loss/preprocess 而非继续扫 optimizer。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容；本轮不是结构改动，只是 optimizer 轴探索。","EF=2 继续保证 selection_cost 在预算内；K 保持 128，不把部署查表成本变化与 optimizer 效应混杂。","r130 clean baseline 已复现当前 feasible frontier，因此可把后续变化更可靠地归因到 optimizer/LR 联动。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"遵守主线推进与单变量原则：family、EF、K 均固定，只切换 optimizer，并按历史规则联动重调 LR 以避免无效比较。风险是 adam 可能带来更慢吞吐或更长收敛时间，因此必须同时检查曲线形状、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens。","summary":"在已稳定复现的 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线上测试一次 optimizer 变化：固定 EF=2、K=128，仅把优化器从 signum 切到 adam，并把 LR 配套下调到 1.0e-3，判断是否存在比当前 feasible baseline 更好的收敛形状与 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/02_20260320_175419/memory.json:2:  "current_focus": "Treat K=128 only as the initial search anchor, not as a success criterion. The research objective is to find configurations whose FVU is dramatically better than the current K=128 baseline, with a target on the order of halving that baseline FVU before rewarding smaller K or lower cost.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0217.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"240"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214-r216 已经连续证明在 EF=1 下沿 K 轴增加查表预算能稳定压低 <0.5x 区域的 FVU，而 r216 仍从 0.1635 改善到 0.1528，说明边际收益尚未耗尽；因此本轮继续在同一最短链路 family 上仅把 K 提到 240，目标是在总成本仍预计约 0.49x、继续留在 <0.5x 区域的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 再向下压一截，并判断 topk@EF1 的收益是否开始真正接近平台。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K240 继续明显改善 FVU 且运行代价未恶化，则低开销区仍可再补一个贴边点。","如果 K240 的收益很小或训练时间明显变差，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 已接近边际收益极限，后续应转向新的低成本 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 目前是 <0.5x 区域最稳的直接兼容主线，且导出路径最简单，适合继续补低开销 Pareto 前沿。","r214-r216 已形成清晰趋势：在 EF=1 固定 encoder 成本下，增加 K 可以持续降低 FVU，因此当前最高信息量的单变量仍是 K 轴。","评估时必须同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认贴近 0.5x 边界后的额外查表预算是否仍值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮选择 K=240 而不是直接上到 256，是为了尽量稳妥地继续留在 <0.5x 区域，同时测试靠近边界时的真实边际收益。风险是收益可能已开始明显变小，但这正是当前需要量化的关键信号。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 240，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1528 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0136.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"NUM_CODES","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"pareto_cost_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，已满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮只改一个主变量 NUM_CODES，把 codebook 容量下调到 32，回答一个问题：在保持主线 family 与 recipe 不变的前提下，是否能以更低的 code_router/codebook_matmul 选择成本和更低的 codebook_deploy 成本，维持接近当前 0.0581 的 FVU，从而形成更强的 LUTurbo 成本侧 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 NUM_CODES=32 仅带来小幅 FVU 退化但明显降低 deploy/selection 成本，则继续细扫更小或中间的 NUM_CODES 以压 Pareto 前沿。","若 NUM_CODES=32 的 FVU 明显恶化，则说明当前 codebook 容量已接近必要下限，回到默认配置后优先改测 STAGE1_RATIO。","若 NUM_CODES=32 与 baseline 几乎等价且吞吐更好，则可把更小 codebook 视为新的 clean baseline，再继续主线 recipe 搜索。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容。","r135 的 matched probe 说明去掉 soft codebook/coarse branch 会明显变差，因此主线继续保留两阶段 soft-codebook 结构。","本轮转向 NUM_CODES，是因为它同时影响 encoder 选择成本与部署 codebook 成本，比继续做无收益 recipe 更贴近 LUTurbo 真实目标。"],"primary_variable":"num_codes","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 均固定，只改 NUM_CODES。该动作直接针对 LUTurbo 总成本中的 codebook 分支，且不触碰已证明重要的 family 主结构；风险是 codebook 容量过小会削弱 coarse branch 表达，因此必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens。","summary":"回到主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，在 EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变的前提下，仅把 NUM_CODES 下调到 32，测试是否能用更小 codebook 获得更优的 cost-FVU 权衡。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0165.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on lowrank_soft_codebook_residual with K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3 unchanged. Final reconstruction formula is x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i, where U(Vx) is a static low-rank trunk library, {c_m} is a static soft-codebook library, and {b_i} is a static residual dictionary. This is 扩展兼容: LUTurbo can export it as trunk lookup + codebook lookup + one residual sparse lookup, all over fixed vector libraries. The single question for this probe is whether removing the second residual refinement stage keeps enough reconstruction quality to justify the lower encoder selection cost and likely lower runtime in the low-EF regime.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If FVU regresses materially versus the mainline while runtime savings are small, return to lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual next round and stop probing nearby parents.","If runtime improves meaningfully at only modest FVU loss, keep lowrank_soft_codebook_residual as a cost-efficient compatible branch on the Pareto frontier, but still return to the mainline next round per probe policy."],"notes_to_memory":["Compatibility: 扩展兼容. Export path is static trunk library + static codebook library + static residual dictionary; no dynamic decoder weights.","This is a matched architecture probe that changes only ARCHITECTURE and stays safely within the known EF=2 selection-cost budget table.","Probe intent is architectural value judgment only: test whether the second sparse stage in the current mainline is worth its extra encoder cost/runtime under LUTurbo constraints."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This probe is conservative because the family is already known and compatible, so upside is mostly in runtime-cost tradeoff rather than discovering a new best FVU. That makes it appropriate after the previous matched probe was policy-rejected: it isolates a single structural difference and should yield a clean comparable signal.","summary":"Run a single matched architecture probe with ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_soft_codebook_residual while keeping K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, and LR=3.0e-3 fixed. The probe tests whether the simpler one-stage soft-codebook parent is still worth continuing as a lower-cost LUTurbo-compatible branch relative to the current two-stage mainline.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0016.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 15 established `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=64` as a valid new Pareto point, so the next most informative single-variable question is whether LUTurbo can push cost lower again without collapsing reconstruction. This round changes only `K`, moving from `64` to `32` while keeping the same family and recipe fixed, to measure the next step on the cost-quality frontier.","summary":"Continue the topk low-K tradeoff lane: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `K` from `64` to `32` to test whether a materially cheaper decomposition still yields an acceptable reconstruction curve.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active topk family, changes exactly one primary variable, and follows directly from the new `K=64` keep result. The main risk is a sharp FVU jump at `K=32`, but mapping that boundary is now more valuable than more K128 recipe polishing because LUTurbo's objective is total online cost, not only anchor quality.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"32"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 15 added a credible `K=64` Pareto point on the accepted topk/signum/LR1.6e-3/EF12 backbone.","Round 16 continues the same low-K mapping by changing only `K` from 64 to 32.","Judge this run on frontier usefulness, not raw comparison to K128 alone: the key question is whether `K=32` remains deployably compatible with a tolerable quality drop for the lower online selection and summation cost."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=32` is still competitive enough, continue the same lane to `K=24` or `K=16` depending on curve shape and degradation size.","If `K=32` degrades sharply, `K=64` may be the practical low-K sweet spot for the current topk recipe.","If `K=32` is borderline but usable, compare it against `K=64` as a cost-quality tradeoff rather than against the K128 anchor alone."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/history_20260320_152535/results.tsv:5:proxy_1773953215	1773953215	proxy	ok	incubate	0.4501677379012108	128	gated	8			5013504	/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0003_proxy/round0003_proxy_1773953155_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef8_k128_20260320_044601	6903b3665fae3916d21a8931869cd86f13404b16	autoresearch-sae	True	Run a proxy prototype for a rotated gated SAE at K=128. This is a quality-first architecture exploration step that keeps the improved Hadamard preprocessing from the current anchor while testing whether independent gate and magnitude branches can materially improve reconstruction before any effort is spent on smaller K or cost reduction.	This respects the fixed execution layer, uses only supported env overrides, and makes one coherent bet: stronger encoder expressivity at the same K=128 quality anchor. Gated is a better next family than group_topk because its selector is differentiable, whereas the current group_topk implementation explicitly notes ineffective router training. The main risk is that sigmoid gating may need optimizer retuning or longer warmup, so a weak proxy result would not fully rule the family out.	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/proxy_1773953215.log
research/history_archive/history_20260320_152535/results.tsv:10:proxy_1773954098	1773954098	proxy	ok	discard	0.2930360250174999	128	residual_topk	8			5013504	/root/sparsify-ascend/checkpoints/research_agent/round_0007_proxy/round0007_proxy_1773954033_dp2_bs1_ga8_ef8_k128_20260320_050044	6903b3665fae3916d21a8931869cd86f13404b16	autoresearch-sae	True	Stabilize the promoted residual_topk family with a narrow architecture edit: remove the fixed per-branch K split so both the base and residual branches can each propose up to K candidates before the final global top-K selection. Run this as a proxy quality-first comparison at K=128 with the existing Hadamard+signum setup to test whether the family had been artificially capacity-limited.	This stays within one coherent hypothesis and follows the program guidance to keep pushing a promising family before chasing smaller K or cost. I kept the execution layer unchanged, edited only sparsify/, and avoided mixing in optimizer or regularization sweeps so the result isolates the branch-allocation change. The main risk is extra duplicate candidates across branches with no quality gain, but the local forward/backward sanity check passed and runtime cost should remain close enough for a proxy read.	/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/proxy_1773954098.log
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0228.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"240"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: jumprelu。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；JumpReLU 只改变单样本在线侧的阈值化支持形成与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 r227 只改一个 env 参数 `K=240`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05`、`JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.02`、`signum`、`LR=0.003` 不变，测试在已经于 0.49x 成本点优于 topk 的前提下，轻微缩短查表链路后是否仍能保持对同成本邻近 topk 点的质量优势，从而补出 `<0.5x` 区域更低 deployment 成本一侧的 Pareto 前沿。该改动只降低部署查表成本，不增加 encoder 成本，total_cost 预计将从约 0.49x 小幅降到约 0.48x，仍稳居当前主战区且满足 LUTurbo 总成本硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@K240` 仍明显优于当前同区间 `topk@K240` 的 FVU=0.14833，且训练总时长不恶化，则继续相对本轮单变量下探到 `K=224`，补齐更低部署成本侧的 jumprelu 前沿形状。","如果 `K=240` 的 FVU 与 r227 基本持平或只小幅变差，但 wall-clock 更短，则可将 jumprelu 视为当前 `<0.5x` 区域同时更强且更便宜的默认直兼容主线，并减少对同一点 recipe 的继续清洗。","如果 `K=240` 的 FVU 退化过快，说明当前 jumprelu 改善主要依赖极高 K 支持预算；则关闭该 family 的 K 下探线，转向新的低成本 family 或回到更高质量锚点解释。"],"notes_to_memory":["r225-r227 已连续证明 jumprelu 在同成本高 K 单库 regime 下优于 topk，其中 r227 的 FVU=0.14564 已低于当前 topk@K248 的 0.14621。","当前最高信息量问题已不再是继续在 `K=248` 单点上做 recipe 微调，而是判断这条直接兼容单库路线能否沿 K 轴向更低部署成本扩展，真正补出 `<0.5x` Pareto 前沿。","评估本轮必须同时看 FVU、tokens_per_sec、duration_sec、final_total_tokens；如果只是极小质量变化但运行明显更慢，则不能视为正面信号。"],"reference_round":227,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r227 只改 `K`，不联动 architecture、EF、LR、bandwidth、init_threshold 或其他 recipe。选择沿 jumprelu 的 K 轴补前沿，而不是继续上探阈值，是因为 r227 已经把同成本质量点做到了优于 topk；当前更有价值的是确认它是否能在更低 deployment 成本邻域也保持优势，从而真正扩展 `<0.5x` frontier，而不是继续在同一点做密集局部优化。主要风险是质量对高 K 依赖过强，但这正是本轮要隔离回答的单一问题。","summary":"相对 r227 的 `jumprelu@EF1,K248,JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05,JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.02` 做一次严格 param_only frontier probe，仅将 `K` 下调到 `240`。目标是在略降总成本的同时，验证 jumprelu 能否继续压过当前 `topk@0.48x` 邻近点，从而补出 `<0.5x` 区域更低部署成本侧的 Pareto 前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/history_20260320_152535/memory.json:2:  "current_focus": "Treat K=128 only as the initial search anchor, not as a success criterion. The research objective is to find configurations whose FVU is dramatically better than the current K=128 baseline, with a target on the order of halving that baseline FVU before rewarding smaller K or lower cost.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0249.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"192"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；低秩 factorized scorer 只改变单样本在线侧的打分与选择链路，不改变 decoder 端的单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿导出形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r246 只改一个 env 参数 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`K=96`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003` 及其余配置不变，测试在仍显著低于 plain topk 的总成本下，适度增大低秩 scorer 容量是否能把 `factorized_topk@K96` 的 FVU 从 0.3987 明显压低，从而在约 0.25x 总成本附近补出一枚比 `topk@K32` 更有竞争力的低开销 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `factorized_topk@K96,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 明显优于 r246 的 0.3987，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则下一轮继续相对本轮单变量上探到 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`，判断这条低秩 scorer 线的质量-成本拐点。","如果质量只小幅改善但运行明显更慢，则把更宽 scorer 记为负面系统信号，不再继续沿 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 上探。","如果即使 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192` 仍显著差于 `topk@K32` 的 FVU=0.3199，则关闭 factorized scorer 作为 `<0.3x` 主前沿候选，把注意力转回其他低开销 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["r246-r248 已经基本测清 `factorized_topk@FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 K 轴：成本可以极低，但 FVU 始终停在 0.40+，说明当前瓶颈更像 scorer 容量而不是查表预算。","r244 说明默认更宽 hidden_dim 在 `K=96` 下能把 FVU 压到 0.3008，但成本槽位也上移；当前更高信息量的问题是适中的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 能否在低于 topk 左端成本的前提下拿回大部分质量。","本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是质量略好但训练显著更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":246,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r246 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，不联动 architecture、K、EF、optimizer 或 LR。选择回到 `K=96` 并提升 scorer 容量，而不是继续沿 `K` 轴左移，是因为 r246-r248 已经显示低 hidden-dim factorized 线的主要问题是质量而非成本；当前最小、最可归因、也最符合低开销探索目标的动作，是测试适度增宽的 factorized scorer 是否能形成更有价值的 cost-FVU 权衡。","summary":"严格锚定 r246，仅把 `factorized_topk` 的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 从 96 提到 192，优先验证这条低秩 scorer 线能否在约 0.25x 总成本处显著提升质量，而不是继续扩展已经基本测清的超左端低 K 边界。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0115.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_baseline","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。Round 114 在成本可行的 EF=2 regime 下把 signum 学习率从 2.4e-3 提到 3.0e-3 后，将 frontier 从 FVU 0.05914 改进到 0.05811，且总时长从前两次 EF=2 运行的 445s/307s 降到 290s，没有出现明显运行代价恶化。本轮只回答一个问题：这个更优的低成本主线点是否可复现，因此应在完全相同的 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3` 配方上补一次 clean baseline。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LR=3.0e-3` 复现出接近 `FVU≈0.0581` 的终点且曲线继续健康下降，则将其定为 EF=2 主线 signum 锚点，再考虑是否继续做单变量 LR 微调。","如果复现明显回退到接近 `0.0591` 或曲线形状变差，则把 `LR=3.0e-3` 视为不稳定候选，回退到 `LR=2.4e-3` 作为稳态锚点。","在这个复现问题解决前，不切换 optimizer，不改 K，也不改任何额外成本轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","EF=2 已满足选择成本硬约束，当前 frontier 可行点为 cost≈1.25x、FVU≈0.05811。","本轮严格遵守单变量原则；虽然 env_overrides 不变，但主问题是 `clean_baseline` 复现，而不是继续同时改变 LR 或其他轴。重点继续检查曲线形状、`tokens_per_sec`、总耗时和 `final_total_tokens`。"],"primary_variable":"clean_baseline","self_review":"这符合当前主线顺序。EF 已确认可行，clean baseline 已对 `LR=2.4e-3` 做过，Round 114 又给出了更优的 `LR=3.0e-3` 候选，因此现在最小且可归因的动作是复现该新候选，而不是继续上探学习率或过早切换优化器。没有引入第二个变量，结论最干净。","summary":"复现当前更优的低成本主线配方 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / EF=2 / K=128 / signum / LR=3.0e-3`，确认它是否是稳定的新 frontier 点，而不是一次性波动。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0214.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。当前 <0.5x 区域只有 topk@K64,EF1 这一个点，且它已经明显优于同成本附近的 factorized_topk；因此本轮不再继续纠缠 lowrank_factorized_residual 的 param_only policy 细节，而是直接回到最稳的低开销单库 family，在 EF=1 保持 encoder 成本约 0.25x 的前提下，把 K 提到 128，测试是否能在总成本仍约 0.37x、明显低于 0.5x 的条件下，把 FVU 从 0.2583 显著压低，补出第二个真正有价值的 <0.5x Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K128 在 <0.5x 内显著优于 K64 且吞吐下降可接受，则再回到同 family 只沿 K 轴补一个中间点。","如果 K128 的 FVU 改善有限但训练耗时或吞吐明显变差，则说明 EF=1 下继续加查表预算的边际收益不足，后续应转向新的低成本 family 而不是继续堆 K。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 的导出形式最干净：单静态字典上的有限加权和，直接兼容 LUTurbo，且是当前唯一已进入 <0.5x frontier 的 family。","r207/r208 已表明在低成本区 topk 明显强于 factorized_topk，但目前缺少同 family 在 <0.5x 区域内更高 K 的质量曲线点；本轮优先补这条最短链路前沿。","评估时必须同时比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，判断 K 增长带来的收益是否值得额外查表和训练时间。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮把主变量明确设为 architecture，并沿用历史已通过的 architecture action 形状：由 family_name 指定 family，不在 env_overrides 中重复写 ARCHITECTURE。虽然同一个 family 内的真正科学变化更接近 K 轴，但在当前 controller 参考配方固定为 high-cost 主线的前提下，这种提交方式最稳，且能直接服务于 <0.5x 区域补点目标。","summary":"切回直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，只把低开销单库路线的支持规模拉到 K=128，目标是在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的条件下，补出一个明显优于当前 0.31x 点的新 <0.5x Pareto 候选。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0147.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_signal","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r145 表明把 signum 学习率从主线参考值 3.0e-3 小幅上调到 3.3e-3 后，FVU 从 0.058106 降到 0.057939，且总耗时未恶化；r146 的 policy_reject 说明不能把这一步包装成 clean baseline，本轮必须继续作为单变量 LR 问题处理。本轮只回答一个问题：相对于当前主线参考配方的 LR=3.0e-3，把 LR 改为 3.3e-3 的收益是否可重复成立，并且不会以更差的 tokens_per_sec、总耗时或 final_total_tokens 为代价。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 LR=3.3e-3 再次优于 3.0e-3，且运行代价基本不变，则可把 3.3e-3 视为新的 signum 主线锚点，后续再决定是否继续微调或转入 optimizer/成本轴。","若 LR=3.3e-3 回落到 3.0e-3 基线附近，则说明 r145 更可能是噪声收益，后续应关闭上探并保守回到 3.0e-3。","若 LR=3.3e-3 只带来极小收益但显著拖慢训练，则将其视为负面 recipe 信号，不再继续围绕更高 LR 上探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r145 首次在 EF=2/K=128/signum 主线上得到 0.057939，因此当前最有价值的问题是确认这个 LR 信号是否可复现。","r146 的 policy_reject 表明必须把 3.3e-3 继续视为 LR 轴单变量问题，而不是以 clean baseline 名义提交。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 与导出形式全部固定，不混入成本轴、loss 轴或新的结构变化。这样既符合当前推荐顺序，也避开了 r146 暴露出的 clean-baseline 包装问题。风险是再次运行 3.3e-3 可能只复现到接近 3.0e-3 的结果，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕当前主线 family 推进，不开新 family；将 r145 的 3.3e-3 结果当作单变量 LR 信号而非新 baseline，保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 不变，再运行一次 LR=3.3e-3，确认该小幅上调是否能稳定优于参考配方的 3.0e-3。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0221.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: lowrank_factorized_residual\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r u_r + \u03a3_i \u03b1_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u3001{b_i} \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u8ba1\u7b97 \u03b2_r \u4e0e \u03b1_i\uff0c\u518d\u6267\u884c trunk \u67e5\u8868 + residual \u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002r220 \u7684 blocker \u4e0d\u662f\u8d28\u91cf\uff0c\u800c\u662f TRUNK_RANK override \u6ca1\u6709\u771f\u6b63\u8fdb\u5165\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u7f6e\uff1b\u5f53\u524d\u6267\u884c\u94fe\u5df2\u5177\u5907 `TRUNK_RANK -> --trunk_rank -> sae.trunk_rank` \u8def\u5f84\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u672c\u8f6e\u5e94\u4e25\u683c\u951a\u5b9a\u6709\u6548\u53c2\u8003\u8f6e r210\uff0c\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a env \u53c2\u6570 `TRUNK_RANK=32`\uff0c\u5148\u9a8c\u8bc1 `research/history/logs/round*.config.json` \u4e0e checkpoint `config.json` \u90fd\u8bb0\u5f55 `sae.trunk_rank=32`\uff0c\u518d\u5224\u65ad\u8be5 family \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u4ee5\u9884\u4f30 total_cost\u22480.36x \u4fdd\u6301\u663e\u8457\u4f18\u4e8e <0.5x \u533a\u57df topk \u524d\u6cbf\u7684 FVU\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u4fdd\u4f4f\u5176\u66f4\u9ad8\u541e\u5410/\u66f4\u77ed\u603b\u65f6\u957f\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0221.json:20:    "summary": "\u590d\u8dd1 r220 \u7684\u79d1\u5b66\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u4f46\u6309\u5408\u6cd5 `param_only` \u5f62\u5f0f\u4e25\u683c\u951a\u5b9a\u6709\u6548\u53c2\u8003\u8f6e r210\uff0c\u4ec5\u4e0b\u53d1 `TRUNK_RANK=32`\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u5148\u505a\u53c2\u6570\u751f\u6548\u786e\u8ba4\uff0c\u518d\u8bc4\u4f30 lowrank_factorized_residual \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u4ee5\u7ea6 0.36x total_cost \u8fdb\u5165 <0.5x Pareto \u4e3b\u524d\u6cbf\u3002",
