research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/memory.json:2047:      "hypothesis": "On the directly compatible `topk` line, increasing `K` from 96 to 160 should produce a materially better `<0.5x` Pareto point, likely around the low-0.18 FVU range at about 0.41x total_cost, while avoiding the recent `factorized_topk` pattern of modest quality gains paired with worse throughput.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/memory.json:2090:    "NOTE: r246 \u5df2\u786e\u8ba4 `factorized_topk@K96,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` \u80fd\u4ee5\u7ea6 0.14x total_cost \u8865\u51fa\u65b0\u7684\u6700\u5de6 Pareto \u70b9\uff1b\u8fd9\u8bf4\u660e\u4f4e hidden-dim factorized scorer \u7ebf\u867d\u8d28\u91cf\u5f31\uff0c\u4f46\u5728\u6210\u672c\u7ef4\u5ea6\u4e0a\u786e\u5b9e\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u65b0\u589e\u4fe1\u606f\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/memory.json:2102:    "NOTE: Recent `factorized_topk` rounds remained far above the best low-cost topk points, and the wider scorer pass at r249 also reduced throughput to about 111k tok/s, so further factorized widening is currently a weak cost-quality bet.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/memory.json:2123:    "If `topk` K=160 underperforms the monotone trend, shift the next round to a different directly compatible low-cost selector family instead of continuing dense K sweeps.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/memory.json:2124:    "If runtime regresses disproportionately at K=160, treat that as a system-side warning and prefer lower-cost frontier densification over larger-K topk pushes."
research/history_archive/history_20260320_152535/round_summaries/round_0007.json:50:    "self_review": "This stays within one coherent hypothesis and follows the program guidance to keep pushing a promising family before chasing smaller K or cost. I kept the execution layer unchanged, edited only sparsify/, and avoided mixing in optimizer or regularization sweeps so the result isolates the branch-allocation change. The main risk is extra duplicate candidates across branches with no quality gain, but the local forward/backward sanity check passed and runtime cost should remain close enough for a proxy read.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0145.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r144 已重新确认当前主线参考配方可稳定复现 0.0581 附近 FVU 且运行代价恢复正常，因此现在应按顺序回到单变量学习率轴，而不是继续做架构探针或过早切换 optimizer。本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family、EF、K、optimizer 全不变的前提下，将 signum 的 LR 从 3.0e-3 小幅上调到 3.3e-3，是否能在不明显恶化 tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens 的情况下，改善中后段收敛形状并把 FVU 压到 0.0581 以下。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 LR=3.3e-3 在曲线中后段与终点上优于 3.0e-3，且运行代价基本不变，则继续围绕 signum 做小步上探或复验。","若 LR=3.3e-3 与 baseline 基本等价或更差，则说明 3.0e-3 已接近当前 signum 最优点，后续应关闭 LR 轴并转向 optimizer 或成本轴。","若 LR=3.3e-3 只带来极小 FVU 变化但明显拖慢训练或拉长总时长，则将其视为负面 recipe 信号，不再继续上探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r144 clean baseline 已重新确认主线参考配方稳定，因此后续 recipe 变化可以更可靠地归因到单变量本身。","学习率轴此前表明 2.4e-3 偏低、3.6e-3 未带来收益；3.3e-3 是对 3.0e-3 的最小上探，用于判断是否仍有轻微的 signum 步长余量。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 与导出形式全部固定，不混入成本轴或 loss 轴变化。该动作符合当前推荐顺序，在 EF 成本可行且 clean baseline 已补齐后，先完成更细的 LR 局部搜索。风险是 3.3e-3 可能只会带来更激进但无收益的更新，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕当前主线 family 推进，不开新 family；在 r144 已恢复 clean baseline 锚点后，本轮进入单变量 LR 微调，保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 不变，只把 LR 从 3.0e-3 小幅上调到 3.3e-3，测试是否能改善中后段收敛并刷新当前可行 frontier。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0205.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: factorized_topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d b_i \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1bfactorized scorer \u4ec5\u7528\u4e8e\u5728\u7ebf\u6253\u5206\u4e0e\u9009\u5740\uff0c\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\u4ecd\u662f\u5355\u5e93\u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e r204 \u5df2\u5728 K=64\u3001EF=2 \u4e0b\u62ff\u5230 0.44x / 0.3013 \u7684 <0.5x \u70b9\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u7ee7\u7eed\u4fdd\u6301 architecture\u3001EF\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u4ec5\u5c06 K \u4ece 64 \u4e0b\u63a2\u5230 32\uff0c\u9884\u8ba1 deployment cost \u53ef\u7531\u7ea6 0.06x \u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u964d\u5230\u7ea6 0.03x\uff0c\u4f7f total_cost \u7ea6\u843d\u5728 0.41x\uff0c\u8865\u5168\u66f4\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u7aef\u8986\u76d6\uff0c\u5e76\u68c0\u9a8c\u8be5 family \u5728\u66f4\u77ed\u67e5\u8868\u94fe\u8def\u4e0b\u7684 FVU \u9000\u5316\u659c\u7387\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0205.json:20:    "summary": "\u5728\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 family factorized_topk \u4e0a\u505a\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u4e0b\u63a2\uff1a\u56fa\u5b9a EF=2\u3001signum\u3001LR=3e-3\uff0c\u4ec5\u628a K \u4ece 64 \u964d\u5230 32\uff0c\u76ee\u6807\u662f\u628a total_cost \u4ece 0.44x \u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.41x\uff0c\u5e76\u8865\u5168 <0.5x Pareto \u524d\u6cbf\u7684\u66f4\u4f4e\u90e8\u7f72\u6210\u672c\u7aef\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0205.json:55:      "\u5982\u679c K=32 \u4ecd\u4fdd\u6301\u53ef\u63a5\u53d7 FVU\uff0c\u53ef\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 factorized_topk \u4e0a\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u4e0b\u63a2 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM\uff0c\u4e89\u53d6\u628a encoder cost \u4e5f\u5f80\u4e0b\u538b\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0205.json:76:    "description": "\u5728\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 family factorized_topk \u4e0a\u505a\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u4e0b\u63a2\uff1a\u56fa\u5b9a EF=2\u3001signum\u3001LR=3e-3\uff0c\u4ec5\u628a K \u4ece 64 \u964d\u5230 32\uff0c\u76ee\u6807\u662f\u628a total_cost \u4ece 0.44x \u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.41x\uff0c\u5e76\u8865\u5168 <0.5x Pareto \u524d\u6cbf\u7684\u66f4\u4f4e\u90e8\u7f72\u6210\u672c\u7aef\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0143.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 architecture 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，alpha_i 为选出的稀疏系数，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。与当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 相比，factorized_topk 不再使用 trunk、soft codebook 或两阶段 refinement，而是用低秩 scorer 做单库稀疏选择，仍保持静态库有限加权和的部署形式；在 EF=2 下其 encoder selection_cost 约 0.38x h×n，显著低于当前主线的约 1.25x，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，部署侧也只需单库 sparse lookup。本轮只回答一个 matched architecture probe 问题：在 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全不变时，这种更激进的低秩单库选择机制是否值得继续，还是它在当前低 EF regime 下会因表示能力不足而明显落后于现有 soft-codebook/two-stage 主线。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 factorized_topk 在大幅降低 selection_cost 的同时仅有有限 FVU 损失，则保留它作为低成本 LUTurbo 候选，但下一轮按策略回到主线 family。","若 factorized_topk 的 FVU 明显落后于 lowrank_residual 与 soft-codebook 系，则说明低秩单库 scorer 在当前 regime 下不值得继续，后续不再占用主线 probe 轮次。","若 factorized_topk 虽然更便宜但训练吞吐或总耗时没有优势，则将其视为负面系统信号，而不是仅凭低 selection_cost 继续推进。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 Round 143 唯一允许的 matched architecture probe，严格保持 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变，只改 architecture。","r141 与 r142 已表明去掉 second stage、再去掉 soft codebook 都会出现阶梯式质量退化，因此本轮改测一条更低成本但机制不同的直接兼容候选，判断非全字典低秩 scorer 是否值得保留。","评估时必须同时比较 FVU、selection_cost、deploy cost、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免只按终点 SAE 指标判断架构价值。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"遵守单变量原则与本轮 probe 约束：只改 architecture，未联动 K、EF、optimizer、LR 或其他 recipe。选择 factorized_topk，是因为它在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 明显低于当前所有兼容 frontier 点，且属于直接兼容的单库静态表示，能直接回答“更激进的低秩单库选择机制是否值得继续”这一独立架构问题。风险是该 family 在旧的高 EF regime 曾明显偏弱，但当前低 EF 成本约束已发生 regime shift，这正是本轮 probe 的信息价值所在。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：把当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成更低成本、直接兼容的 factorized_topk，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一次干净对照判断低秩单库选择机制在当前 LUTurbo 成本约束下是否仍值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0052.json:78:      "Round 52 returns from K mapping to recipe refinement and isolates the LR question specifically at `K=4`, where LUTurbo online cost is minimal and training dynamics are most likely to expose over-aggressive step size."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0087.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"With `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual`, `lowrank_residual_vq`, and `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` all failing to challenge the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the highest-value remaining matched architecture probe is `lowrank_gated_residual`. It keeps the same low-rank trunk and static-library export contract, but replaces the two-stage residual path with a single gated residual selector that is materially simpler for LUTurbo online execution. If this simpler low-rank gated family is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then the current evidence favors keeping the two-stage residual structure rather than continuing single-stage low-rank selector variants.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` to `lowrank_gated_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_gated_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This follows the matched architecture probe rule by changing only `architecture` and keeping the mainline `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe fixed. `lowrank_gated_residual` is a cleaner LUTurbo-aligned probe than another multi-stage or codebook-heavy family because it preserves static exportability while potentially lowering online selection and compensation complexity. The risk is that earlier low-K history for this family was weak, so this round may mainly confirm that simpler single-stage low-rank gating cannot retain the mainline quality at K128.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_gated_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 87 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_gated_residual` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Judge this run strictly as a family-worthiness test for a simpler low-rank single-stage gated selector with potentially lower LUTurbo online cost; return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_gated_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, discard it and resume mainline tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round.","If `lowrank_gated_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a viable lower-complexity branch but still return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round per probe policy."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0018.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 17 showed that `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=24` still descended smoothly through the late phase rather than flattening early, so the current recipe appears capacity-limited but still stable. This round changes only `K`, moving from `24` to `16`, to answer whether LUTurbo can reach the next allowed lower-cost point before reconstruction degradation becomes clearly impractical.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0018.json:20:    "summary": "Continue the active topk low-K frontier mapping: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `K` from `24` to `16` to test whether the deployable cost-quality frontier extends one more step down.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0018.json:53:      "For LUTurbo, this is still the most direct way to probe lower online selection and weighted-sum cost while staying within the same export-compatible topk recipe."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0018.json:78:    "description": "Continue the active topk low-K frontier mapping: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `K` from `24` to `16` to test whether the deployable cost-quality frontier extends one more step down.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0229.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"224"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: jumprelu。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；JumpReLU 只改变单样本在线侧的阈值化支持形成与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 r228 只改一个 env 参数 `K=224`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05`、`JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.02`、`signum`、`LR=0.003` 不变，测试在 r228 已经于更低部署成本点压过同区间 topk 的前提下，继续缩短查表链路后是否仍能保持明显质量优势，从而把 jumprelu 前沿从约 0.48x 进一步扩展到约 0.47x。该改动只降低 deployment 查表成本，不增加 encoder 成本，预计 total_cost 约从 0.48x 降到 0.47x，仍满足 LUTurbo 总成本硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@K224` 仍明显优于当前同区间 `topk@K224` 的 FVU=0.15281，且训练时长未恶化，则继续相对本轮单变量下探到 `K=192`，补齐更低部署成本侧的 Pareto 形状。","如果 `K=224` 的 FVU 仅小幅变差但仍优于 topk，且运行代价接近或优于 r228，则可将 jumprelu 视为 `<0.5x` 区域沿 K 轴可稳定外推的直兼容主线。","如果 `K=224` 的 FVU 退化到接近或差于同区间 topk，则停止 jumprelu 的 K 下探线，转向新的低成本 family，而不是继续消耗在这条高 K 依赖支线上。"],"notes_to_memory":["r228 已证明 `jumprelu@K240` 在更低部署成本点仍优于同区间 topk：FVU=0.14756 对比 `topk@K240` 的 0.14833，同时 duration=391s，没有出现比近期 jumprelu 轮更差的系统代价。","当前最高信息量问题是 jumprelu 的质量优势能否继续沿 K 轴向更低 deployment 成本扩展，而不是继续在 `K=240` 单点上做 recipe 微调。","评估本轮时必须同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、duration_sec、final_total_tokens；若质量收益极小但训练明显更慢，应视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":228,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r228 只改 `K`，不联动 architecture、EF、LR、bandwidth、init_threshold 或其他 recipe。选择继续下探到 `K=224`，是因为 r228 已经满足开放假设的前半条件：在更低 deployment 成本处仍压过同区间 topk，且总时长没有恶化；此时继续沿同一成本轴补点，比再次切到高不确定性新 family 更能直接服务于 `<0.5x` Pareto 前沿补全。主要风险是 jumprelu 的改进对极高 K 过于敏感，但这正是本轮要隔离回答的单一问题。","summary":"相对 r228 的 `jumprelu@EF1,K240,JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH=0.05,JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD=0.02` 做一次严格 param_only frontier probe，仅将 `K` 下调到 `224`。目标是在进一步降低总成本的同时，验证 jumprelu 能否继续压过当前 `topk@0.47x` 邻近点，从而把 `<0.5x` 区域更低 deployment 成本侧的 Pareto 前沿补完整。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0220.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是 trunk 静态向量库、{b_i} 是 residual 静态向量库；factorized residual scorer 只影响在线选择与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端导出形态，因此可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已证明该 family 在 K=64、EF=1 下能以 0.69x 拿到 0.1256 FVU，当前主矛盾是 trunk 成本过高而不是训练质量不足；本轮严格锚定 r210，只改一个主轴 TRUNK_RANK，从 auto≈256 下调到 32，测试是否能把 total_cost 明确压入 <0.5x 区域，同时尽量保留明显优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 仍明显优于 <0.5x 区域 topk 前沿，则继续相对本轮单变量下探 TRUNK_RANK=16，检查成本-质量拐点。","如果 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留 r210 作为质量锚点，转向同 family 的单变量 K 轴或回到 topk 前沿继续补点。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_factorized_residual 的导出形式稳定为 trunk 静态库 + residual 静态库的有限加权和，满足 LUTurbo 扩展兼容约束。","r210 的质量信号很强且训练吞吐约 166.6k tokens/s、总耗时 291s，说明该 family 值得优先做成本压缩而不是直接放弃。","在 EF=1、K=64 下，TRUNK_RANK 是同时影响 encoder 与 deployment 的最高杠杆单变量；先压 trunk 比继续加 K 更符合当前 <0.5x 目标区。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","reference_round":210,"self_review":"该提案满足单变量原则：相对 r210 只改 TRUNK_RANK，其余核心配方保持不变。选择 32 而不是 16，是因为它仍应明显低于 0.5x，同时比更激进的 trunk 压缩更有机会保住 r210 展现出的质量优势；主要风险是 trunk 过窄后 coarse 补偿能力不足，FVU 可能回落到接近 topk。","summary":"相对 r210 的 lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1 做一次严格 param_only 成本压缩，只下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，优先验证能否把该高质量 family 推入 total_cost < 0.5x 区域。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0173.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_grouped_soft_codebook_residual` with `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` fixed. Final reconstruction formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library, `{c_m}` is a static soft-codebook library, and `{b_i}` is a static residual dictionary; grouping changes only how the residual support is selected, not the exported decoder basis. This is `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export it as one static trunk lookup plus one static codebook lookup plus one sparse weighted sum over a static residual library, so inference remains a finite weighted sum over fixed vector banks. At EF=2 its encoder selection cost should remain within the `\u2264 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n` hard budget because it reuses the same feasible lowrank soft-codebook scorer stack and only constrains support selection. The single question is whether the soft-codebook branch remains worthwhile with cheaper group-local residual competition, or whether full global residual selection is still necessary.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0173.json:53:      "Evaluate `tokens_per_sec`, total duration, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU, because LUTurbo cares about total runtime cost rather than FVU alone; a tiny quality change with slower runtime is negative."
research/history_archive/history_20260320_152535/round_summaries/round_0003.json:7:    "summary": "Run a proxy prototype for a rotated gated SAE at K=128. This is a quality-first architecture exploration step that keeps the improved Hadamard preprocessing from the current anchor while testing whether independent gate and magnitude branches can materially improve reconstruction before any effort is spent on smaller K or cost reduction.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0045.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 44 cleanly reproduced the Hadamard-enabled `gated` improvement at `K=128`, so that preprocess gain is now stable enough to treat as the operative recipe rather than a one-off. The next single question is therefore K transfer under the improved recipe: if we keep `gated`, `signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EF=12`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1` fixed and step down only to `K=96`, does the stronger recipe preserve or extend `gated`'s advantage at the next lower support where online cost is meaningfully lower?","summary":"Adopt the reproduced Hadamard recipe as the current `gated` reference and begin K mapping under that stronger setting. Keep `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1` fixed, and change only `K` from `128` to `96`. Judge the run by the whole trajectory as well as the endpoint: if the improved recipe yields a smooth curve and clearly beats the old `gated@96` control (`0.168960`), then the preprocess gain transfers to a lower-cost point and the family deserves at least one more K step; if it falls back toward the earlier K96 result or loses its curve advantage, keep the improved recipe mainly as a K128 anchor.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active `gated` family, respects the fixed `EF=12` rule, and changes exactly one core variable: `k`. The clean Hadamard confirmation in Round 44 closes the recipe-clarification loop, so moving to K is now the most policy-clean next action. The main risk is that the K128 improvement may not transfer downward, but that is precisely the high-value deployment question this round answers.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"K","value":"96"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"1"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Rounds 43 and 44 jointly established that `USE_HADAMARD=1` is a reproducible improvement for `gated@128` under `signum, LR=2.0e-3`, so this recipe is now stable enough to use for K mapping.","Round 45 transfers the improved `gated` recipe to `K=96` to test whether the K128 preprocess gain also buys a better lower-cost point rather than only improving the largest-support anchor."],"next_hypotheses":["If the improved `gated@96` run beats the old K96 control with a similarly healthy curve, continue down to `K=64` under the same recipe.","If `gated@96` fails to improve materially under the stronger recipe, treat the Hadamard gain as mostly a K128 effect and avoid a long downward K sweep without new evidence."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0133.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"pareto_cost_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的固定向量库，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 时已满足 selection_cost ≤ 1.5×h×n，本轮不再继续无收益的 LR/loss 试探，而只改一个部署相关主变量：将 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 32，测试是否能在进一步降低 encoder selection_cost 与 trunk/codebook deploy 成本的同时，把 FVU 保持在接近当前 0.0581 的水平，从而形成新的 cost-FVU Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 TRUNK_RANK=32 能明显降成本且 FVU 仅小幅退化，可继续细扫更低或中间 rank 以压出新的 Pareto 前沿。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 的 FVU 明显恶化，则说明当前 trunk 容量已接近下限，后续应回到默认 rank 并改测 NUM_CODES。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 与 baseline 几乎等价且吞吐更好，则可将更低 rank 视为新的 clean baseline，再继续 recipe 搜索。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变，family 仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 继续保证选择成本在硬约束内；本轮通过降低 TRUNK_RANK 探索更低成本 Pareto，而不是追求单点最优 FVU。","r132 表明 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 与 baseline 基本等价，因此暂时结束 loss 轴试探，转向更有系统价值的成本轴。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 均固定，只改 TRUNK_RANK。该动作直接服务于 LUTurbo 的真实目标，因为它同时触碰 encoder 选择成本与部署 trunk 成本；风险是 trunk 容量下降可能导致 coarse branch 表达不足，因此必须结合 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和最终 token 数一起判断是否值得保留。","summary":"在低成本可行主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 上做一次成本轴探索：固定 EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3，仅把 TRUNK_RANK 下调到 32，判断能否以更低 selection/deploy 成本维持接近当前 frontier 的重构质量。","touched_files":[]}
