research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0247.json:35:      "r246 \u5df2\u786e\u8ba4 `factorized_topk@K96,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` \u80fd\u4ee5\u7ea6 0.14x total_cost \u8865\u51fa\u65b0\u7684\u6700\u5de6 Pareto \u70b9\uff1b\u8fd9\u8bf4\u660e\u4f4e hidden-dim factorized scorer \u7ebf\u867d\u8d28\u91cf\u5f31\uff0c\u4f46\u5728\u6210\u672c\u7ef4\u5ea6\u4e0a\u786e\u5b9e\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u65b0\u589e\u4fe1\u606f\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0162.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，alpha_i 是单样本 top-k 选出的稀疏系数，因此最终表示是单静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.5x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，并显著低于当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x。本轮严格保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主要 recipe 不变，只将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 改为 topk，回答唯一问题：在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下，这条最朴素、最低复杂度的单库稀疏路线是否仍值得继续，还是其表示能力会明显落后于带 trunk、soft-codebook 和 staged refinement 的主线结构。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 topk 明显落后于当前主线，则说明最简单单库稀疏路线在当前 regime 下不值得继续，下一轮回到主线。","若 topk 与当前主线差距小于预期且运行代价更优，则记录其为更简单的低成本备选，但下一轮仍按要求回到主线。","若 topk 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 的系统级收益需要重新审视，但本轮仅做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为直接兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","r159-r161 已依次检验去掉 second stage、去掉 soft-codebook coarse branch、以及更低成本 factorized 单库路线的价值；本轮补充最朴素直接兼容单库 baseline，完成当前低 EF regime 下的主干结构对照。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把质量差异与吞吐波动混淆。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 topk 是因为它是当前尚未在这一严格 matched 配方下补齐的最简单直接兼容基线，能用一次最低复杂度对照回答“主线结构是否真的必要”这个剩余问题。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为 topk，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断这种最简单的直接兼容单库架构是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0159.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 probe family \u7684\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\u3002\u5176\u4e2d U(Vx) \u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{c_m} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 soft-codebook \u5e93\uff0c{b_i} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u6700\u7ec8\u4ecd\u662f\u591a\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 0.75x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u6bd4\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual \u7684\u7ea6 1.25x \u66f4\u4f4e\u3002\u5f53\u524d round 159 \u53ea\u5141\u8bb8\u4e00\u4e2a matched architecture probe\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4fdd\u6301 K=128\u3001EXPANSION_FACTOR=2\u3001OPTIMIZER=signum\u3001LR=3.0e-3 \u4ee5\u53ca\u4e3b\u8981 recipe \u5b8c\u5168\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u4ec5\u5c06 architecture \u4ece lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual \u6362\u6210\u5176\u6700\u90bb\u8fd1\u7684\u5355\u9636\u6bb5\u7236\u8282\u70b9 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual\uff0c\u56de\u7b54\u552f\u4e00\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e EF \u53ef\u90e8\u7f72 regime \u4e0b\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9636\u6bb5 residual refinement \u662f\u5426\u4ecd\u7136\u503c\u5f97\u4fdd\u7559\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u5355\u9636\u6bb5 soft-codebook \u7248\u672c\u5df2\u7ecf\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u66f4\u4f18\u7684\u7cfb\u7edf\u7ea7 cost-FVU \u6743\u8861\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0159.json:25:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u9075\u5b88\u67b6\u6784\u63a2\u9488\u89c4\u5219\uff0c\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf architecture\uff0c\u5e76\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684 K\u3001EF\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\u3002\u9009\u62e9 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u66f4\u8fdc\u7684 topk \u6216 factorized_topk\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684\u6700\u8fd1\u7236\u8282\u70b9\uff0c\u80fd\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u5730\u9694\u79bb\u201c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9636\u6bb5 residual refinement \u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u201d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u8fd8\u80fd\u7ed9\u51fa\u66f4\u4f4e selection_cost \u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u7167\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0159.json:80:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u9075\u5b88\u67b6\u6784\u63a2\u9488\u89c4\u5219\uff0c\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf architecture\uff0c\u5e76\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684 K\u3001EF\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\u3002\u9009\u62e9 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u66f4\u8fdc\u7684 topk \u6216 factorized_topk\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684\u6700\u8fd1\u7236\u8282\u70b9\uff0c\u80fd\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u5730\u9694\u79bb\u201c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9636\u6bb5 residual refinement \u672c\u8eab\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u201d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u8fd8\u80fd\u7ed9\u51fa\u66f4\u4f4e selection_cost \u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u7167\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0177.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction remains `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j`; routing only perturbs stage-1/stage-2 support selection scores, while all decoded terms still come from static trunk, codebook, and residual libraries. This is `扩展兼容` because LUTurbo/Lottable can export the low-rank trunk matrices, soft codebook vectors, and residual dictionary once, then execute `trunk lookup + codebook lookup + routed support selection + weighted sparse lookups + sum` online. The key question is whether router-driven support allocation is worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime. Current cost accounting strongly suggests no: adding two full routers likely pushes encoder selection cost above the `1.5x h×n` hard cap, so the most informative outcome is a quick policy gate that rules this family out as a mainline candidate at `EF=2`.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If this routed matched probe is policy-rejected as expected, mark routed two-stage soft-codebook as not worth continuing in the current low-cost regime unless a future single-variable cost-reduction round explicitly targets router cost."],"notes_to_memory":["`routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: routing changes selector logic only; decode path is still a finite weighted sum over static trunk/codebook/residual libraries.","At matched `K=128, EF=2`, routed two-stage soft-codebook is expected to exceed the encoder-cost cap because the two router projections add substantial full-dictionary selection cost on top of the mainline scorer.","Treat a fast policy rejection here as a useful architectural conclusion, not a runtime failure: the family is exportable but not cost-viable in the current feasible regime."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes, while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` remain fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe is intentionally chosen to answer a clean architectural question under the new budget regime: whether routing is inherently worth carrying forward once low-EF cost feasibility is enforced.","summary":"Probe `routed_lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) by the same static-library decomposition as the mainline, but is likely to be ruled out quickly because the extra routers make encoder selection cost exceed the hard budget, which would mean this family is not worth continuing on the current Pareto frontier.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0202.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"matched_probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，soft codebook 项 Σ_m pi_m c_m 可导出为静态 codebook 库上的加权和，residual 项 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路。兼容性判断为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 是否已经足够接近当前 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线，从而说明第二个 residual refinement stage 在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下边际价值不足，不值得继续承担额外 encoder 选择成本与潜在训练时延。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 在 FVU 上接近当前主线且 tokens_per_sec 更高或总耗时更低，则记录为更优低成本/低时延备选，但下一轮仍按策略回到 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线。","若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 明显落后于当前主线，则说明第二阶段 residual refinement 在 EF=2 下仍有明确结构价值，后续应继续围绕主线做成本轴微调而不是退回单阶段。","若该 probe 运行明显更慢但 FVU 改善不足，则把单阶段 soft-codebook 也视为负面信号，不继续展开该 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 的 LUTurbo 导出形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + codebook 静态库 + residual 静态字典的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","该 family 在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 明显低于当前 two-stage 主线，因此它是检验第二阶段 refinement 是否值得的最直接低成本对照。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更高训练代价误判为架构优势。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这次严格沿用历史已通过的 architecture action 形状：architecture 只由 family_name 指定，不在 env_overrides 中重复声明，从而避免前两轮的 policy_reject。科学问题也保持单一明确，只测试 two-stage 主线中的第二 residual stage 是否在 EF=2 的兼容成本区间内值得保留。","summary":"执行一个合法的 matched architecture probe：family_name 切到 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该 family 的最终重构仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态查表链路，兼容性为扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即当前主线中的第二个 residual refinement stage 是否真的值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0203.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"matched_probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j，其中仅将两阶段 residual refinement 的预算分配改为前重后轻，近似 stage1_k≈0.75K、stage2_k≈0.25K。low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，soft codebook 项 Σ_m pi_m c_m 可导出为静态 codebook 库上的加权和，两阶段 residual 项仍可导出为静态 residual 字典上的有限稀疏加权和，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路。兼容性判断为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，固定前置更多 stage1 预算是否能比对称 two-stage 更好地利用有限 K，从而判断 asymmetric two-stage 这条 family 在低 EF 可部署 regime 下是否值得继续。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若该 asymmetric probe 明显劣于对称主线或运行更慢，则关闭该 family，下一轮按策略回到 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线。","若该 probe 的 FVU 接近或优于主线且吞吐不差，则记录 asymmetric budget split 为值得保留的结构变体，但下一轮仍回到主线。","若运行代价上升而收益很小，则把固定前置 stage budget 视为负面信号，不继续在该 family 上展开 STAGE1_RATIO 搜索。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的导出路径与当前主线同类，仍是 trunk 静态库 + codebook 静态库 + 两阶段 residual 静态字典的有限加权和，属扩展兼容。","该 family 在 EF=2 下与当前 two-stage 主线处于同一选择成本量级并满足 1.5x encoder selection-cost 硬约束，因此适合作为最后一个高价值 matched architecture probe。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更慢训练误判成结构收益。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这次沿用 r202 已验证通过的 architecture action 形状：architecture 只由 family_name 指定，不在 env_overrides 中重复声明。相比继续重复已得到有效结果的 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 或 lowrank_residual，这个 asymmetric two-stage 变体是当前最有信息价值且尚未获得有效 matched 运行的可行 family。","summary":"执行一个合法的 matched architecture probe：family_name 切到 lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该 family 的最终重构仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的静态查表链路，兼容性为扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即固定前置更多 stage1 稀疏预算的 asymmetric two-stage 结构在当前低 EF regime 下是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0017.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 16 showed that `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=32` did not collapse and still maintained a smooth late-stage FVU descent, so the next single question is whether LUTurbo can push cost one more notch lower before quality degradation becomes too steep. This round changes only `K`, moving from `32` to `24` while keeping the same family and recipe fixed, to measure the next deployable point on the low-K cost-quality frontier.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0017.json:53:      "For LUTurbo, this lane is valuable because it directly probes lower online selection and weighted-sum cost under a fixed export-compatible topk recipe."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0169.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` with `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` fixed. Final reconstruction formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library and `{b_i}` is a static residual dictionary; JumpReLU only changes the single-sample support/coef shaping before top-k, not the exported decoder basis. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export it as one static trunk lookup plus one sparse weighted sum over a fixed residual vector library, with the learned thresholds used only in online selection. At EF=2 its encoder selection cost should stay within the `≤ 1.5×h×n` hard budget and remain below the current two-stage soft-codebook mainline. The single question is whether this thresholded low-rank single-stage selector is intrinsically worth keeping in the current low-EF deployable regime, or whether the mainline’s soft-codebook plus two-stage refinement remains clearly necessary.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` is clearly worse than the mainline in both FVU and runtime metrics, discard it and return to `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round.","If it is somewhat worse in FVU but materially better in throughput or total runtime, record it as a lower-complexity compatible side branch, but still return to the mainline next round per probe policy.","If it is unexpectedly close to the mainline at lower selection cost, allow at most one later family-specific follow-up after the required return to the mainline."],"notes_to_memory":["Compatibility: `扩展兼容`. Export path is `U(Vx)` trunk lookup plus one sparse residual lookup over a fixed decoder library; JumpReLU modifies only selector thresholds, not decoder exportability.","This round is a strict matched architecture probe: keep `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` explicitly pinned, and change only `ARCHITECTURE`.","Judge family worthiness using `tokens_per_sec`, total duration, and `final_total_tokens` alongside final FVU, because LUTurbo cares about total online/runtime cost rather than FVU alone."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` and explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe fields. After `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` and `lowrank_gated_residual` both failed to pressure the mainline, `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` is the highest-value remaining feasible matched probe because it preserves LUTurbo exportability, stays in the low-EF budgeted regime, and tests a simpler thresholded selector that could reduce total online complexity if quality holds up. The main risk is that historical evidence for JumpReLU-style selectors has been weak, so this may mainly confirm that a single-stage thresholded low-rank branch cannot recover enough quality.","summary":"Run one valid matched architecture probe on `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` while keeping the `K=128`, `EF=2`, `signum`, `LR=3.0e-3` mainline recipe fixed. This cleanly tests whether a thresholded single-stage low-rank selector is worth any continued attention under LUTurbo-compatible low-EF constraints.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0124.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其导出路径仍是静态 trunk 向量库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、静态 residual 字典库 {b_i} 上的有限加权和，可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿链路，因此兼容性为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 约 1.25x，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮吸取 r123 policy_reject 的信号，严格只改一个主变量：在保持 K=128、EF=2、LR=3.0e-3 不变的前提下，仅将 optimizer 从 signum 切到 adam，先确认 optimizer 轴本身是否可跑、曲线是否有价值，再决定是否值得单独为 adam 开 LR 子扫。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 adam@3.0e-3 直接劣化或不稳定，则停止 optimizer 轴，恢复 signum 主线并转向 K 轴比较 96 vs 128。","若 adam@3.0e-3 可跑但曲线显示明显过冲或震荡，再以 lr 为唯一主变量为 adam 单独补 1.5e-3。","若 adam@3.0e-3 与 signum 最终 FVU 接近但耗时更长，则将 adam 视为负面信号，不再继续投入轮次。"],"notes_to_memory":["family 不变，兼容性仍为扩展兼容，导出公式与 LUTurbo 链路映射不变。","r123 policy_reject 表明上一轮 optimizer+lr 联动可能违反当前单变量策略，本轮改为只测 optimizer。","评估必须同时记录 FVU、总耗时、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens，确认是否存在吞吐下降导致的伪改进或伪退化。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"本轮严格遵守单变量原则，只改变 optimizer，避免再次触发耦合变量的 policy_reject。缺点是 adam 使用 signum 的 LR 可能不是最优，但先验证 optimizer 轴是否值得继续，比再次提交耦合改动更稳妥。","summary":"围绕预算内主线 family 做一次严格单变量的 optimizer 测试：固定 K=128、EF=2、LR=3.0e-3，仅把 signum 切到 adam，先确认 adam 在该主线上的可运行性、曲线形状与时间成本。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0222.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。基于 r218 已在 total_cost=0.49x 处给出当前 <0.5x 区域最佳 FVU=0.1462，而最近两轮更复杂低成本结构 probe（factorized_topk、lowrank_factorized_residual@TRUNK_RANK=32）分别给出明显更差 FVU，且 r221 还把吞吐压到 111k tokens/s、总时长拉到 760s，说明当前更值得在最强低开销锚点上做不增加系统成本的单变量 recipe 探针。本轮严格锚定 r218，只改 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`，测试在 EF=1、K=248、字典容量已很紧、支持集已很大的低成本 regime 下，去掉 auxiliary-K loss 是否能减少对主重构目标的干扰，在不恶化 tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens 的前提下，把 <0.5x 前沿 FVU 继续压低。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 在保持接近 r218 吞吐与总时长的同时把 FVU 压到 0.1462 以下，则下一轮对该无辅助损失配方做一次 clean repeat 确认，再考虑继续围绕 topk 低成本主线做 recipe 局部化。","如果 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 与 r218 基本等价，则记录 auxiliary loss 在 `topk@EF1,K248` 低成本主线中不是关键因子，随后转向同一锚点上的单变量 LR probe。","如果 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 明显退化，则恢复默认 auxiliary loss，并将 loss 轴在该 low-cost topk 主线上暂时关闭。"],"notes_to_memory":["r221 证明低秩 trunk 压缩在 lowrank_factorized_residual 上同时伤害质量与运行代价，不应继续占用 <0.5x 主线轮次。","当前最有价值的动作是在已知最强 <0.5x 点 `topk@EF1,K248` 上做不改变部署成本的单变量 recipe probe，而不是继续引入更长选择链路。","若 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 成功，则说明在高 K、低 EF 的单库 topk 低成本 regime 中，auxiliary K loss 可能只是训练干扰项而非必要正则。"],"reference_round":218,"self_review":"该提案满足单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r218 只改 `AUXK_ALPHA`，不改 family、K、EF、optimizer、LR 或其他结构参数。相比继续做新的 architecture probe，这一步信息更干净，因为它直接回答当前最强 <0.5x 锚点是否还有零部署增量的可挖掘训练收益；风险是 auxiliary loss 可能仍对活跃特征利用有帮助，但这正是本轮要隔离验证的问题。","summary":"相对 r218 的 `topk@EF1,K248` 做一次严格 param_only loss 轴验证，仅将 `AUXK_ALPHA` 设为 0.0，判断去掉 auxiliary-K loss 能否在不增加系统成本和运行时负担的前提下继续压低 <0.5x 前沿 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0137.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002low-rank trunk \u57fa\u5e93 U\u3001soft codebook \u5e93 {c_m}\u3001\u4e24\u9636\u6bb5 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93 {b_i} \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u7684\u56fa\u5b9a\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u65f6 encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.25x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002\u6700\u8fd1 r132/r133/r136 \u5728\u6539 AUXK_ALPHA\u3001TRUNK_RANK\u3001NUM_CODES \u540e\u5f97\u5230\u51e0\u4e4e\u5b8c\u5168\u76f8\u540c\u7684 start/mid/end FVU\u3001tokens_per_sec \u4e0e final_total_tokens\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u66f4\u9700\u8981\u5148\u8865\u4e00\u8f6e\u65e0\u9644\u52a0\u6210\u672c\u8f74\u6270\u52a8\u7684 clean baseline\uff0c\u786e\u8ba4\u4e3b\u7ebf reference recipe \u7684\u771f\u5b9e\u66f2\u7ebf\u4e0e\u8fd0\u884c\u4ee3\u4ef7\uff0c\u518d\u51b3\u5b9a\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u662f\u5411\u4e0a\u8fd8\u662f\u5411\u4e0b\u5fae\u8c03 LR\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0086.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` and `lowrank_residual_vq` both failed to pressure the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the most informative single matched architecture probe is `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`. It preserves the same low-rank static-library export path while collapsing the selector back to a single residual pass with thresholded support selection, which is more promising for LUTurbo's total online cost (`selection + coeffs + lookup + compensation`) than another multi-stage or routed variant. If it is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=2.0e-3, EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then this simpler low-rank single-stage family is not worth continuing in the current regime.","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching `ARCHITECTURE` to `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the round rule by changing exactly one primary variable: `architecture`. I kept the current mainline recipe fixed, explicitly pinned `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, and chose a candidate that is LUTurbo-compatible and meaningfully simpler online than the current two-stage mainline. Risk: older low-K evidence for this family was weak, so this may just confirm that the simpler single-stage thresholded selector cannot retain enough quality at matched K128.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_jumprelu_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 86 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Judge this run as a family-worthiness test for a simpler low-rank single-stage thresholded selector that may reduce LUTurbo online selection and compensation cost; return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor, discard it and resume mainline tuning on `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round.","If `lowrank_jumprelu_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a viable lower-online-complexity branch but still return to the mainline next round per probe policy."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0180.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual_vq"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_residual_vq","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_residual_vq` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library, `c_m` is one selected codebook vector from a static coarse library, and the residual term is a weighted sum over a static residual dictionary. This is `扩展兼容` because LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors, coarse codebook, and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then run `trunk branch + coarse code lookup + sparse residual lookups + weighted sum` online. The single question for this probe is whether replacing the soft coarse branch with a hard VQ-style coarse branch is worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime. This should stay inside the encoder-cost budget at `EF=2`, so it is likely to produce a real training/runtime signal rather than another policy reject.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If `lowrank_residual_vq` underperforms the mainline on FVU or slows training without a compensating runtime/quality benefit, mark hard-VQ coarse branches as not worth continuing in the current low-cost regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_residual_vq` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: decode is a finite weighted sum over static trunk vectors, one static coarse codebook entry, and static residual dictionary atoms.","This matched probe tests a meaningful architecture axis that has not been revisited recently in the current low-EF regime: soft coarse branch versus hard coarse branch.","Review `tokens_per_sec`, total runtime, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU; a small quality change with worse throughput should count against continuing the family."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` remain fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe stays within the compatible family set, is likely budget-feasible, and answers a clean architectural question without drifting into another over-budget selector variant.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_residual_vq` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) through a static low-rank trunk, a static coarse codebook, and a static residual dictionary, and it tests whether a hard coarse branch is worth continuing versus the current soft-codebook two-stage mainline.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0158.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"该 family 的最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可离线导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终重构仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r157 已在当前低 EF 主线下再次给出 adam 的爆炸性负信号，因此 optimizer 分支可视为已被明确关闭。按推荐顺序，下一步应转向 loss/preprocess 轴；本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family、EF、K、主优化器和 LR 不变的前提下，完全去掉 auxiliary K loss（AUXK_ALPHA=0.0）是否能减少对主重构目标的干扰，带来更好的曲线形状或至少确认该辅助项在当前可部署 regime 下已无必要。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 在不恶化吞吐与总时长的前提下改善曲线或终点，则下一轮做一次同配方 clean repeat 确认。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 与基线几乎等价，则记录 auxiliary loss 在该 regime 下非关键，随后再考虑更贴近系统成本的 K 轴。","若 AUXK_ALPHA=0.0 明显退化，则恢复默认辅助项并结束 loss 轴试探。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 下 selection_cost 仍在预算内；本轮不改 EF、K、TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或其他成本轴，只隔离 auxiliary loss 效应。","r157 在当前主线 regime 下再次复现了 adam 的强负信号，optimizer 分支应正式关闭。","评估本轮必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，区分是否存在由训练更长或吞吐异常造成的假信号。"],"primary_variable":"auxk_alpha","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 AUXK_ALPHA，family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，符合单变量原则。当前策略顺序在 optimizer 之后本就应转向 loss/preprocess，而 r157 已把 optimizer 问题回答得足够清楚；因此继续停留在 optimizer 分支价值很低，不如用最小改动检查辅助损失在当前低成本主线中的必要性。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；在 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3 固定的前提下，仅将 AUXK_ALPHA 设为 0.0，判断去掉 auxiliary K loss 是否能改善当前可部署 regime 的训练曲线或确认其已无必要。","touched_files":[]}
