research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0060.json:85:      "If matched `jumprelu` is roughly competitive with a healthy curve, still return to the `gated` mainline next round, but preserve one later revisit because its thresholded support path may better align with LUTurbo online-cost goals.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0112.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.4e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，因此该 family 属于扩展兼容。单主变量改为 EXPANSION_FACTOR: 12 -> 2，可把该 family 的 selection_cost 压到约 1.16x h×n，回到 ≤1.5x 硬预算内，同时保留当前主线结构，回答“这个强 backbone 在最低可行 EF 下是否仍能以更低总在线成本给出比 factorized_topk 更好的 FVU/时延权衡”。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 EF=2 已可行且 FVU 仍明显优于 factorized_topk，则下一轮在同 family 上补 clean baseline，检查曲线是否仍在下降。","若 EF=2 曲线形状健康但收敛偏慢，则只调 LR 作为单变量。","若 EF=2 的 FVU 退化过大，则保留该 family 但转向单变量降低 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM 或 TRUNK_RANK，探索 EF=2 下更便宜 scorer 的最优点。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性：扩展兼容；导出形式为 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","本轮严格遵守单变量原则，只验证 EF 收缩后的成本可行性与低 EF 表达质量。","K 对选择成本几乎无影响，因此保持 K=128，不把成本变化和稀疏预算变化混在一起。"],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor","self_review":"这是当前策略要求下最小且可归因的主线动作：先把主线 family 拉回预算内，再看其低 EF regime 是否仍有竞争力。风险是 EF=2 可能让 FVU 明显恶化，但这正是本轮唯一要回答的问题。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构。用参考配方 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / K=128 / signum / LR=2.4e-3，仅将 EXPANSION_FACTOR 从 12 降到 2，先验证该扩展兼容结构在 LUTurbo 选择成本预算内的可行 Pareto 点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0183.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"NUM_CODES","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。r182 在只把 NUM_CODES 从默认 256 降到 128 时，FVU 与整条训练曲线都基本不变，说明当前 coarse codebook 仍有明显冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：把 NUM_CODES 继续降到 64，是否仍能基本保持主线质量，同时进一步降低 code_router、codebook_matmul 与 codebook_deploy 的总成本，从而改善 LUTurbo 可部署 Pareto 点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 NUM_CODES=64 仍接近 0.0581 且吞吐/总耗时不恶化，则继续沿 codebook size 轴下探，或把 64 作为新的低成本 clean mainline。","若 NUM_CODES=64 出现明显 FVU 退化，则说明 128 已接近 coarse branch 下限，下一轮回到 NUM_CODES=128 并改测 TRUNK_RANK。","若 FVU 基本不变但 tokens_per_sec 再次异常下滑，则优先把该现象视为运行时噪声信号，而不是结构负面结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 在 `NUM_CODES=64` 下导出路径不变，仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库的有限加权和。","r182 已表明 `NUM_CODES=128` 相对 baseline 几乎零质量损失，因此继续缩小 codebook 是当前最干净的单变量成本推进。","评估本轮必须同时检查 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，确认收益来自真实成本下降而非运行时漂移。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，只继续沿 `NUM_CODES` 这一主成本旋钮推进。相比重复测过的 TRUNK_RANK，这一步更直接触碰 coarse branch 的选择成本和部署查表成本，且与 r182 形成自然的连续主线。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构；固定 `K=128, EF=2, signum, LR=3.0e-3`，仅把 `NUM_CODES` 从 128 再降到 64，验证 coarse codebook 是否还能继续压缩而不明显伤害 FVU，从而进一步降低 LUTurbo 的总在线成本。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0148.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.6e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r145 与 r147 在相同 family/K/EF/optimizer 下两次复现了 LR=3.3e-3 的更优终点 FVU=0.0579389，相比 3.0e-3 baseline 的 0.0581064 是稳定正信号；同时 r147 的更长耗时主要来自 tokens_per_sec 从约 166.5k 降到 66.6k，而 final_total_tokens 仍是 59,969,536，说明这次变慢更像运行时吞吐波动，不应提前终止 LR 轴。本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family、EF、K、optimizer 与导出形式不变的前提下，把 signum 学习率从 3.3e-3 继续上探到 3.6e-3，是否还能延续中后段收敛改善并进一步压低 FVU，还是已经开始进入过冲区间。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 3.6e-3 终点继续优于 3.3e-3 且曲线未出现更早平台或震荡，则补一轮 clean repeat 确认新的 signum 主线 LR。","若 3.6e-3 与 3.3e-3 持平或更差，则关闭 signum LR 上探分支，把 3.3e-3 视为当前主线最优配方。","若 3.6e-3 明显过冲或训练曲线变差，则停止继续加大学习率，后续只在已确认的 3.3e-3 锚点上考虑其余单变量轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的导出形式未变，仍属扩展兼容，可继续作为 LUTurbo 主线 family。","EF=2 继续满足 selection_cost 预算；K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与 LR 轴混杂。","r145 与 r147 已把 3.3e-3 从一次性噪声提升为可复现信号；r147 的慢速更像吞吐异常而非训练更长。","近期一些成本侧参数改动出现与 baseline 完全相同的终点与 token 轨迹，后续若再走成本轴，应先确认这些 override 在执行链路中的实际生效情况。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 全部固定在当前主线参考配方。相比再开 optimizer 或 loss/preprocess 分支，这一步更符合当前主线推进要求，因为 3.3e-3 已给出稳定改善而其上界仍未确认。主要风险是 3.6e-3 只是更激进而不更好，因此评估时必须同时看完整曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，而不是只看最终 FVU。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；在 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 固定的前提下，仅把 LR 从已复现改善的 3.3e-3 上调到 3.6e-3，判断 signum 上探是否还能进一步降低 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0140.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。这里 low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 的兼容性判断为扩展兼容。EF=2 时其 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，仍满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。近期 clean baseline、LR=2.4e-3、STAGE1_RATIO=0.75 都已看清：3.0e-3 signum 仍是稳定锚点，而 r136 把 NUM_CODES 降到 32 后在 start/mid/end FVU、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens 上与 baseline 基本重合，说明 codebook 容量可能仍有未利用冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：在 family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全固定的前提下，进一步把 NUM_CODES 从当前等效可行的 32 压到 16，是否仍能维持接近 0.0581 的 FVU，同时继续降低 code_router/codebook_matmul 的 encoder 选择成本和 codebook_deploy 的部署查表成本，从而形成更强的 LUTurbo 成本侧 Pareto 点。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0140.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0157.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"该 family 的最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可离线导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终重构仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下的 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r153-r155 已先后补齐 clean baseline 并把 signum 的 LR 曲线看清，3.3e-3 虽有小幅稳定收益，但当前策略顺序要求在 LR 之后先回答 optimizer 问题，且 r156 的 K 轴尝试已被 policy 拦截，因此本轮只改一个主变量 OPTIMIZER：保持 family、EF、K、LR 与导出形式不变，仅将优化器从 signum 切到 adam，回答唯一问题：在同样的可部署低成本 regime 下，optimizer 本身是否仍有值得保留的曲线形状或终点信号，还是应被再次明确关闭。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 adam 在相同 LR=3.0e-3 下再次明显爆炸或曲线极差，则正式关闭该 family 在当前低 EF regime 的 optimizer 分支，后续不再用它驱动主线。","若 adam 没有爆炸且曲线具备可比性，即使终点未赢，也可记录为需要一次 optimizer-local LR callback 的候选。","若 adam 意外优于 signum 基线，则下一轮再严格做一次单变量的 optimizer 分支确认或回调。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 下 selection_cost 仍在预算内；本轮不改 EF、K、TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或其他成本轴，只隔离 optimizer 效应。","r153-r155 已把主线 baseline 与 LR 曲线重新看清；当前最缺的是在现行策略顺序下对 optimizer 的明确结论。","评估时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，区分是优化器本身导致训练更慢、更长，还是直接数值不稳定。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 optimizer，family、EF、K、LR 全部固定，符合单变量原则和当前主线推进顺序。虽然历史上 adam 在该 family 上已有负信号，但在当前回合策略明确要求 LR 之后先看 optimizer，而 r156 的 K 轴尝试已被 policy 拦截；因此最合规且信息量最高的动作是用当前参考配方再给 optimizer 一次干净结论，而不是继续提前动 K。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、LR=3.0e-3，仅将 OPTIMIZER 从 signum 切到 adam，判断 optimizer 分支在当前可部署 regime 下是否仍值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0243.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: jumprelu。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；JumpReLU 只改变单样本在线侧的阈值化支持形成与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端的单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿导出形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r242 只改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu`，保持 `K=96`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003` 及其余配置不变，测试在当前 `<0.5x` 主战区约 0.34x 成本位置，learned-threshold selector 是否能在不继续拉长 plain topk 查表链路的前提下，把 FVU 压到优于 `topk@K96` 的 0.2219。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@K96` 明显优于 `topk@K96`，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有像 r234 那样显著恶化，则下一轮继续在同 family 内相对本轮单变量调 `K=112` 或回到已验证更强的高 K jump 线做受控降本。","如果 `jumprelu@K96` 与 `topk@K96` 基本持平但运行明显更慢，则关闭 jumprelu 在中低 K 区域的主线优先级，不再把它作为 `<0.5x` 默认扩展方向。","如果 `jumprelu@K96` 明显差于 `topk@K96`，则把本轮记为低 K learned-threshold 负信号，后续转向其他低开销 family，而不是继续加密 plain topk 或继续做 jump 阈值微调。"],"notes_to_memory":["r242 已说明继续沿 plain topk 的中段 K 轴能改善 FVU，但 508s 的时长恶化使其不再适合作为默认主线；下一步更有信息量的问题是同成本位置是否存在更优 family。","jumprelu family 在 EF=1、高 K 区域已有正面先验：`K=224-248` 时 FVU 可达 0.145-0.152，说明 learned-threshold selector 在低成本 regime 并非天然无效。","本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只带来很小质量收益但时长显著变差，应直接视为负面系统信号。"],"reference_round":242,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r242 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不联动 K、EF、optimizer、LR 或 JumpReLU 专属参数。选择 `jumprelu` 而不是继续推 `topk@K112`，是因为 r242 已给出“质量继续改善但运行代价显著抬升”的信号；当前更高价值的问题是同一成本槽位是否存在比 plain topk 更好的低开销兼容 family。","summary":"停止继续加密 plain topk 的中段 K 扫描，严格锚定 r242 仅切到 `jumprelu`，在约 0.34x 总成本位置测试 learned-threshold 单库结构能否比 `topk@K96` 给出更好的 cost-FVU 权衡，同时避免重演 r234 那类明显的运行时代价恶化。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0181.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_factorized_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_factorized_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_factorized_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk and the residual coefficients are chosen by a factorized scorer but still decode as a finite weighted sum over a static residual dictionary `B`. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then run `trunk branch + factorized support scoring + weighted sparse lookup-sum` online. The single question is whether a lower-cost factorized residual selector is worth continuing versus the current two-stage soft-codebook mainline in the low-EF feasible regime. This probe should stay safely within the encoder-cost budget and gives a clean read on whether scorer factorization is a viable architecture direction rather than another likely policy reject.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If `lowrank_factorized_residual` underperforms on FVU and/or slows throughput without a compensating cost advantage, mark factorized residual scoring as not worth continuing in the current low-cost regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_factorized_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: the factorized encoder changes selector-side scoring only; decode remains a finite weighted sum over static trunk and residual libraries.","This matched probe tests a still-compatible low-cost architecture direction that has not recently been revisited under the current `K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3e-3` regime.","Review `tokens_per_sec`, wall-clock time, and `final_total_tokens` together with FVU; if factorization only saves selector cost proxy but trains materially slower or reconstructs worse, treat that as a negative signal."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` remain fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe stays inside the compatible and likely feasible set, and it answers a distinct architectural question about whether factorized scoring is intrinsically worth keeping alive on the Pareto search path.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_factorized_residual` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) through a static low-rank trunk plus static residual dictionary, and it tests whether factorized residual scoring is worth continuing against the current soft-codebook two-stage mainline in the low-EF feasible regime.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0218.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"248"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214-r217 已连续证明在 EF=1 下沿 K 轴增加查表预算能稳定压低 <0.5x 区域的 FVU，且最近一轮 K=240 仍把最佳低开销 FVU 压到 0.1483，说明边际收益虽变小但尚未消失；因此本轮继续只提升 K 到 248，目标是在总成本仍预计略低于 0.5x、继续留在低开销区的前提下，再验证 topk@EF1 的贴边收益，并避免直接跳到可能越过 0.5x 的更大 K。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K248 仍有可见改善且运行代价稳定，则可再补一个贴近 0.5x 的终点。","如果 K248 的收益已经很小或训练代价恶化，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 基本到头，后续应转向新的低成本 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 仍是当前 <0.5x 区域最稳的直接兼容主线，导出路径最简单，且连续数轮都给出可解释的 Pareto 改善。","选择 K=248 而不是 256，是为了尽量稳妥地继续停留在 <0.5x 区域，同时测试贴边预算下的最后一段边际收益。","评估时继续同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认这段额外查表预算是否值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮保持单一变化轴并延续已验证有效的低开销 topk 主线。相比直接冲 K=256，K=248 更符合当前“补 <0.5x 前沿”而不是跨到 0.5x 以上质量锚点的目标；风险是收益可能已接近饱和，但这正是当前需要测清的信号。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 248，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1483 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0159.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.75x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，并且比当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x 更低。当前 round 159 只允许一个 matched architecture probe，因此保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 以及主要 recipe 完全不变，仅将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成其最邻近的单阶段父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，回答唯一问题：在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下，第二阶段 residual refinement 是否仍然值得保留，还是单阶段 soft-codebook 版本已经提供了更优的系统级 cost-FVU 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 明显落后于 two-stage 主线，则说明第二阶段 refinement 在当前低 EF regime 下仍然有价值，下一轮回到主线继续 recipe 轴。","若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 与 two-stage 接近且成本更低，则记录其为更强的低成本备选 family，但下一轮仍按要求回到当前主线。","若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 本身值得重新审视，但本轮只做架构价值判断，不立即连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为扩展兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更低 FVU 或更低成本误判为吞吐波动导致的假信号。","该 probe 的核心问题不是刷新 frontier，而是判断 two-stage 结构增量在当前可部署低 EF regime 下是否仍然值得继续。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 而不是更远的 topk 或 factorized_topk，是因为它是当前主线的最近父节点，能最干净地隔离“第二阶段 residual refinement 本身是否值得”这个问题，同时还能给出更低 selection_cost 的直接对照。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为其单阶段父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断第二阶段 refinement 在当前低成本 regime 下是否仍然值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0125.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002\u5176\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93 U\u3001\u9759\u6001 soft-codebook \u5e93 {c_m} \u4e0e\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93 {b_i} \u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u6620\u5c04\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u2018\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u2019\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u5f53\u524d family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b selection_cost \u7ea6\u4e3a 1.16x \u5230 1.25x\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002r124 \u8868\u660e adam@3.0e-3 \u5728\u8be5\u4e3b\u7ebf\u4e0b\u76f4\u63a5\u7206\u70b8\uff0coptimizer \u8f74\u5df2\u7ed9\u51fa\u660e\u786e\u8d1f\u9762\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u56de\u7b54\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u6062\u590d\u7a33\u5b9a\u4e3b\u7ebf signum@3.0e-3 \u540e\uff0cK=96 \u76f8\u5bf9 K=128 \u7684\u66f4\u4f4e\u90e8\u7f72\u67e5\u8868\u6210\u672c\u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u4ee5\u5c11\u91cf FVU \u9000\u5316\u6362\u53d6\u66f4\u597d\u7684\u7cfb\u7edf\u6027\u4ef7\u6bd4\u4e0e\u8bad\u7ec3\u8017\u65f6\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0186.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"16"}],"expected_win":"pareto_improve","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 仍满足 ≤1.5×h×n 硬约束。r133 把 `TRUNK_RANK` 降到 32 时几乎零损失复现了主线 FVU，r182-r184 继续压缩 `NUM_CODES` 也未改变终点，说明当前主线可能仍有明显结构冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：将 `TRUNK_RANK` 进一步下调到 16，是否仍能保持接近当前主线的训练曲线与终点 FVU，同时继续降低 trunk 相关的 encoder 选择成本与部署查表成本，从而推动兼容 Pareto 前沿向更低总成本移动。","summary":"继续围绕同一主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3`，仅把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从已验证无损的 32 再降到 16，测试更激进的 trunk 压缩是否仍能维持当前 LUTurbo 可部署质量。","needs_sanity":false,"notes_to_memory":["family 与导出路径不变，`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 在 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 下仍是扩展兼容：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库的有限加权和。","r133 表明 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 相对主线几乎无损，因此继续沿 trunk 容量轴下探比重复未增益的 `NUM_CODES` 压缩更有信息价值。","评估本轮必须同时比较 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认任何收益来自真实成本下降而非运行时漂移。"],"next_hypotheses":["若 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 仍接近当前主线 FVU 且吞吐不恶化，可将更低 rank 视为新的低成本主线，并考虑继续下探或做一次 clean baseline 复验。","若 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 明显退化，则说明 trunk 容量下限更接近 32，下一轮回到 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 并转向 `NUM_CODES` 或其他单一成本轴。","若终点接近但吞吐显著变差，则把更低 trunk rank 视为负面系统信号，而不是仅凭 FVU 保留。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"本轮严格遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，只推进 `TRUNK_RANK` 这一直接作用于 encoder 选择成本和部署 trunk 成本的主变量。相比继续尝试在 policy 上有风险的 optimizer 分支，这一步更稳、更可归因，也更贴近 LUTurbo 的真实总成本目标。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0231.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"group_topk"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"group_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family: group_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；group_topk 只改变单样本在线侧的支持形成方式，先在每个静态分组内选 winner，再做全局保留，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 r215 只改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE=group_topk`，保持 `K=192`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`signum`、`LR=0.003` 及其余配置不变，测试在约 0.44x 总成本处，用组内竞争带来的更均匀支持分配能否优于当前同成本 `topk@K192` 的 FVU=0.16352，或者至少给出比 plain topk 更有价值的系统信号。选择这个 probe 的原因是：r230 已经说明“极短 factorized scorer”虽然很便宜但质量塌陷，因此下一步更值得测试的是不缩短 decoder 契约、也不抬高成本、只改支持分配规则的同成本单库架构。默认 `group_topk_size=4` 时，EF=1 对应 768 latents 可分成 192 组，恰好允许 `K=192` 的有效运行，成本与 topk 同阶且满足 LUTurbo 总成本硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `group_topk@K192` 在同成本下优于 `topk@K192`，且 tokens_per_sec、duration_sec 没有明显恶化，则可相对本轮继续单变量切到 `K=128` 或 `K=224` 的同 family 映射，判断这条组竞争支线是否值得进入 `<0.5x` 主前沿。","如果 `group_topk` 质量与 topk 接近但运行更差，则将其记为负面系统信号，说明单库组竞争没有带来有效收益，不再继续占用主线轮次。","如果 `group_topk` 明显差于 `topk@K192`，则关闭这条同成本 grouped selector 支线，转向其他低成本 family，而不是继续在单库支持规则上做更多小改。"],"notes_to_memory":["r230 已证明 factorized_topk 的极低 encoder 成本并没有转化为可用质量：虽然 total_cost 只有约 0.30x，但 FVU=0.3909，远差于同区间 topk。","当前更高价值的问题不是继续压 factorized scorer 的 hidden，而是在不改变单库导出契约、也不增加成本的前提下，测试另一种支持分配机制能否改善 `<0.5x` 区域的质量。","`group_topk` 在 EF=1、K=192、group_topk_size=4 下是有效配置；评估时必须同步看 FVU、tokens_per_sec、duration_sec、final_total_tokens，避免把极小质量变化误判成正收益。"],"reference_round":215,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r215 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，不联动 K、EF、optimizer、LR 或其他参数。选择 `group_topk` 而不是继续沿 jumprelu 或 factorized_topk 做邻域微调，是因为前者在当前低开销区间尚未得到干净的低 EF probe，同时能以与 `topk@K192` 几乎相同的成本，直接回答“更结构化的支持分配是否值得”这个独立问题。主要风险是 grouped 约束可能过强导致质量下滑，但这正是本轮需要以最小变量改动确认的内容。","summary":"相对 r215 的 `topk@EF1,K192` 做一次严格 param_only architecture probe，仅切到 `group_topk`。目标是在保持约 0.44x 总成本不变的前提下，测试组内竞争式支持分配能否在 `<0.5x` 区域形成比 plain topk 更好的 cost-FVU 权衡。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0165.json:17:    "hypothesis": "Matched architecture probe on lowrank_soft_codebook_residual with K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3 unchanged. Final reconstruction formula is x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i, where U(Vx) is a static low-rank trunk library, {c_m} is a static soft-codebook library, and {b_i} is a static residual dictionary. This is \u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9: LUTurbo can export it as trunk lookup + codebook lookup + one residual sparse lookup, all over fixed vector libraries. The single question for this probe is whether removing the second residual refinement stage keeps enough reconstruction quality to justify the lower encoder selection cost and likely lower runtime in the low-EF regime.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0165.json:18:    "summary": "Run a single matched architecture probe with ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_soft_codebook_residual while keeping K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, and LR=3.0e-3 fixed. The probe tests whether the simpler one-stage soft-codebook parent is still worth continuing as a lower-cost LUTurbo-compatible branch relative to the current two-stage mainline.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0165.json:23:    "self_review": "This probe is conservative because the family is already known and compatible, so upside is mostly in runtime-cost tradeoff rather than discovering a new best FVU. That makes it appropriate after the previous matched probe was policy-rejected: it isolates a single structural difference and should yield a clean comparable signal.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0165.json:34:      "This is a matched architecture probe that changes only ARCHITECTURE and stays safely within the known EF=2 selection-cost budget table.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0165.json:35:      "Probe intent is architectural value judgment only: test whether the second sparse stage in the current mainline is worth its extra encoder cost/runtime under LUTurbo constraints."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0165.json:39:      "If runtime improves meaningfully at only modest FVU loss, keep lowrank_soft_codebook_residual as a cost-efficient compatible branch on the Pareto frontier, but still return to the mainline next round per probe policy."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0077.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Rounds 75 and 76 ruled out the simplest matched single-stage alternatives under the current `two_stage_residual` anchor: both `topk` and `jumprelu` were clearly worse at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=2.0e-3`. The next single matched architecture probe should therefore test a structurally different exportable decomposition rather than another plain selector. `codebook_topk` is the highest-value remaining yes/no probe because it still maps to a finite weighted sum over static vector libraries, but may reduce LUTurbo online coefficient and lookup cost by reusing a compact static basis instead of a full staged residual path. This round asks one question only: under the exact current mainline recipe, is `codebook_topk` competitive enough in full-curve behavior to remain worth later consideration, or should it be ruled out as clearly inferior to `two_stage_residual`?","summary":"Use the one allowed matched architecture probe on `codebook_topk`. Keep the current mainline recipe fixed at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and the same aux/runtime settings, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `two_stage_residual` to `codebook_topk`. Judge the run by the whole trajectory, not just the endpoint: if `codebook_topk` stays reasonably close with a healthy curve, keep it in reserve because its shared-codebook structure may lower LUTurbo online lookup and coefficient cost; if it is clearly worse throughout, close the probe and return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"codebook_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This obeys the Round 77 rule by changing exactly one primary variable, `architecture`, while keeping `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, `LR`, and the rest of the recipe fixed. `codebook_topk` is a better use of the single probe than revisiting already-rejected plain selector variants because it tests a different cost-quality tradeoff that is still compatible with LUTurbo's static export contract. The main risk is that prior matched probing in an earlier regime already suggested weakness, but this remains the most informative remaining architecture-worthiness check under the current mainline anchor.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"codebook_topk"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 77 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `codebook_topk` against the current `two_stage_residual` mainline recipe, because it represents a distinct static-library decomposition that may reduce LUTurbo online lookup and coefficient cost while preserving exportability.","Judge this probe as a family-worthiness test only: compare matched `codebook_topk@128` against the `two_stage_residual` reference at fixed `EF=12`, `signum`, and `LR=2.0e-3`, then return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome."],"next_hypotheses":["If matched `codebook_topk` is reasonably close with a healthy curve, return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round but keep one later `codebook_topk` revisit available because its shared-codebook path may be cheaper to deploy.","If matched `codebook_topk` is clearly worse than `two_stage_residual` across the curve, close the probe and return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round.","If matched `codebook_topk` unexpectedly beats the current `two_stage_residual` reference, still return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round per policy, but record `codebook_topk` as a high-priority later follow-up family."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0088.json:19:    "hypothesis": "After `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual`, `lowrank_residual_vq`, `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`, and `lowrank_gated_residual` all failed to pressure the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the most informative remaining matched architecture probe is `lowrank_grouped_residual`. It preserves the same low-rank trunk and static-vector export contract, but replaces full global residual selection with group-local winner selection, which is directly relevant to lowering LUTurbo's online selection cost while keeping the reconstruction as a finite weighted sum over a static library. If this grouped selector is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then grouped single-stage low-rank selection is not worth continuing in the current regime.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0088.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0088.json:57:      "If `lowrank_grouped_residual` is unexpectedly competitive at matched K128, record it as a viable lower-selection-cost branch but still return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round per probe policy."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0239.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"48"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r238 只改一个 env 参数 `K=48`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003`、`AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` 及其余配置不变，测试在约 0.30x 总成本处，是否能把刚建立的左端点 `topk@K32` 的 FVU=0.3199 继续明显压低，并补出 `0.28x -> 0.31x` 之间缺失的 Pareto 过渡点。选择这一步而不是继续开新 family，是因为 r238 已证明最简单单库结构在超低 K 左端优于 `factorized_topk@0.30x`，当前最高信息量问题变成 topk 左侧前沿的真实斜率，而不是再次切到最近已给出负信号的 `codebook_topk`、`factorized_topk` 或 recipe 微调线。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `topk@EF1,K48` 在约 0.30x 成本处显著优于 `K32`，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则相对本轮继续单变量上探到 `K=56` 或直接回接 `K=64`，把左侧低成本前沿补完整。","如果 `K48` 相比 `K32` 改善很小，则说明 `<0.3x` 左端的单库 topk 已接近明显退化区，后续主注意力应回到更高价值的 `0.31x-0.49x` 区间。","如果质量改善存在但运行显著更慢，则按运行时优先级将其记为负面系统信号，不把该配方升格为左侧前沿点。"],"notes_to_memory":["r238 已确认 `topk@EF1,K32` 在约 0.28x 成本处优于当前最左端 `factorized_topk@0.30x`，说明左侧超低成本前沿应由 plain topk 而不是 factorized scorer 主导。","当前 `<0.5x` 前沿在 `0.28x` 与 `0.31x` 之间仍有空档；相对 r238 只提升 `K` 是最小、最可解释、最有利于刻画左端 Pareto 斜率的动作。","评估本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是小幅质量改善但运行明显更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":238,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r238 只改 `K`，不联动 architecture、EF、LR、optimizer、AUXK_ALPHA 或任何新参数。主要风险是 `K32->48` 的收益可能不足以形成新的非支配点；但在左端低成本区刚出现正信号后，先补中间过渡点比贸然切回已被证伪的 family 更符合当前 Pareto 补全目标。","summary":"相对 r238 的 `topk@EF1,K32` 做一次严格 param_only 左端补点，仅设置 `K=48`，验证 plain topk 能否在约 0.30x 总成本处继续压低 FVU，并补完整个超低成本左侧前沿。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0086.json:19:    "hypothesis": "After `routed_lowrank_two_stage_residual` and `lowrank_residual_vq` both failed to pressure the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor, the most informative single matched architecture probe is `lowrank_jumprelu_residual`. It preserves the same low-rank static-library export path while collapsing the selector back to a single residual pass with thresholded support selection, which is more promising for LUTurbo's total online cost (`selection + coeffs + lookup + compensation`) than another multi-stage or routed variant. If it is still clearly weaker under the exact matched `K=128, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=2.0e-3, EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, then this simpler low-rank single-stage family is not worth continuing in the current regime.",
