research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0198.json:54:      "\u7ee7\u7eed\u907f\u514d routed \u4e0e bucketed matched probe\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u4eec\u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b selection_cost \u8d85\u8fc7 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u9884\u7b97\u3002"
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0138.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002low-rank trunk \u57fa\u5e93 U\u3001soft codebook \u5e93 {c_m}\u3001\u4e24\u9636\u6bb5 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93 {b_i} \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u7684\u56fa\u5b9a\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u65f6 encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.25x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002r137 \u7684 clean baseline \u4e0e r132/r133/r136 \u5728 start/mid/end FVU \u548c final_total_tokens \u4e0a\u5b8c\u5168\u91cd\u5408\uff0c\u4e14 late stage \u4ecd\u663e\u793a\u5728\u6539\u5584\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf recipe \u5df2\u7a33\u5b9a\u5230\u8db3\u4ee5\u8fdb\u5165\u5355\u53d8\u91cf LR \u626b\u63cf\uff1b\u540c\u65f6 r137 \u7684\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u4e0a\u5347\u4e3b\u8981\u6765\u81ea tokens_per_sec \u5f02\u5e38\u4e0b\u964d\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u8bad\u7ec3\u66f4\u957f\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u5e94\u628a\u8fd9\u6b21\u53d8\u6162\u8bef\u5224\u4e3a\u7ed3\u6784\u6216\u914d\u65b9\u9000\u5316\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u56de\u7b54\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 family\u3001EF\u3001K\u3001optimizer \u4e0d\u53d8\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u5c06 LR \u4ece 3.0e-3 \u4e0b\u8c03\u5230 2.4e-3\uff0c\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u6539\u5584\u672b\u6bb5\u6536\u655b\u5f62\u72b6\u5e76\u628a FVU \u538b\u5230 0.0581 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u5f15\u5165\u65b0\u7684\u9009\u62e9\u6210\u672c\u6216\u90e8\u7f72\u6210\u672c\u53d8\u5316\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0138.json:20:    "summary": "\u7ee7\u7eed\u4e3b\u7ebf family\uff0c\u4e0d\u5f00\u65b0\u67b6\u6784\uff1bclean baseline \u5df2\u8bc1\u660e\u5f53\u524d recipe \u7a33\u5b9a\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u672c\u8f6e\u8fdb\u5165\u5355\u53d8\u91cf LR \u626b\u63cf\uff0c\u5728 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual\u3001EF=2\u3001K=128\u3001signum \u4e0d\u53d8\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u53ea\u628a LR \u4e0b\u8c03\u5230 2.4e-3\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u6539\u5584\u672b\u6bb5\u6536\u655b\u5e76\u53d6\u5f97\u65b0\u7684 cost-FVU Pareto \u6539\u5584\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0138.json:25:    "self_review": "\u9075\u5b88\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u53ea\u6539 LR\uff0cfamily\u3001EF\u3001K\u3001optimizer \u5168\u90e8\u56fa\u5b9a\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u53c2\u8003\u914d\u65b9\u3002\u8be5\u52a8\u4f5c\u7b26\u5408\u63a8\u8350\u987a\u5e8f\uff0c\u5728 clean baseline \u4e4b\u540e\u8fdb\u5165\u5b66\u4e60\u7387\u8f74\uff1b\u540c\u65f6\u4e0d\u89e6\u78b0\u4efb\u4f55\u4f1a\u6539\u53d8 LUTurbo \u5bfc\u51fa\u5f62\u5f0f\u3001encoder selection_cost \u6216\u90e8\u7f72\u67e5\u8868\u6210\u672c\u7684\u53c2\u6570\u3002\u98ce\u9669\u662f lower LR \u53ef\u80fd\u53ea\u4f1a\u8ba9\u524d\u4e2d\u671f\u66f4\u6162\u800c\u4e0d\u6539\u5584\u7ec8\u70b9\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u5fc5\u987b\u7ee7\u7eed\u540c\u65f6\u89c2\u5bdf\u66f2\u7ebf\u5f62\u72b6\u3001tokens_per_sec\u3001\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u548c final_total_tokens\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u53ea\u770b\u6700\u540e FVU\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0138.json:78:    "description": "\u7ee7\u7eed\u4e3b\u7ebf family\uff0c\u4e0d\u5f00\u65b0\u67b6\u6784\uff1bclean baseline \u5df2\u8bc1\u660e\u5f53\u524d recipe \u7a33\u5b9a\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u672c\u8f6e\u8fdb\u5165\u5355\u53d8\u91cf LR \u626b\u63cf\uff0c\u5728 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual\u3001EF=2\u3001K=128\u3001signum \u4e0d\u53d8\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u53ea\u628a LR \u4e0b\u8c03\u5230 2.4e-3\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u6539\u5584\u672b\u6bb5\u6536\u655b\u5e76\u53d6\u5f97\u65b0\u7684 cost-FVU Pareto \u6539\u5584\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0138.json:79:    "self_review": "\u9075\u5b88\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u53ea\u6539 LR\uff0cfamily\u3001EF\u3001K\u3001optimizer \u5168\u90e8\u56fa\u5b9a\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u53c2\u8003\u914d\u65b9\u3002\u8be5\u52a8\u4f5c\u7b26\u5408\u63a8\u8350\u987a\u5e8f\uff0c\u5728 clean baseline \u4e4b\u540e\u8fdb\u5165\u5b66\u4e60\u7387\u8f74\uff1b\u540c\u65f6\u4e0d\u89e6\u78b0\u4efb\u4f55\u4f1a\u6539\u53d8 LUTurbo \u5bfc\u51fa\u5f62\u5f0f\u3001encoder selection_cost \u6216\u90e8\u7f72\u67e5\u8868\u6210\u672c\u7684\u53c2\u6570\u3002\u98ce\u9669\u662f lower LR \u53ef\u80fd\u53ea\u4f1a\u8ba9\u524d\u4e2d\u671f\u66f4\u6162\u800c\u4e0d\u6539\u5584\u7ec8\u70b9\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u5fc5\u987b\u7ee7\u7eed\u540c\u65f6\u89c2\u5bdf\u66f2\u7ebf\u5f62\u72b6\u3001tokens_per_sec\u3001\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u548c final_total_tokens\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u53ea\u770b\u6700\u540e FVU\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0126.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_selection_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0126.json:25:    "self_review": "本轮严格只改一个主变量，并把探索重心从已基本洗净的 signum/LR/K 轴转向更贴近 Pareto 目标的 selection-cost 轴。风险在于 TRUNK_RANK=32 可能过于激进，但它能最快回答该 family 是否还有内部压缩空间。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0126.json:57:      "评估时必须同时记录 selection_cost、FVU、总耗时、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens，区分收益来自真实算子简化还是训练时长波动。"
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0126.json:60:      "若 TRUNK_RANK=32 仅小幅伤害 FVU 但明显降低 selection_cost，则继续沿 trunk_rank 轴补一个中间点以细化 Pareto。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0126.json:62:      "若 TRUNK_RANK=32 同时改善时间与 selection_cost，但 FVU 退化可接受，则把它作为低成本分支保留，不再继续降 K。"
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0126.json:83:    "self_review": "本轮严格只改一个主变量，并把探索重心从已基本洗净的 signum/LR/K 轴转向更贴近 Pareto 目标的 selection-cost 轴。风险在于 TRUNK_RANK=32 可能过于激进，但它能最快回答该 family 是否还有内部压缩空间。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0075.json:20:    "summary": "Use the one allowed matched architecture probe on `topk`. Keep the current mainline recipe fixed at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and the same aux/runtime settings, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `two_stage_residual` to `topk`. Judge the run by the whole trajectory, not just the endpoint: if `topk` stays reasonably close with a healthy curve, keep it in reserve because its simpler single-stage lookup path may lower LUTurbo online cost; if it is clearly worse throughout, close the probe and return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0075.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0075.json:75:      "Round 75 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `topk` against the current `two_stage_residual` mainline recipe, because `topk` is the simplest directly compatible LUTurbo candidate and may reduce online selection and compensation cost despite weaker reconstruction.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0075.json:101:    "description": "Use the one allowed matched architecture probe on `topk`. Keep the current mainline recipe fixed at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and the same aux/runtime settings, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `two_stage_residual` to `topk`. Judge the run by the whole trajectory, not just the endpoint: if `topk` stays reasonably close with a healthy curve, keep it in reserve because its simpler single-stage lookup path may lower LUTurbo online cost; if it is clearly worse throughout, close the probe and return to the `two_stage_residual` mainline next round.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0245.json:20:    "summary": "\u4e25\u683c\u951a\u5b9a r242\uff0c\u4ec5\u5207\u5230 `group_topk`\uff0c\u5728\u7ea6 0.34x \u603b\u6210\u672c\u4f4d\u7f6e\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5206\u7ec4\u7ade\u4e89\u7684\u5355\u5e93\u7ed3\u6784\u80fd\u5426\u6bd4 `topk@K96` \u7ed9\u51fa\u66f4\u597d\u7684 cost-FVU \u6743\u8861\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u68c0\u67e5\u5b83\u662f\u5426\u6bd4\u8fd1\u671f\u5931\u8d25\u7684 jump/factorized \u5206\u652f\u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0245.json:22:    "expected_win": "better_fvu_within_low_cost_region",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0245.json:62:    "description": "\u4e25\u683c\u951a\u5b9a r242\uff0c\u4ec5\u5207\u5230 `group_topk`\uff0c\u5728\u7ea6 0.34x \u603b\u6210\u672c\u4f4d\u7f6e\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5206\u7ec4\u7ade\u4e89\u7684\u5355\u5e93\u7ed3\u6784\u80fd\u5426\u6bd4 `topk@K96` \u7ed9\u51fa\u66f4\u597d\u7684 cost-FVU \u6743\u8861\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u68c0\u67e5\u5b83\u662f\u5426\u6bd4\u8fd1\u671f\u5931\u8d25\u7684 jump/factorized \u5206\u652f\u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0016.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 15 established `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=64` as a valid new Pareto point, so the next most informative single-variable question is whether LUTurbo can push cost lower again without collapsing reconstruction. This round changes only `K`, moving from `64` to `32` while keeping the same family and recipe fixed, to measure the next step on the cost-quality frontier.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0016.json:25:    "self_review": "This stays on the active topk family, changes exactly one primary variable, and follows directly from the new `K=64` keep result. The main risk is a sharp FVU jump at `K=32`, but mapping that boundary is now more valuable than more K128 recipe polishing because LUTurbo's objective is total online cost, not only anchor quality.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0016.json:53:      "Judge this run on frontier usefulness, not raw comparison to K128 alone: the key question is whether `K=32` remains deployably compatible with a tolerable quality drop for the lower online selection and summation cost."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0016.json:58:      "If `K=32` is borderline but usable, compare it against `K=64` as a cost-quality tradeoff rather than against the K128 anchor alone."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0016.json:79:    "self_review": "This stays on the active topk family, changes exactly one primary variable, and follows directly from the new `K=64` keep result. The main risk is a sharp FVU jump at `K=32`, but mapping that boundary is now more valuable than more K128 recipe polishing because LUTurbo's objective is total online cost, not only anchor quality.",
