research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0094.json:25:    "self_review": "This is policy-clean: one probe, one primary variable, allowed `K`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` is explicit. I am choosing `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` over a heavier two-stage soft-codebook variant because the operator goal is LUTurbo online cost, not just SAE FVU, and this probe directly tests whether the promising soft-codebook branch survives with a deployment-friendlier selector. The main risk is that the added gate path may not beat the already-close grouped probe, but that still cleanly answers whether this family is worth continuing at all.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0094.json:52:      "Interpret this strictly as a family-worthiness test for a codebook-assisted single-stage gated selector that may lower LUTurbo online selection and compensation cost versus the mainline two-stage residual path.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0094.json:77:    "self_review": "This is policy-clean: one probe, one primary variable, allowed `K`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` is explicit. I am choosing `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` over a heavier two-stage soft-codebook variant because the operator goal is LUTurbo online cost, not just SAE FVU, and this probe directly tests whether the promising soft-codebook branch survives with a deployment-friendlier selector. The main risk is that the added gate path may not beat the already-close grouped probe, but that still cleanly answers whether this family is worth continuing at all.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0114.json:52:      "EF=2 \u5df2\u5728 Round 112 \u548c Round 113 \u4e0b\u7a33\u5b9a\u843d\u5728\u9009\u62e9\u6210\u672c\u9884\u7b97\u5185\uff0c\u5f53\u524d frontier \u53ef\u884c\u70b9\u4e3a cost\u22481.25x\u3001FVU\u22480.05914\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0046.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 45 showed that the strengthened `gated` recipe (`signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `USE_HADAMARD=1`) transfers from `K=128` down to `K=96`, improving the prior `gated@96` result while keeping a smooth, still-improving curve. The next single question is whether that gain carries one more step down the cost ladder: if we hold the improved recipe fixed and reduce only `K` to `64`, can `gated` produce a clearly better lower-cost point than the old `K=64` result, or does the Hadamard benefit fade before this support level?",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0046.json:20:    "summary": "Continue the active `gated` mainline and keep the improved recipe fixed: `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1`. Change only `K` from `96` to `64` to test whether the new recipe yields a stronger lower-cost deployment point at the next allowed support level. Judge the run by the full trajectory as well as the endpoint: if it stays smooth and finishes materially below the old `gated@64` control (`0.195828`), the improved recipe is genuinely useful beyond the `K=128` anchor; if it falls back toward the old curve, treat the current gain as mainly a high-K effect.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0046.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0046.json:25:    "self_review": "This stays on the current mainline family, respects the fixed `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` rule, and changes exactly one primary variable: `K`. It follows the prescribed order because the clean baseline, LR, optimizer, loss, and preprocess questions have already been answered on this recipe, and Round 45 provided positive evidence that the improved recipe transfers at least to `K=96`. The main risk is that `K=64` may sit past the regime where Hadamard helps, but that is the highest-value remaining single-question probe for LUTurbo-relevant cost reduction.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0046.json:80:      "Round 46 isolates the next deployment-relevant K question by testing whether that improved recipe also lowers `gated@64` enough to strengthen the lower-cost part of the frontier."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0046.json:104:    "description": "Continue the active `gated` mainline and keep the improved recipe fixed: `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1`. Change only `K` from `96` to `64` to test whether the new recipe yields a stronger lower-cost deployment point at the next allowed support level. Judge the run by the full trajectory as well as the endpoint: if it stays smooth and finishes materially below the old `gated@64` control (`0.195828`), the improved recipe is genuinely useful beyond the `K=128` anchor; if it falls back toward the old curve, treat the current gain as mainly a high-K effect.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0046.json:105:    "self_review": "This stays on the current mainline family, respects the fixed `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` rule, and changes exactly one primary variable: `K`. It follows the prescribed order because the clean baseline, LR, optimizer, loss, and preprocess questions have already been answered on this recipe, and Round 45 provided positive evidence that the improved reci��该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。最近 r132/r133/r136 在改 AUXK_ALPHA、TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 后得到几乎完全相同的 start/mid/end FVU、tokens_per_sec 与 final_total_tokens，说明当前更需要先补一轮无附加成本轴扰动的 clean baseline，确认主线 reference recipe 的真实曲线与运行代价，再决定下一轮是向上还是向下微调 LR。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 仍复现 0.0581 且晚段仍在改善，则下一轮只下调 LR 到 2.4e-3，测试是否能改善末段收敛。","若 clean baseline 的曲线比近期 archive 更差或更快平台化，则下一轮只上调 LR 到 3.6e-3，测试当前 3.0e-3 是否偏保守。","若 clean baseline 与近期三轮继续完全重合，则说明 recipe 已高度稳定，后续应优先做单变量 LR 扫描而不是继续扫成本侧小参数。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的导出形式未变，仍属扩展兼容，可继续作为 LUTurbo 主线 family。","r132/r133/r136 的 FVU 曲线与吞吐几乎完全一致，近期成本轴小改动没有提供新的可解释信号。","本轮先补 clean baseline，是为了恢复后续 LR 试验的可靠参照，而不是扩大搜索空间。"],"primary_variable":"other_param","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 固定到当前主线参考配方，不引入新的结构改动，也不混入额外 recipe 变量。该动作不追求立刻刷新 FVU，而是先建立可信的 clean baseline，避免在近期多轮零信号的情况下继续做难归因的参数扰动。风险是这一轮可能再次得到与近期相同的结果，但即便如此也能为下一轮 LR 单变量搜索提供干净参照。","summary":"继续主线 family，不开新架构；在已确认 EF=2 成本可行后，先补一轮 exact clean baseline：lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2, signum, LR=3.0e-3，无额外成本侧或 loss 侧改动。目标是确认当前主线配方的真实训练曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，再据此进入单变量 LR 调整。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0174.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_grouped_residual` with `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` fixed. Final reconstruction formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library and `{b_i}` is a static residual dictionary; grouped competition changes only how residual support is selected, not the exported decoder basis. This is `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export it as one static trunk lookup plus one sparse weighted sum over a static residual library, so inference remains a finite weighted sum over fixed vector banks. At EF=2 its encoder selection cost should remain within the `\u2264 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n` hard budget because it reuses the feasible `lowrank_residual` scorer stack and only constrains support selection. The single question is whether group-local residual competition is intrinsically worth keeping in the low-EF deployable regime, or whether even this cheaper selector simplification is clearly inferior to the current two-stage soft-codebook mainline.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0174.json:53:      "Evaluate `tokens_per_sec`, total duration, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU, because LUTurbo cares about total runtime cost rather than FVU alone; a tiny quality change with slower runtime is negative."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0015.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Lowering `AUXK_ALPHA` on the accepted `topk/signum/K128/EF12/LR=1.6e-3` recipe did not improve FVU, which suggests the current K128 recipe is close to saturated on the loss-shaping axis. This round changes only `K`, dropping from `128` to `64` while keeping the same family, optimizer, LR, and EF fixed, to test whether LUTurbo can gain a materially cheaper decomposition point with still-acceptable reconstruction quality on the current best-understood topk recipe.","summary":"Move to the K axis on the stabilized topk mainline: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and set `K=64` to measure the first real quality-cost tradeoff point in the allowed K set.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays within the active `topk` family, changes exactly one primary variable, and follows the repo's own K-coverage guidance once LR and one loss-axis check have been explored. The main risk is a noticeable FVU jump at `K=64`, but that is now the relevant question because LUTurbo cares about total online cost, not only the K128 quality anchor.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"64"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["The aux-loss reduction to `AUXK_ALPHA=0.015625` did not improve the K128 mainline, so the current topk recipe appears near-saturated on that loss axis.","Round 15 begins explicit K tradeoff mapping with `K=64` on the accepted topk/signum/LR1.6e-3/EF12 backbone.","Judge this run against LUTurbo goals, not only raw FVU: the key question is whether `K=64` preserves a tolerable reconstruction curve shape while offering a meaningfully cheaper online decomposition point."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=64` is competitive enough, continue the same lane with `K=32` to map the next cost-quality tradeoff point.","If `K=64` degrades too sharply, keep K128 as the quality anchor and reconsider recipe tuning only if there is a strong new signal.","If `K=64` is borderline but usable, compare its cost-quality position directly against K128 rather than demanding it beat the anchor on FVU alone."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0176.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j`, with the only architectural change versus the mainline being a fixed front-loaded sparse budget split (`stage1_k\u22480.75K`, `stage2_k\u22480.25K`). This is `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9` because LUTurbo can export the low-rank trunk, soft codebook, and residual dictionary as static libraries and execute them in the usual `trunk lookup + codebook lookup + two residual lookups + weighted sum` pipeline. Because this family keeps the same trunk/codebook/residual components as the mainline and only reallocates K across the two residual stages, its encoder selection cost should remain within the same feasible regime as the current mainline rather than triggering policy rejection. The probe answers one question only: at low-cost EF=2, is front-loading the residual budget intrinsically better than the symmetric two-stage split, or should this family be deprioritized.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0176.json:25:    "self_review": "Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes, while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` stay fixed. I am avoiding another clearly over-budget probe and choosing a matched variant that isolates one architectural question while remaining compatible with LUTurbo export and likely feasible under the selection-cost constraint.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0176.json:52:      "This is the cleanest remaining matched architecture probe because it preserves the mainline's static libraries and likely feasible encoder cost, avoiding another likely policy-reject like routed/bucketed variants.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0176.json:56:      "Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune a single cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0176.json:78:    "self_review": "Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes, while `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` stay fixed. I am avoiding another clearly over-budget probe and choosing a matched variant that isolates one architectural question while remaining compatible with LUTurbo export and likely feasible under the selection-cost constraint.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0241.json:22:    "expected_win": "better_fvu_within_low_cost_region",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0209.json:17:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d b_i \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1b\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\u4ecd\u662f\u5355\u6837\u672c top-k \u9009\u62e9\u540e\u7684\u5355\u5e93\u67e5\u8868\u4e0e\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002r208 \u5df2\u8bc1\u660e topk \u5728 EF=1\u3001K=64\u3001total_cost=0.31x \u4e0b\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u4f18\u4e8e\u6b64\u524d factorized_topk \u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u70b9\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u672c\u8f6e\u4fdd\u6301 architecture=topk\u3001EXPANSION_FACTOR=1\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ea\u628a K \u4ece 64 \u63d0\u5230 96\uff0c\u6cbf deployment \u6210\u672c\u8f74\u5728 <0.5x \u533a\u57df\u5185\u6362\u53d6\u66f4\u4f4e FVU\u3002\u9884\u8ba1 deployment cost \u7531\u7ea6 0.06x \u5347\u5230\u7ea6 0.09x\uff0ctotal_cost \u7ea6\u4e3a 0.34x\uff0c\u4ecd\u7a33\u5c45\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u533a\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u6709\u671b\u660e\u663e\u6539\u5584\u5f53\u524d 0.2583 \u7684 FVU\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0209.json:20:    "expected_win": "better_fvu_within_low_cost_region",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0144.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"confirm_baseline","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。经过 r141-r143 的 matched architecture probes 后，当前已经重新确认 two-stage soft-codebook 主线在质量上显著优于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual、lowrank_residual 与 factorized_topk，但这些 probe 的总耗时更短，说明近期运行代价结论可能混杂了架构差异而非主线 recipe 漂移。本轮只回答一个问题：回到主线参考配方 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 做一次 clean baseline 复验，当前 feasible 主线的 FVU、训练曲线、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens 是否仍稳定可复现，从而为后续继续做主线 recipe 调整提供干净锚点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 继续稳定复现 0.0581 附近且运行代价正常，则下一轮继续留在主线 family，优先做一个单变量 recipe 问题而不是继续开 architecture probe。","若 clean baseline 的吞吐或总耗时明显恶化而 FVU 不变，则优先把这视为运行时信号，而不是误判为主线架构退化。","若 clean baseline 本身出现曲线漂移或终点退化，则先重新建立主线锚点，再决定是否进入 LR 或成本轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍是当前兼容 frontier 上质量最强的可行主线，导出形式未变，继续属于扩展兼容。","r141-r143 三个 matched architecture probes 已把更简化候选的质量下界看清：单阶段 soft-codebook、plain lowrank residual、factorized_topk 都未超过当前主线。","在 probe 轮次后先补 clean baseline，有助于分离架构差异与近期运行代价波动，避免后续 recipe 归因失真。"],"primary_variable":"clean_baseline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：本轮不新开 family，不改 K、EF、optimizer、LR，也不混入额外成本轴或 loss 轴变量，只做主线 clean baseline 复验。该动作符合当前推荐顺序：EF 已确认在预算内，且经过连续架构探针后，先恢复可信主线锚点比直接继续调 recipe 更稳。风险是这一轮可能再次得到与现有主线相同的 FVU，但它能提供必要的运行代价参照，避免把架构探针的更短时长误读为主线 recipe 问题。","summary":"回到当前主线参考配方做一次 clean baseline 复验：固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum、LR=3.0e-3，不引入任何新结构或新 recipe，只确认当前 feasible 主线的 FVU、训练曲线与运行代价是否仍稳定可复现。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0009.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`two_stage_residual` has established a new K=128 full frontier point, but the sharp K=64 regression suggests the current prototype may be capacity-limited or too brittle outside its initial setting rather than broadly Pareto-dominant yet. The next informative move is a family-specific stabilization pass at the winning K=128 anchor by increasing expansion factor to 32, testing whether more latent capacity lets the staged residual design convert its structural advantage into another quality gain without changing architecture or optimization.","summary":"Run a `two_stage_residual` proxy stabilization pass at K=128 with `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32`, keeping the current signum/aux-free recipe fixed and changing only expansion factor.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"quality_improve","family_name":"two_stage_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows the winning family rather than abandoning it after one lower-K miss, and it changes exactly one variable on the current best K=128 setup. Risk: the prototype may already be width-saturated and EF=32 may add cost without improving FVU, but this is the cleanest next stabilization read after K=64 regressed sharply.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"two_stage_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"32"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`two_stage_residual` remained a real K=128 winner in full, but its K=64 proxy run regressed badly to 0.2899633552879095, so lower-K transfer is not automatic for this family.","This round begins family-specific stabilization on the winning K=128 anchor by testing whether extra latent capacity improves the staged residual design at fixed optimization settings."],"next_hypotheses":["If `two_stage_residual` with `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32` improves K=128 proxy FVU, promote it to full and continue stabilization around the stronger width.","If EF=32 is flat or worse, test a family-specific sparsity-allocation parameter next rather than continuing generic width sweeps indefinitely.","If quality improves but runtime regresses materially, follow with a targeted performance pass instead of discarding the architecture."],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0019.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Round 18 showed that `topk/signum/LR=1.6e-3/EF=12` at `K=16` still maintained a negative late-phase FVU slope instead of fully stalling, even though dead-feature pressure rose sharply. This round changes only `K`, moving from `16` to `8`, to answer whether the current export-compatible topk recipe can still support one more major cost reduction before reconstruction quality and compensation burden become clearly impractical.","summary":"Continue the active topk low-K boundary search: keep `ARCHITECTURE=topk`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed, and reduce `K` from `16` to `8` to test whether the practical LUTurbo cost-quality frontier extends below `K=16`.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This stays on the active `topk` family, changes exactly one primary variable (`k`), respects the fixed `EF=12` rule and allowed-K set, and follows directly from the observed `K=16` curve shape. The main risk is that `K=8` may push the recipe past the useful regime, but `K=16` still improved through the end rather than hard-plateauing, so the next clean question is whether the true boundary sits at `K=8` or between `8` and `16`.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"K","value":"8"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 18 (`K=16`) reached `FVU=0.3084372282028198`; the late-phase slope remained negative, so training was still improving rather than collapsing early.","At `K=16`, `dead_pct` and `auxk` rose sharply in the late phase, indicating meaningful capacity stress and likely growing reliance on online compensation if K is reduced further.","For LUTurbo, probing `K=8` is now the most informative single-variable action because it directly tests whether the current topk recipe still offers a viable lower-cost deployment point or whether `K=16` is already near the practical floor."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=8` is still usable, run `K=4` to locate the hard lower bound of the current topk/signum regime.","If `K=8` degrades sharply or the late curve nearly flatlines, treat `K=16` as the current practical low-K boundary for this recipe.","If `K=8` is borderline, compare it against `K=16` as a deployment tradeoff point rather than against the K128 anchor alone."],"primary_variable":"k"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0158.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u8be5 family \u7684\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002\u5176\u4e2d U(Vx) \u53ef\u79bb\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{c_m} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 soft-codebook \u5e93\uff0c{b_i} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u4ecd\u662f\u591a\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.25x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002r157 \u5df2\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e EF \u4e3b\u7ebf\u4e0b\u518d\u6b21\u7ed9\u51fa adam \u7684\u7206\u70b8\u6027\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 optimizer \u5206\u652f\u53ef\u89c6\u4e3a\u5df2\u88ab\u660e\u786e\u5173\u95ed\u3002\u6309\u63a8\u8350\u987a\u5e8f\uff0c\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u5e94\u8f6c\u5411 loss/preprocess \u8f74\uff1b\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u56de\u7b54\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 family\u3001EF\u3001K\u3001\u4e3b\u4f18\u5316\u5668\u548c LR \u4e0d\u53d8\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u5b8c\u5168\u53bb\u6389 auxiliary K loss\uff08AUXK_ALPHA=0.0\uff09\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u51cf\u5c11\u5bf9\u4e3b\u91cd\u6784\u76ee\u6807\u7684\u5e72\u6270\uff0c\u5e26\u6765\u66f4\u597d\u7684\u66f2\u7ebf\u5f62\u72b6\u6216\u81f3\u5c11\u786e\u8ba4\u8be5\u8f85\u52a9\u9879\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u53ef\u90e8\u7f72 regime \u4e0b\u5df2\u65e0\u5fc5\u8981\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0158.json:56:      "EF=2 \u4e0b selection_cost \u4ecd\u5728\u9884\u7b97\u5185\uff1b\u672c\u8f6e\u4e0d\u6539 EF\u3001K\u3001TRUNK_RANK\u3001NUM_CODES \u6216\u5176\u4ed6\u6210\u672c\u8f74\uff0c\u53ea\u9694\u79bb auxiliary loss \u6548\u5e94\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0184.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"NUM_CODES","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"pareto_improve","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式仍为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。r182 与 r183 在连续下调 `NUM_CODES` 后仍复现约 0.0581 FVU，说明 coarse codebook 可能还有可压缩冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：将 `NUM_CODES` 进一步下调到 32，是否仍能维持接近当前主线的训练曲线与终点 FVU，同时继续降低 `code_router`、`codebook_matmul` 与 `codebook_deploy` 成本，从而把当前主线点向更低总成本方向推进。","summary":"继续围绕当前主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3`，仅把 `NUM_CODES` 从 64 再降到 32，测试 coarse codebook 是否还能继续压缩而不明显伤害 LUTurbo 可部署质量。","expected_win_reason":"If `NUM_CODES=32` still preserves the curve shape and endpoint, it improves the compatible Pareto point by cutting coarse-branch selection and deployment cost without changing the export formula.","needs_sanity":false,"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 在 `NUM_CODES=32` 下导出路径不变，仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库的有限加权和，因此保持扩展兼容。","r183 若在 `NUM_CODES=64` 下仍复现约 0.0581 FVU，则 coarse codebook 冗余尚未耗尽，继续沿 `NUM_CODES` 轴下探比切换到新 recipe 更符合单变量主线推进。","评估本轮必须同时比较 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，区分是真实结构退化还是近期运行时吞吐波动。"],"next_hypotheses":["若 `NUM_CODES=32` 仍接近当前主线 FVU 且运行代价未显著恶化，可将更小 codebook 视为新的低成本主线并考虑继续下探或回到 clean baseline 复验。","若 `NUM_CODES=32` 明显退化，则说明 coarse branch 容量下限接近 64，下一轮回到 `NUM_CODES=64` 或 `128` 并改测 `TRUNK_RANK`。","若 FVU 基本不变但吞吐再次异常波动，则优先视为运行时噪声，避免把吞吐抖动误判成结构结论。"],"primary_variable":"num_codes","self_review":"本轮严格遵守单变量原则，只继续推进已经给出正面压缩信号的 `NUM_CODES` 轴；family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部保持不变。相比现在转去 `TRUNK_RANK` 或 optimizer，这一步更直接服务于 LUTurbo 总在线成本，因为它同时减少 coarse selector 成本和部署查表成本，并且能回答 coarse codebook 的最小可用规模这一尚未解决的问题。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0095.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"Rounds 92 through 94 suggest the soft-codebook coarse branch is the first recent non-mainline idea with real signal, but the cheaper single-stage selectors (`lowrank_soft_codebook_residual`, `lowrank_grouped_soft_codebook_residual`, `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual`) still did not beat the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128 anchor. The single most informative remaining matched architecture probe is `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual`: it keeps the same LUTurbo-compatible static-library export path, but asks whether a front-loaded sparse budget after codebook projection can preserve most of the quality while shifting more of the work into the earlier coarse correction and reducing reliance on a large second-stage cleanup. This round answers one question only: under the exact matched `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` recipe, is that asymmetric soft-codebook two-stage architecture intrinsically worth any future follow-up, or should the soft-codebook branch be treated as unable to justify more complexity than the current mainline?","summary":"Run one matched architecture probe by switching only `ARCHITECTURE` to `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` while keeping `K=128`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` fixed.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"This stays within the round policy: one probe, one primary variable, allowed `K`, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` is explicit. I am choosing the asymmetric soft-codebook two-stage variant over routed, whitened, or bucketed alternatives because it is the simplest remaining probe that still targets LUTurbo-relevant execution structure rather than adding extra selector or preprocessing machinery. The main risk is that it still inherits more moving parts than the mainline, so only a clearly strong curve would justify keeping this branch alive.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"2.0e-3"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 95 spends the single allowed matched architecture probe on `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` against the exact `lowrank_two_stage_residual` K128/EF12/signum/LR=2.0e-3 anchor.","Interpret this strictly as a family-worthiness test for whether the promising soft-codebook branch becomes more deployment-relevant when the sparse budget is front-loaded into the first refinement pass rather than split more evenly across two stages.","Return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome; do not open another new family immediately after this probe."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` is clearly weaker than the matched `lowrank_two_stage_residual` anchor and not better than the earlier soft-codebook probes, close the asymmetric soft-codebook branch and resume mainline tuning next round.","If `lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` stays surprisingly close, record it as a reserve branch with a more deployment-friendly stage allocation, but still return to `lowrank_two_stage_residual` next round per probe policy."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0152.json:57:      "\u82e5 topk \u5728\u5927\u5e45\u66f4\u4f4e selection_cost \u4e0b\u4ecd\u4e0e\u4e3b\u7ebf\u63a5\u8fd1\uff0c\u5219\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u590d\u6742\u7ed3\u6784\u7684\u603b\u6210\u672c\u4f18\u52bf\u9700\u8981\u91cd\u65b0\u5ba1\u89c6\uff0c\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u6309\u89c4\u5219\u56de\u5230\u4e3b\u7ebf\u540e\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u8003\u8651\u66f4\u8d34\u8fd1\u603b\u6210\u672c\u76ee\u6807\u7684\u7b80\u5355 family\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0180.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_residual_vq` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library, `c_m` is one selected codebook vector from a static coarse library, and the residual term is a weighted sum over a static residual dictionary. This is `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9` because LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors, coarse codebook, and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then run `trunk branch + coarse code lookup + sparse residual lookups + weighted sum` online. The single question for this probe is whether replacing the soft coarse branch with a hard VQ-style coarse branch is worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime. This should stay inside the encoder-cost budget at `EF=2`, so it is likely to produce a real training/runtime signal rather than another policy reject.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0180.json:56:      "Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0180.json:57:      "If `lowrank_residual_vq` underperforms the mainline on FVU or slows training without a compensating runtime/quality benefit, mark hard-VQ coarse branches as not worth continuing in the current low-cost regime."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0202.json:49:      "\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b selection_cost \u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d two-stage \u4e3b\u7ebf\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u5b83\u662f\u68c0\u9a8c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9636\u6bb5 refinement \u662f\u5426\u503c\u5f97\u7684\u6700\u76f4\u63a5\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5bf9\u7167\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0216.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"224"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此兼容性为直接兼容。r214 与 r215 已证明在 EF=1 下沿 K 轴增加查表预算能稳定改善 <0.5x 区域的 FVU，且最新一轮 K=192 反而把总耗时降到 302s，未出现明显吞吐惩罚；因此本轮继续沿同一最短链路 family 只把 K 提到 224，目标是在总成本仍预计约 0.47x、继续留在 <0.5x 区域的前提下，把当前最佳低开销 FVU 从 0.1635 进一步压低，并判断 topk@EF1 的边际收益是否开始接近饱和。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 topk@EF1,K224 继续明显改善 FVU 且吞吐未恶化，则低开销前沿仍可沿 K 轴补一个更高点。","如果 K224 的收益已明显变小或训练代价开始恶化，则说明 EF=1 下继续堆 K 的边际收益接近耗尽，后续应转向新的低成本 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["topk 仍是当前 <0.5x 区域最稳、最短链路、最易导出的直接兼容 family，已连续三次给出可解释的 Pareto 改善。","r215 在 total_cost=0.44x 处把 FVU 压到 0.1635，且运行代价未恶化，因此当前最高信息量单变量仍是 K 轴，而不是回到 repeatedly policy-reject 的 lowrank_factorized_residual param_only。","评估时必须同步比较 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认新增查表预算是否仍值得。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮延续已验证有效的低开销 topk 主线，选择 K=224 而不是直接冲到 256，是为了继续留在 <0.5x 区域内补点，避免过早踩到 0.5x 边界。风险是 K 继续增大后 FVU 收益可能开始递减，但这正是当前需要量化的关键问题。","summary":"继续使用直接兼容的 topk family，固定 EF=1、signum、LR=3e-3，把 K 提到 224，测试是否能在仍低于 0.5x 总成本的前提下，把低开销区最佳 FVU 从 0.1635 进一步压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0172.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_gated_soft_codebook_residual` with `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` fixed. Final reconstruction formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library, `{c_m}` is a static soft-codebook library, and `{b_i}` is a static residual dictionary; the gate only changes single-sample support weighting before top-k, not the exported decoder basis. This is `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export it as one static trunk lookup plus one static codebook lookup plus one sparse weighted sum over a static residual library, so inference still reduces to finite weighted sums over fixed vector banks. At EF=2 its encoder selection cost is expected to remain within the `\u2264 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n` hard budget because it adds one gate scorer on top of the already-feasible `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` path while staying below the current two-stage mainline\u2019s selector complexity. The single question is whether the soft-codebook coarse branch remains worthwhile with a cheaper gated single-stage selector, or whether the current two-stage refinement is still clearly necessary.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0172.json:53:      "Evaluate with `tokens_per_sec`, total duration, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU, because LUTurbo cares about total runtime cost rather than FVU alone; small quality changes with noticeably worse runtime are negative."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0230.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM","value":"96"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family: factorized_topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；低秩 factorized scorer 只参与单样本在线打分与 top-k 选择，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 r219 只改一个 env 参数 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`K=256`、`signum`、`LR=0.003` 及其余配置不变，测试把 scorer 链路从默认宽 hidden 大幅压缩后，是否能把该 family 的 total_cost 压到约 0.40x，同时仍靠满查表支持预算获得明显优于当前低成本 topk 前沿的 FVU。这个方向的价值在于它直接回答当前阶段最重要的低开销问题之一：更短的选择链路是否能在不牺牲 LUTurbo 可导出性的前提下，形成比 plain topk 更好的 cost-FVU 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 在约 0.40x 成本处把 FVU 压到优于当前 `topk@0.44x` 的 0.16352，且 tokens_per_sec 或总时长没有显著恶化，则继续相对本轮单变量下探 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=64`，寻找更低 encoder 成本拐点。","如果质量仅接近 `topk@0.38x` 到 `topk@0.44x` 区间，但运行代价明显更优，则保留 factorized_topk 作为更便宜的直兼容备选，并再做一次同 family 的单变量 K 轴映射。","如果 FVU 仍明显差于同成本或邻近成本 topk，或训练没有带来预期的系统收益，则关闭 factorized_topk 的低秩 scorer 主线，把注意力转回其他低成本 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["r229 已证明 jumprelu 在更低 K 处虽然还能微弱压过同区间 topk，但 tokens_per_sec 掉到 66.6k，说明继续沿该支线下探的系统性价比开始变差。","当前 round 230 更高价值的动作不是继续在 jumprelu 上做小步延伸，而是重新打开一个天然低 encoder 成本、且完全符合 LUTurbo 单库导出契约的 factorized scorer 方向。","本地 `selection_cost_estimate()` 显示 `factorized_topk@EF1,K256,FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96` 的 combined_ratio 约为 0.40x，远低于默认宽 scorer 配置，正好落在当前重点搜索区间。"],"reference_round":219,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r219 只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，不联动 architecture、K、EF、optimizer、LR 或其他参数。选择切回 factorized_topk 而不是继续沿 jumprelu 的 K 轴下探，是因为 r229 已经暴露出“极小 FVU 收益换来显著更慢训练”的负面系统信号；与其继续消耗在高 K 依赖支线上，不如用一次更短选择链路的 clean probe 去回答当前低开销阶段更核心的问题。主要风险是低秩 scorer 压缩后质量仍会明显不足，但这正是本轮要以最小单变量代价验证的科学问题。","summary":"相对 r219 的 `factorized_topk@EF1,K256` 做一次严格 param_only 低秩 scorer 探针，仅设置 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=96`。目标是在约 0.40x 总成本处检验 factorized scorer 路线能否以更短选择链路换回足够的质量，从而为 `<0.5x` 区域补出新的低成本 Pareto 候选。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0142.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 architecture 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 low-rank trunk 基库 U 与 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。相较当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，它同时去掉 soft codebook coarse branch 与第二阶段 residual refinement，但仍保持静态向量库上的有限加权和形式；在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 约 0.62x h×n，显著低于当前主线的约 1.25x，且满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，同时部署成本也更低。r141 已经表明仅去掉第二阶段但保留 soft codebook 时，FVU 会从 0.0581 回退到 0.0647，因此本轮只回答一个更直接的 matched architecture probe 问题：在 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全不变时，当前主线的 soft codebook coarse branch 本身是否仍值得保留，还是更简化的 lowrank_residual 已能提供更优的系统级 cost-FVU 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_residual 在更低 selection_cost 与 deploy cost 下仅有有限 FVU 损失，则保留它作为更激进的 LUTurbo 成本侧候选，但下一轮按策略回到主线 family。","若 lowrank_residual 的 FVU 明显落后于 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 与 two-stage 主线，则说明 soft codebook coarse branch 在 EF=2 下仍然必要，后续不再继续简化该主干。","若 lowrank_residual 训练吞吐或总耗时没有优势，且质量又明显更差，则将其视为负面架构信号，只保留历史参考价值，不再占用后续 probe 轮次。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 Round 142 唯一允许的 matched architecture probe，严格保持 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变，只改 architecture。","r141 已证明 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 相比 two-stage 主线存在明确质量差距，因此本轮改测更简化父节点 lowrank_residual，直接判断 soft codebook 分支本身的必要性。","评估时必须同时比较 FVU、selection_cost、deploy cost、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免只按终点 SAE 指标判断架构价值。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"遵守单变量原则与本轮 probe 约束：只改 architecture，未联动 K、EF、optimizer、LR 或其他 recipe。选择 lowrank_residual 作为 probe，是因为 r141 已给出单阶段 soft-codebook 父节点的直接对照，本轮继续向上剥离 coarse branch 可以最干净地回答“soft codebook 本身是否值得”这一剩余架构问题。风险是该 probe 很可能在 FVU 上进一步落后，但这正是判断当前主线结构必要性的直接证据。","summary":"继续执行一个严格匹配的架构探针：把当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成更简化的父节点 lowrank_residual，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一次干净对照判断 soft codebook coarse branch 在当前低成本 regime 下是否仍值得保留。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0061.json:20:    "summary": "Run one matched architecture probe on `routed`. Keep the current mainline recipe fixed at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, `USE_HADAMARD=1`, and the same runtime knobs, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `gated` to `routed`. Judge this probe by the whole trajectory, not just the endpoint: if `routed` stays smooth and lands near the `0.142923` `gated` anchor, it is worth keeping in reserve because decoupled routing may offer a better LUTurbo cost/quality tradeoff than full gating; if it is clearly worse across the curve, archive it as a non-promising matched alternative and return to the `gated` mainline next round.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0061.json:25:    "self_review": "This obeys the Round 61 matched-probe rule by changing exactly one primary variable, `architecture`, while keeping `K`, `OPTIMIZER`, `LR`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, and the settled mainline recipe fixed. `routed` is the highest-value remaining probe because it stays very close to the successful `gated` family while changing only the support-selection mechanism, which is directly relevant to LUTurbo online cost. The main risk is that the matched `gated`-tuned recipe may not be ideal for routed support, but that is acceptable for a family-worthiness screen.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0061.json:85:      "If matched `routed` is roughly competitive with a healthy curve, still return to the `gated` mainline next round, but preserve one later revisit because decoupled routing may better align with LUTurbo online-cost goals.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0061.json:105:    "description": "Run one matched architecture probe on `routed`. Keep the current mainline recipe fixed at `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, `USE_HADAMARD=1`, and the same runtime knobs, and change only `ARCHITECTURE` from `gated` to `routed`. Judge this probe by the whole trajectory, not just the endpoint: if `routed` stays smooth and lands near the `0.142923` `gated` anchor, it is worth keeping in reserve because decoupled routing may offer a better LUTurbo cost/quality tradeoff than full gating; if it is clearly worse across the curve, archive it as a non-promising matched alternative and return to the `gated` mainline next round.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0061.json:106:    "self_review": "This obeys the Round 61 matched-probe rule by changing exactly one primary variable, `architecture`, while keeping `K`, `OPTIMIZER`, `LR`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, and the settled mainline recipe fixed. `routed` is the highest-value remaining probe because it stays very close to the successful `gated` family while changing only the support-selection mechanism, which is directly relevant to LUTurbo online cost. The main risk is that the matched `gated`-tuned recipe may not be ideal for routed support, but that is acceptable for a family-worthiness screen.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0246.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0192.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk 项 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库上的加权和，soft codebook 分支 Σ_m pi_m c_m 可导出为静态 codebook 库上的加权和，residual 分支 Σ_i alpha_i b_i 可导出为静态 residual 字典上的稀疏加权和，因此能够映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的条件下，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 以更低 encoder selection cost（frontier 已显示约 0.75x vs 主线 1.25x）有望提供值得保留的 cost/FVU 点；若其 FVU 明显落后，则说明 two-stage refinement 本身值得继续保留。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若该 probe 明显劣于主线，则下一轮回到 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK、NUM_CODES 或 STAGE1_RATIO。","若该 probe 在更低 selection_cost 下接近主线且训练更快，可把 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 作为低成本支线继续做单轴清洗。","继续避免 routed 与 bucketed matched probe，因为在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 约 2.25x h×n，会被预算约束卡住。"],"notes_to_memory":["r191 的 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 提案被 policy_reject，原因是用 param_only 承载架构切换；同一假设应以 architecture 类型重提。","本轮严格 matched：只改 architecture，其余保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3。","该 family 为扩展兼容，导出路径是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这是对 r191 被 policy 拦截的同一科学问题做合法重提，不引入第二主变量。相比继续试 grouped/gated/asymmetric 的兄弟结构，one-stage parent 能更直接回答 two-stage 增益是否值得其额外选择成本；同时它已在当前 frontier 上显示为可行兼容点，信息增益和可解释性都足够。","summary":"执行一个合法的 matched architecture probe：将主线从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 切到 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。该架构的最终重构可导出为 trunk 静态库、soft codebook 静态库和 residual 静态字典上的有限加权和，属扩展兼容；本轮只回答一个问题，即去掉第二阶段 residual refinement 后，这个 family 是否仍值得继续保留为低成本 LUTurbo 候选。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0152.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"该 matched probe 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主线参考配方一致，仅把 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 改为 topk，这一轮只回答一个问题：在当前低 EF 预算内，若去掉 low-rank trunk、soft-codebook coarse branch 与 two-stage refinement，只保留最朴素的单库稀疏选择，重构质量会退化到什么程度，从而判断当前主线复杂结构是否确实提供了值得继续投入的架构价值。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 topk 在大幅更低 selection_cost 下仍与主线接近，则说明当前主线复杂结构的总成本优势需要重新审视，下一轮按规则回到主线后应优先考虑更贴近总成本目标的简单 family。","若 topk 明显更差，则说明当前主线的 low-rank trunk + soft-codebook + staged refinement 组合在 EF=2 下仍有真实结构价值，下一轮回到主线继续做单变量 recipe 或成本轴工作。","若 topk 更快但质量远差，则把它保留为低成本 sanity baseline，不再继续占用主线轮次。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是单次 matched architecture probe，严格只改 architecture，其余 K、EF、optimizer、LR 全部与主线参考配方一致。","topk 为直接兼容 family，不属于不兼容候选，可合法作为兼容 frontier 的架构对照。","r150 与 r151 已经表明去掉 second stage 或去掉 soft-codebook 后 FVU 都明显变差；本轮进一步测试最简单单库 baseline，可帮助量化当前主线相对朴素 LUTurbo 兼容方案的真实结构增益。","评估时必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，区分更高吞吐是否只是来自结构更简单而非更优的总成本-质量权衡。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"遵守本轮架构探针规则：只改 architecture，保持主线的 K、OPTIMIZER、LR、EXPANSION_FACTOR 与主要 recipe 不变。相比重复已明显落后的近邻 family，这个 probe 提供了最强的低成本下界对照，能更清楚回答当前主线复杂结构是否值得继续。","summary":"执行一次严格 matched architecture probe：把当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成最简单的 topk，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断当前主线复杂结构相对直接兼容单库方案是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/06_20260320_183226/round_summaries/round_0008.json:87:      "If the quality gain is real but runtime or memory regresses, keep the direction and follow with a targeted cost/perf pass afterward."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0187.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"8"}],"expected_win":"pareto_improve","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 仍满足 ≤1.5×h×n 硬约束。r133 的 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 与 r186 的 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 都未伤害终点 FVU，说明 trunk 容量可能仍有可压缩冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：将 `TRUNK_RANK` 进一步下调到 8，是否仍能保持接近当前主线的训练曲线与终点 FVU，同时继续降低 trunk 相关的 encoder 选择成本与部署查表成本，从而把兼容 Pareto 点继续推向更低总成本。","summary":"继续围绕同一主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, K=128, EF=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3`，仅把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 16 再降到 8，测试更激进的 trunk 压缩是否仍能维持当前 LUTurbo 可部署质量。","needs_sanity":false,"notes_to_memory":["family 与导出路径不变，`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 在 `TRUNK_RANK=8` 下仍是扩展兼容：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + two-stage residual 字典库的有限加权和。","`TRUNK_RANK=32` 与 `16` 都复现了约 0.0581 FVU，因此继续沿 trunk 容量轴下探比回到已多次无增益的 codebook 轴更有信息价值。","评估本轮必须同时比较 curve_start/mid/end、tokens_per_sec、总耗时与 final_total_tokens，确认收益来自真实成本下降而不是运行时漂移。"],"next_hypotheses":["若 `TRUNK_RANK=8` 仍接近当前主线 FVU 且吞吐不恶化，可将更低 rank 视为新的低成本主线，并考虑一次 clean baseline 复验来确认曲线稳定性。","若 `TRUNK_RANK=8` 明显退化，则说明 trunk 容量下限更接近 16，下一轮回到 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 并转向 `NUM_CODES` 或其他单一成本轴。","若终点接近但吞吐显著变差，则把更低 trunk rank 视为负面系统信号，而不是仅凭 FVU 保留。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"本轮严格遵守单变量原则：family、EF、K、optimizer、LR 全部固定，只推进 `TRUNK_RANK` 这一直接作用于 encoder 选择成本和部署 trunk 成本的主变量。相比现在切回高风险的 optimizer 分支，这一步更稳、更可归因，也更贴近 LUTurbo 的真实总成本目标。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family: lowrank_factorized_residual。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r beta_r u_r + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {u_r} 是 trunk 静态向量库、{b_i} 是 residual 静态向量库；factorized residual scorer 只影响在线选择与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端导出形态，因此可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。基于 r210 已证明该 family 在 K=64、EF=1 下能以 0.69x 拿到 0.1256 FVU，当前主矛盾是 trunk 成本过高而不是训练质量不足；本轮严格锚定 r210，只改一个主轴 TRUNK_RANK，从 auto≈256 下调到 32，测试是否能把 total_cost 明确压入 <0.5x 区域，同时尽量保留明显优于同成本 topk 的 FVU。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:20:    "summary": "相对 r210 的 lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1 做一次严格 param_only 成本压缩，只下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，优先验证能否把该高质量 family 推入 total_cost < 0.5x 区域。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0220.json:82:    "description": "相对 r210 的 lowrank_factorized_residual@K64,EF1 做一次严格 param_only 成本压缩，只下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，优先验证能否把该高质量 family 推入 total_cost < 0.5x 区域。 [INVALID: launcher did not forward TRUNK_RANK; checkpoint config kept sae.trunk_rank=null, so this result cannot be used to judge TRUNK_RANK=32]",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0241.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"64"}],"expected_win":"better_fvu_within_low_cost_region","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"frontier_mapping","hypothesis":"候选 family: topk。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；在线侧只做单样本 top-k 选择与系数计算，部署侧仍是单库查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。相对 reference_round=r240 只改一个 env 参数 `K=64`，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=topk`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=signum`、`LR=0.003`、`AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` 及其余配置不变，测试左端低成本前沿从 `K=32 -> 48 -> 56` 的连续改善是否会平滑延续到已有锚点 `K=64`，并在约 0.31x 总成本处对这段 Pareto 斜率做一次干净确认。选择这一步而不是继续补更细中间点或切回已给出负信号的新 family，是因为 r240 已满足当前开放假设的前半条件：`K56` 明显优于 `K48`，且总时长继续下降；当前最高信息量的问题是这条左侧 topk 前沿能否无缝回接到既有 `K64` 质量锚点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `topk@EF1,K64` 复现或优于现有 0.31x 点的 FVU=0.2583，且 `tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens` 没有明显恶化，则可停止对 `K32-64` 区间的细密映射，把注意力转回 `0.31x-0.38x` 之间更稀疏的缺口。","如果 `K64` 明显劣于现有锚点或运行代价异常，则说明左端序列存在较强噪声或阶段性不可比因素，后续应优先做 clean repeat 而不是继续沿 K 轴外推。","如果质量改善存在但运行显著更慢，则按运行时优先级将其记为负面系统信号，不把该配方升格为左侧前沿确认点。"],"notes_to_memory":["r238 和 r239 已证明 plain `topk` 主导 `<0.31x` 左端低成本前沿；r240 进一步表明从 `K48` 到 `K56` 的改进不仅存在，而且运行代价没有恶化。","当前更高信息量的问题不是再开新 family，而是确认这条左侧 topk 前沿是否能平滑回接到既有 `K64` 锚点，从而完成 `0.28x-0.31x` 区间的闭环。","评估本轮必须同时比较 `val_fvu`、`tokens_per_sec`、`duration_sec`、`final_total_tokens`；若只是轻微质量收益但运行明显更慢，应直接视为负面信号。"],"reference_round":240,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对 r240 只改 `K`，不联动 architecture、EF、LR、optimizer、AUXK_ALPHA 或任何新参数。主要风险是 `K64` 已有历史点，本轮可能只得到重复信息；但在左端低成本序列刚形成连续正信号的情况下，这个 clean confirm 的信息价值高于继续做更细碎的局部插值或重开已证伪 family。","summary":"相对 r240 的 `topk@EF1,K56` 做一次严格 param_only 左端确认，仅设置 `K=64`，验证左侧低成本 topk 前沿是否能平滑回接到已有 0.31x 锚点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0120.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"96"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。low-rank trunk、soft codebook、两阶段 residual 都是静态向量库上的有限加权和，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；该 family 属于扩展兼容。当前 EF=2 已稳定满足 encoder 选择成本硬约束，而最近几轮在同一 family 上做 LR、optimizer、auxiliary loss 清洗都未带来进一步改进，其中 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 还把总时长拉高到 541s 但 FVU 仍停在 0.058106，属于负面信号。按主线顺序，recipe 轴已基本看清，本轮只改一个主变量 `K`，将 `K` 从 128 降到 96，回答唯一问题：在保持相同 encoder 选择成本的前提下，能否用更低的部署查表成本换取可接受的 FVU，从而更接近 LUTurbo 的总在线成本目标。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=96` 只带来很小 FVU 退化但明显降低部署查表成本，则继续沿 K 轴向下小步搜索。","如果 `K=96` 的 FVU 明显恶化，则关闭 K 降低分支，保留 `K=128` 作为该 family 在 EF=2 下的主线配置。","评估时同时比较曲线形状、`tokens_per_sec`、总耗时、`final_total_tokens`，区分性能变化来自训练吞吐还是表示能力下降。"],"notes_to_memory":["兼容性判断：`lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` 为扩展兼容；导出形式不变，仍是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","`K` 不影响 encoder 选择成本，因此本轮不会触碰 1.5x 选择成本硬约束；变化只体现在部署查表成本与表示预算之间的权衡。","最近 loss/preprocess 清洗未见收益且出现更长耗时，主线现在应转向更贴近 LUTurbo 总成本目标的 `K` 轴。"],"primary_variable":"k","self_review":"这符合当前优先级顺序。EF 已确认在预算内，clean baseline、LR、optimizer、loss/preprocess 已做过一轮清理且没有继续改进，因此现在才动 `K`。只改 `K` 一项，归因清晰；同时这一步直接对应 LUTurbo 的部署查表成本，而不是继续在已停滞的训练轴上空转。","summary":"保持 `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual / EF=2 / signum / LR=3.0e-3` 主线不变，仅将 `K` 从 `128` 下调到 `96`，测试在不改变 encoder 选择成本的前提下，是否能用更低部署查表成本换取可接受的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0208.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d b_i \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1b\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\u4ecd\u662f\u5355\u6837\u672c top-k \u9009\u62e9\u540e\u7684\u5355\u5e93\u67e5\u8868\u4e0e\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002r207 \u8868\u660e\u5728\u76f8\u540c K=64\u3001EF=2 \u4e0b\uff0ctopk \u7684 FVU \u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e factorized_topk\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e <0.5x \u533a\u57df\u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u74f6\u9888\u5f88\u53ef\u80fd\u6765\u81ea scorer factorization \u800c\u975e\u7eaf\u9884\u7b97\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u4fdd\u6301 architecture=topk\u3001K=64\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ea\u628a EXPANSION_FACTOR \u4ece 2 \u964d\u5230 1\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u538b\u4f4e encoder selection cost\uff0c\u76ee\u6807\u662f\u5728\u8fdb\u5165 <0.5x \u533a\u57df\u7684\u540c\u65f6\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u975e factorized \u5355\u5e93 baseline \u80fd\u5426\u62ff\u5230\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e factorized_topk@0.44x \u7684 FVU\u3002\u6309\u6210\u672c\u8868\u7ebf\u6027\u5916\u63a8\uff0cselection cost \u7ea6\u53ef\u4ece 0.50x \u964d\u5230 0.25x\uff0ctotal_cost \u7ea6\u843d\u5728 0.31x\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0208.json:22:    "expected_win": "enter_low_cost_region_with_stronger_baseline",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0047.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 46 answered the `K=64` transfer question positively: the strengthened `gated` recipe (`signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `USE_HADAMARD=1`) did not merely hold up, it materially improved the prior `gated@64` result and now owns the frontier at that support. The next single question is where this downward transfer breaks for LUTurbo-relevant cost reduction: if we keep the same improved recipe fixed and reduce only `K` to `32`, does `gated` remain competitive enough to establish a stronger lower-cost point, or does the family advantage collapse below the high-K regime?",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0047.json:20:    "summary": "Continue the active `gated` mainline and keep the improved recipe fixed: `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1`. Change only `K` from `64` to `32` to test whether the recipe improvement extends one more step down the allowed support ladder. Judge the run by the full trajectory as well as the endpoint: if training remains smooth and finishes clearly below the current `K=32` control (`0.249427`), then `gated` has earned a meaningful lower-cost foothold; if the curve degrades sharply or the endpoint lands near or above the control, treat the current `gated` advantage as largely confined to `K>=64`.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0047.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0047.json:25:    "self_review": "This stays on the active `gated` family, respects the fixed `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` rule, and changes exactly one primary variable: `K`. It follows the current mainline logic because the clean baseline, LR, optimizer, loss, and preprocess questions have already been resolved on this recipe, and the last two rounds showed successful transfer from `K=128` to `K=96` and then to `K=64`. The main risk is that `K=32` may sit beyond the range where the improved gating recipe is effective, but that is precisely the highest-value remaining single-variable question for mapping LUTurbo-relevant cost-quality tradeoffs.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0047.json:80:      "Round 47 isolates the next cost-quality question by testing whether the same recipe remains effective at `K=32`, where LUTurbo online cost would drop further but support pressure becomes much tighter."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0047.json:104:    "description": "Continue the active `gated` mainline and keep the improved recipe fixed: `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1`. Change only `K` from `64` to `32` to test whether the recipe improvement extends one more step down the allowed support ladder. Judge the run by the full trajectory as well as the endpoint: if training remains smooth and finishes clearly below the current `K=32` control (`0.249427`), then `gated` has earned a meaningful lower-cost foothold; if the curve degrades sharply or the endpoint lands near or above the control, treat the current `gated` advantage as largely confined to `K>=64`.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0047.json:105:    "self_review": "This stays on the active `gated` family, respects the fixed `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` rule, and changes exactly one primary variable: `K`. It follows the current mainline logic because the clean baseline, LR, optimizer, loss, and preprocess questions have already been resolved on this recipe, and the last two rounds showed successful transfer from `K=128` to `K=96` and then to `K=64`. The main risk is that `K=32` may sit beyond the range where the improved gating recipe is effective, but that is precisely the highest-value remaining single-variable question for mapping LUTurbo-relevant cost-quality tradeoffs.",
research/history_archive/06_20260320_183226/round_summaries/round_0009.json:90:      "If the matryoshka run helps quality but hurts throughput, keep it as a quality lead and follow with a targeted cost/perf cleanup later."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0201.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"}],"expected_win":"clarify_frontier","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"active_baseline_probe","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe under the fixed mainline recipe. Final reconstruction formula is x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i. This is LUTurbo 扩展兼容 because the low-rank trunk term U(Vx) can be exported as a static trunk vector library, the soft codebook term Σ_m pi_m c_m uses a static codebook library, and the sparse residual term Σ_i alpha_i b_i uses a static residual dictionary, so LUTurbo/Lottable inference remains static lookup plus weighted summation plus optional residual compensation. Holding K=128, EXPANSION_FACTOR=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, and LR=3.0e-3 fixed, this probe isolates whether the second residual refinement stage in lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual is actually buying enough FVU to justify its extra encoder selection cost and runtime overhead in the feasible low-EF regime.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual mainline next round as required by policy.","If lowrank_soft_codebook_residual is close in FVU while materially faster or cheaper at the same K/EF recipe, treat the second residual stage as weak value in the current LUTurbo-compatible regime."],"notes_to_memory":["Compatibility label: 扩展兼容.","This is a parent-family matched probe, not a new incompatible line: same trunk+codebook decomposition, only removes the second sparse refinement branch.","Selection-cost rationale: this family is comfortably feasible at EF=2 and materially cheaper than the two-stage parent, making it the cleanest architecture-only test of whether stage-2 refinement is worth keeping.","Judge the result using both FVU and runtime counters (tokens_per_sec, total wall time, final_total_tokens), because recent rounds show meaningful throughput drift."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This obeys the one-variable rule and avoids the previously policy-rejected asymmetric candidate. It is the most informative matched probe because it differs from the current mainline by exactly one structural element: the existence of the second residual stage. More distant probes like factorized_topk or lowrank_residual answer broader questions but are less diagnostic for the current mainline family.","summary":"Probe ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_soft_codebook_residual with the mainline K=128, EF=2, signum, LR=3.0e-3 recipe unchanged. This directly tests whether the extra second-stage residual refinement in the current mainline is worth its added online selection cost and runtime in the LUTurbo-compatible low-EF setting.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0144.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002low-rank trunk \u57fa\u5e93 U\u3001soft codebook \u9759\u6001\u5e93 {c_m}\u3001\u4ee5\u53ca\u4e24\u9636\u6bb5 residual \u9759\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u5e93 {b_i} \u90fd\u53ef\u79bb\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u6620\u5c04\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u65f6 encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.25x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002\u7ecf\u8fc7 r141-r143 \u7684 matched architecture probes \u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d\u5df2\u7ecf\u91cd\u65b0\u786e\u8ba4 two-stage soft-codebook \u4e3b\u7ebf\u5728\u8d28\u91cf\u4e0a\u663e\u8457\u4f18\u4e8e lowrank_soft_codebook_residual\u3001lowrank_residual \u4e0e factorized_topk\uff0c\u4f46\u8fd9\u4e9b probe \u7684\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u66f4\u77ed\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u8fd1\u671f\u8fd0\u884c\u4ee3\u4ef7\u7ed3\u8bba\u53ef\u80fd\u6df7\u6742\u4e86\u67b6\u6784\u5dee\u5f02\u800c\u975e\u4e3b\u7ebf recipe \u6f02\u79fb\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u56de\u7b54\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u56de\u5230\u4e3b\u7ebf\u53c2\u8003\u914d\u65b9 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual\u3001K=128\u3001EF=2\u3001signum\u3001LR=3.0e-3 \u505a\u4e00\u6b21 clean baseline \u590d\u9a8c\uff0c\u5f53\u524d feasible \u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684 FVU\u3001\u8bad\u7ec3\u66f2\u7ebf\u3001tokens_per_sec\u3001\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u4e0e final_total_tokens \u662f\u5426\u4ecd\u7a33\u5b9a\u53ef\u590d\u73b0\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u4e3a\u540e\u7eed\u7ee7\u7eed\u505a\u4e3b\u7ebf recipe \u8c03\u6574\u63d0\u4f9b\u5e72\u51c0\u951a\u70b9\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0045.json:19:    "hypothesis": "Round 44 cleanly reproduced the Hadamard-enabled `gated` improvement at `K=128`, so that preprocess gain is now stable enough to treat as the operative recipe rather than a one-off. The next single question is therefore K transfer under the improved recipe: if we keep `gated`, `signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `EF=12`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1` fixed and step down only to `K=96`, does the stronger recipe preserve or extend `gated`'s advantage at the next lower support where online cost is meaningfully lower?",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0045.json:20:    "summary": "Adopt the reproduced Hadamard recipe as the current `gated` reference and begin K mapping under that stronger setting. Keep `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1` fixed, and change only `K` from `128` to `96`. Judge the run by the whole trajectory as well as the endpoint: if the improved recipe yields a smooth curve and clearly beats the old `gated@96` control (`0.168960`), then the preprocess gain transfers to a lower-cost point and the family deserves at least one more K step; if it falls back toward the earlier K96 result or loses its curve advantage, keep the improved recipe mainly as a K128 anchor.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0045.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0045.json:80:      "Round 45 transfers the improved `gated` recipe to `K=96` to test whether the K128 preprocess gain also buys a better lower-cost point rather than only improving the largest-support anchor."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0045.json:104:    "description": "Adopt the reproduced Hadamard recipe as the current `gated` reference and begin K mapping under that stronger setting. Keep `ARCHITECTURE=gated`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=2.0e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125`, and `USE_HADAMARD=1` fixed, and change only `K` from `128` to `96`. Judge the run by the whole trajectory as well as the endpoint: if the improved recipe yields a smooth curve and clearly beats the old `gated@96` control (`0.168960`), then the preprocess gain transfers to a lower-cost point and the family deserves at least one more K step; if it falls back toward the earlier K96 result or loses its curve advantage, keep the improved recipe mainly as a K128 anchor.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0141.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 architecture 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i。其中 low-rank trunk 基库 U、soft codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。相较当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，它只去掉第二阶段 residual refinement，保持同样的静态导出类别，但把选择成本从约 1.25x 降到约 0.75x h×n，仍满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，同时部署成本维持在当前 frontier 同量级。当前主线已连续 5 轮无改进，因此本轮只回答一个 matched architecture probe 问题：在 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全不变时，第二阶段 residual refinement 在低 EF 可部署 regime 下是否真的值得保留，还是单阶段 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 已经提供更优的系统级 cost-FVU 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 在明显更低 selection_cost 下仅有有限 FVU 损失，则保留它作为更强的 LUTurbo 成本侧候选，但下一轮按策略回到主线 family。","若该 probe 的 FVU 明显落后于 two-stage 主线，则说明第二阶段 refinement 在 EF=2 下仍然值得，下一轮回到 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续主线搜索。","若该 probe 训练更慢或吞吐更差而没有对应质量收益，则将其视为负面架构信号，不再继续扩展该单阶段分支。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 Round 141 唯一允许的 matched architecture probe，严格保持 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变，只改 architecture。","lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 与主线共享 trunk + soft-codebook 导出链路，差异只在是否保留第二阶段 residual refinement，因此信息回报直接对应“第二阶段是否值得”。","评估时必须同时比较 FVU、selection_cost、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免只按终点 SAE 指标判断架构价值。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"遵守单变量原则与本轮 probe 约束：只改 architecture，未联动 K、EF、optimizer、LR 或其他 recipe。选择 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 是因为它是当前主线的最近父节点，导出公式同属扩展兼容且成本显著更低，能最干净地回答“第二阶段 residual refinement 是否值得继续”这个单一问题。风险是该 probe 很可能在 FVU 上不如主线，但这正是本轮架构价值判断所需的直接信号。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：把当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 换成其单阶段父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一次干净对照判断第二阶段 residual refinement 在当前低成本 regime 下是否仍值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0156.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"112"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"smaller_k","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"该 family 的最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、soft-codebook 静态库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 静态字典库 {b_i} 都可离线导出，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 EF=2 下该 family 的 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，仍满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，而 r154-r155 已把 signum 主线 LR 稳定到 3.3e-3。既然 optimizer 分支在 EF=2、同 family 上已出现爆炸性负信号，loss 轴与 TRUNK_RANK=32 也未带来收益，本轮只回答一个更贴近 LUTurbo 总在线成本的问题：在保持 family、EF、optimizer、LR 不变时，仅将 K 从 128 小步下调到 112，能否在明显降低部署查表成本的同时，把 FVU 维持在接近当前 0.05794 的水平，从而形成更优的总成本权衡点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 K=112 仅小幅退化且部署成本改善明显，则继续沿 K 轴小步下探到 104 或 96。","若 K=112 已明显恶化到接近先前 K=96 的趋势，则关闭降 K 分支，保留 K=128 作为该 family 的主线部署点。","若 K=112 几乎不损失 FVU，则将更小 K 升格为新的主线配方，并再评估其曲线与吞吐稳定性。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 继续满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性仍为扩展兼容。","EF=2 下 selection_cost 仍在预算内；本轮改 K 不触碰 encoder 成本硬约束，只改变部署查表成本。","r154-r155 已把 signum@3.3e-3 复验为稳定优于 3.0e-3 的主线 LR。","adam 在该 family/EF=2 上已有爆炸性负信号，AUXK_ALPHA 与 TRUNK_RANK=32 也未显示有效收益；因此当前更高价值的问题是更贴近系统目标的 K 轴成本权衡。","评估本轮必须同时记录 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，确认收益不是由异常训练时长或吞吐波动伪造。"],"primary_variable":"k","self_review":"这轮严格只改一个主变量 K，符合单变量原则，也仍留在当前主线 family。虽然策略顺序通常先看 optimizer，但该分支在同一低 EF regime 已给出强负信号；继续重复低价值 optimizer 试探不如转向更贴近 LUTurbo 总在线成本目标的部署查表成本轴。选择 112 而不是直接回到 96，是为了做更小、更可归因的降 K 台阶，避免一次性损失过多表示能力。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、signum、LR=3.3e-3，仅将 K 从 128 小步下调到 112，测试是否能以更低部署查表成本维持接近当前最佳的 FVU。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/06_20260320_183226/round_summaries/round_0003.json:105:      "If startup still times out, inspect dataset shuffle/select ordering and other pre-step costs in the local artifact path.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0222.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i \u03b1_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_i} \u6765\u81ea\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ea\u505a\u5355\u6837\u672c top-k \u9009\u62e9\u4e0e\u7cfb\u6570\u8ba1\u7b97\uff0c\u90e8\u7f72\u4fa7\u4ecd\u662f\u5355\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e r218 \u5df2\u5728 total_cost=0.49x \u5904\u7ed9\u51fa\u5f53\u524d <0.5x \u533a\u57df\u6700\u4f73 FVU=0.1462\uff0c\u800c\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e\u66f4\u590d\u6742\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u7ed3\u6784 probe\uff08factorized_topk\u3001lowrank_factorized_residual@TRUNK_RANK=32\uff09\u5206\u522b\u7ed9\u51fa\u660e\u663e\u66f4\u5dee FVU\uff0c\u4e14 r221 \u8fd8\u628a\u541e\u5410\u538b\u5230 111k tokens/s\u3001\u603b\u65f6\u957f\u62c9\u5230 760s\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u66f4\u503c\u5f97\u5728\u6700\u5f3a\u4f4e\u5f00\u9500\u951a\u70b9\u4e0a\u505a\u4e0d\u589e\u52a0\u7cfb\u7edf\u6210\u672c\u7684\u5355\u53d8\u91cf recipe \u63a2\u9488\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u951a\u5b9a r218\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5728 EF=1\u3001K=248\u3001\u5b57\u5178\u5bb9\u91cf\u5df2\u5f88\u7d27\u3001\u652f\u6301\u96c6\u5df2\u5f88\u5927\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c regime \u4e0b\uff0c\u53bb\u6389 auxiliary-K loss \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u51cf\u5c11\u5bf9\u4e3b\u91cd\u6784\u76ee\u6807\u7684\u5e72\u6270\uff0c\u5728\u4e0d\u6076\u5316 tokens_per_sec\u3001\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u548c final_total_tokens \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a <0.5x \u524d\u6cbf FVU \u7ee7\u7eed\u538b\u4f4e\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0222.json:22:    "expected_win": "better_fvu_within_low_cost_region",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0222.json:42:      "\u5982\u679c `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` \u660e\u663e\u9000\u5316\uff0c\u5219\u6062\u590d\u9ed8\u8ba4 auxiliary loss\uff0c\u5e76\u5c06 loss \u8f74\u5728\u8be5 low-cost topk \u4e3b\u7ebf\u4e0a\u6682\u65f6\u5173\u95ed\u3002"
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0200.json:23:    "self_review": "This is a strict one-variable matched architecture probe: K, EXPANSION_FACTOR, OPTIMIZER, and LR remain fixed. I am reusing the same candidate as the rejected Round 199 attempt because the scientific question was valid and the rejection appears procedural rather than scientific. Routed and bucketed two-stage soft-codebook variants are intentionally excluded because their EF=2 encoder selection cost exceeds the hard budget and would likely be blocked again.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0200.json:35:      "Feasibility check: this family stays within the 1.5x encoder selection-cost cap at EF=2, unlike routed/bucketed two-stage soft-codebook variants which would be over budget in the matched setting.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0162.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 probe family \u7684\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_i} \u662f\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u56fa\u5b9a\u5411\u91cf\uff0calpha_i \u662f\u5355\u6837\u672c top-k \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u7a00\u758f\u7cfb\u6570\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u6700\u7ec8\u8868\u793a\u662f\u5355\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 0.5x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\uff0c\u5e76\u663e\u8457\u4f4e\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual \u7684\u7ea6 1.25x\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u4fdd\u6301 K=128\u3001EXPANSION_FACTOR=2\u3001OPTIMIZER=signum\u3001LR=3.0e-3 \u4e0e\u4e3b\u8981 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ea\u5c06 architecture \u4ece lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual \u6539\u4e3a topk\uff0c\u56de\u7b54\u552f\u4e00\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e EF \u53ef\u90e8\u7f72 regime \u4e0b\uff0c\u8fd9\u6761\u6700\u6734\u7d20\u3001\u6700\u4f4e\u590d\u6742\u5ea6\u7684\u5355\u5e93\u7a00\u758f\u8def\u7ebf\u662f\u5426\u4ecd\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u5176\u8868\u793a\u80fd\u529b\u4f1a\u660e\u663e\u843d\u540e\u4e8e\u5e26 trunk\u3001soft-codebook \u548c staged refinement \u7684\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7ed3\u6784\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0126.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"},{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_selection_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j，其中 U(Vx) 对应可静态导出的 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，最终仍可落到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，因此兼容性为扩展兼容。当前主线已确认 EF=2 在预算内，而 signum/LR/K 轴最近几轮没有带来改进，本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family、K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变的前提下，下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，能否进一步压低 encoder 选择成本并维持可接受的 FVU，从而得到更优的 Pareto 权衡。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 TRUNK_RANK=32 仅小幅伤害 FVU 但明显降低 selection_cost，则继续沿 trunk_rank 轴补一个中间点以细化 Pareto。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 明显恶化 FVU 且时间收益有限，则恢复默认 trunk 配方，转向 loss/preprocess 轴。","若 TRUNK_RANK=32 同时改善时间与 selection_cost，但 FVU 退化可接受，则把它作为低成本分支保留，不再继续降 K。"],"notes_to_memory":["family 不变，兼容性仍为扩展兼容，导出路径不变：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + residual 字典库。","r125 复现了 K=96 的较差 FVU，说明继续压 K 的回报有限，本轮改测更直接作用于 encoder 成本的 trunk_rank。","评估时必须同时记录 selection_cost、FVU、总耗时、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens，区分收益来自真实算子简化还是训练时长波动。"],"primary_variable":"trunk_rank","self_review":"本轮严格只改一个主变量，并把探索重心从已基本洗净的 signum/LR/K 轴转向更贴近 Pareto 目标的 selection-cost 轴。风险在于 TRUNK_RANK=32 可能过于激进，但它能最快回答该 family 是否还有内部压缩空间。","summary":"保持 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 主线与 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变，仅下调 TRUNK_RANK 到 32，测试是否能以有限 FVU 损失换取更低 encoder 成本和更好的 LUTurbo 总体权衡。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0078.json:25:    "self_review": "This is policy-clean: one matched architecture probe, one primary variable, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` is explicitly pinned. The main tradeoff is that `lowrank_two_stage_residual` likely raises online coefficient cost versus the current mainline, so it is only worth continuing if the FVU gain is material rather than marginal. I am choosing it over another simple selector family because recent matched probes already showed that lighter alternatives are clearly behind the current anchor.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0078.json:81:    "self_review": "This is policy-clean: one matched architecture probe, one primary variable, and `EXPANSION_FACTOR=12` is explicitly pinned. The main tradeoff is that `lowrank_two_stage_residual` likely raises online coefficient cost versus the current mainline, so it is only worth continuing if the FVU gain is material rather than marginal. I am choosing it over another simple selector family because recent matched probes already showed that lighter alternatives are clearly behind the current anchor.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0149.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.3e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，因此最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r145 与 r147 已两次显示 LR=3.3e-3 的终点 FVU=0.0579389，优于 3.0e-3 baseline 的 0.0581064；而 r148 上探到 3.6e-3 后回落到 0.0581512 且总耗时升至 453s，说明继续上调 LR 的收益已不成立，当前更需要回答的单一问题不是继续扩张搜索，而是确认 3.3e-3 这个更优点在当前运行波动下是否仍能以可接受的 tokens_per_sec 与总耗时稳定复现，从而决定是否把它正式视为主线 signum 配方。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 3.3e-3 再次稳定复现更低 FVU，且 tokens_per_sec/总耗时恢复到接近正常区间，则把 3.3e-3 升格为该 family 的 signum 主线 LR。","若 3.3e-3 终点回落到接近 3.0e-3 或继续出现明显慢速，则不要把这点微弱改善视为可靠主线优势，关闭 LR 分支并回到 3.0e-3 参考配方。","若 3.3e-3 终点仍更好但吞吐持续异常偏低，则记录它是质量更优但系统代价更差的 recipe，后续优先转向 optimizer 或其他不增加运行代价的单变量轴。"],"notes_to_memory":["lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的导出形式未变，仍属扩展兼容，可继续作为 LUTurbo 主线 family。","EF=2 继续满足 selection_cost 预算；K 保持 128，避免把部署查表成本变化与 LR 复验混杂。","r148 已给出负面信号：3.6e-3 比 3.3e-3 更差且更慢，因此应关闭 signum 上探分支。","本轮重点不是只看最终 FVU，而是同时核对 tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens，判断 3.3e-3 的微弱质量收益是否值得其真实在线研究成本。"],"primary_variable":"lr","self_review":"遵守单变量原则：只改 LR，family、EF、K、optimizer 全部固定在当前主线 family 上。相比立刻切 optimizer，这一步更稳，因为 3.6e-3 已证明上探失败，而 3.3e-3 虽有两次正信号，但仍需要在近期明显变慢的运行条件下做一次干净复验后，才能决定是否值得结束 LR 分支。","summary":"继续围绕主线 family 推进，不开新 family；在 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual、EF=2、K=128、signum 固定的前提下，把 LR 设回已显示更优终点的 3.3e-3，做一轮干净复验，确认这点改善是否在当前运行代价波动下仍然成立。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0191.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i；其中 low-rank trunk U(Vx)、soft codebook 库 {c_m} 与 residual 字典 {b_i} 都可静态导出到 LUTurbo 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’链路，因此该 family 属于扩展兼容。主假设：在保持 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 完全 matched 的前提下，去掉第二阶段 residual refinement 后，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 仍可能以更低的 encoder 选择成本与更快训练吞吐保住一个有价值的 Pareto 点；若 FVU 明显回退，则说明 stage-2 是当前主线真正有效的结构增益。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若该 probe 的 FVU 仍显著落后于 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual，则下一轮回到主线，只调一个成本轴如 TRUNK_RANK / NUM_CODES / STAGE1_RATIO。","若该 probe 以更低 selection_cost 保持接近 FVU 且训练更快，可把 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 重新视为低成本支线继续做单轴 recipe 清洗。","继续避免 routed / bucketed matched probe at EF=2，因为其 selection_cost 约 2.25x h×n，已超 policy 预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["本轮是 matched architecture probe；除 architecture 外显式保持 K=128、EF=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 不变。","lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 为扩展兼容，导出路径是 trunk 库 + codebook 库 + residual 字典库的有限加权和。","在 EF=2 下，lowrank_soft_codebook_residual 的 selection_cost 约 0.75x h×n，低于主线 two-stage 的 1.25x；routed / bucketed 同配方约 2.25x，当前不可行。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这不是全新 family，信息增益低于真正新结构；但在当前 matched、兼容、且满足成本约束的候选里，它是最干净的 probe。最近的 grouped/gated/asymmetric siblings 已给出负信号，而 routed/bucketed 在 EF=2 被预算拦截，因此本轮用 one-stage parent 来隔离‘第二阶段 residual 是否值得其额外成本’是最可解释的动作。","summary":"执行一个 matched architecture probe：把主线从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 切到其 one-stage 父节点 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual，其余 recipe 保持 K=128 / EF=2 / signum / LR=3.0e-3 不变。该 family 的 LUTurbo 导出公式为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i，属扩展兼容；本轮重点看去掉 stage-2 后，是否能用更低 encoder 选择成本与更快训练代价维持一个值得保留的 Pareto 点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0178.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_gated_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"lowrank_gated_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_gated_residual` under the unchanged mainline recipe (`K=128, EF=2, signum, lr=3.0e-3`). Final reconstruction is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library and the gated selector only changes which residual dictionary atoms `b_i` are activated and with what coefficients. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export the trunk factors and residual dictionary as static vector libraries, then run `trunk branch + gated sparse selection + weighted lookup-sum` online. The architectural question is whether dropping the soft-codebook branch but using a gated residual selector yields a better low-cost tradeoff than the current two-stage soft-codebook mainline. Selection cost should remain within the feasible regime at `EF=2`, so this probe should produce a real training signal rather than another fast policy reject.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["Return to the mainline `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round and tune exactly one cost knob such as `TRUNK_RANK`, `NUM_CODES`, or `STAGE1_RATIO`.","If `lowrank_gated_residual` trails the mainline on FVU and/or slows tokens_per_sec without a compensating benefit, mark the family as not worth continuing in the low-EF feasible regime."],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_gated_residual` is LUTurbo `扩展兼容`: decode is still a finite weighted sum over a static low-rank trunk plus a static residual dictionary; gating only affects selector-side scoring.","This is a useful matched probe because it is likely budget-feasible at `EF=2`, unlike routed/bucketed two-stage variants, and it tests whether the soft-codebook branch is actually necessary in the current low-cost regime.","When evaluating the run, inspect `tokens_per_sec`, wall-clock time, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU; a small FVU gain with materially worse throughput should count as a negative signal."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"Single-variable discipline is preserved: only `ARCHITECTURE` changes, with `K`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR`, `OPTIMIZER`, and `LR` fixed to the mainline recipe. This probe is intentionally chosen to answer a clean architectural question inside the feasible cost band instead of spending another round on an architecture that is likely to be policy-rejected immediately.","summary":"Probe `lowrank_gated_residual` as the one matched architecture change. It is LUTurbo-exportable (`扩展兼容`) through a static low-rank trunk plus static residual dictionary, and it should give a real low-EF signal about whether gated residual selection is worth continuing once the soft-codebook branch is removed.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/06_20260320_183226/round_summaries/round_0004.json:50:    "self_review": "This introduces a new architecture family, so the first proxy result may underperform or show extra compute cost. If it is only marginally better than TopK, it still may not justify promotion given the aggressive goal of roughly halving the current baseline FVU.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0194.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 probe family \u7684\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\uff1b\u5176\u4e2d low-rank trunk \u9879 U(Vx) \u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0cresidual \u5206\u652f \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i \u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b57\u5178\u4e0a\u7684\u7a00\u758f\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u3002factorized scorer \u53ea\u6539\u53d8\u5728\u7ebf\u9009\u62e9\u6253\u5206\u8def\u5f84\uff0c\u4e0d\u6539\u53d8\u6700\u7ec8 decoder \u5f62\u5f0f\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u2018\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u2019\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 K=128\u3001EXPANSION_FACTOR=2\u3001OPTIMIZER=signum\u3001LR=3.0e-3 \u5b8c\u5168 matched \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0clowrank_factorized_residual \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u4ee5\u66f4\u4f4e encoder selection cost\uff08\u7ea6 0.5x h\u00d7n\uff09\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e00\u4e2a\u4ecd\u503c\u5f97\u4fdd\u7559\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u652f\u7ebf\uff1b\u82e5 FVU \u660e\u663e\u52a3\u4e8e lowrank_residual\uff0c\u5219\u8bf4\u660e factorized scorer \u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e EF regime \u4e0b\u635f\u5931\u8fc7\u5927\uff0c\u4e0d\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u4f5c\u4e3a\u4e3b\u7ebf\u517c\u5bb9\u65b9\u5411\u3002",
