research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0161.json:25:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u9075\u5b88\u67b6\u6784\u63a2\u9488\u89c4\u5219\uff0c\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf architecture\uff0c\u5e76\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684 K\u3001EF\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\u3002\u9009\u62e9 factorized_topk \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u518d\u6b21\u91cd\u590d\u5df2\u6d4b\u8fc7\u7684 topk/lowrank \u7236\u8282\u70b9\uff0c\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u7528\u4e00\u6b21\u66f4\u4f4e selection_cost \u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 probe \u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u5269\u4f59\u7684\u5173\u952e\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u6781\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5355\u5e93\u8def\u7ebf\u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u4ef7\u503c\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0161.json:80:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u9075\u5b88\u67b6\u6784\u63a2\u9488\u89c4\u5219\uff0c\u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf architecture\uff0c\u5e76\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7684 K\u3001EF\u3001optimizer\u3001LR \u4e0d\u53d8\u3002\u9009\u62e9 factorized_topk \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u518d\u6b21\u91cd\u590d\u5df2\u6d4b\u8fc7\u7684 topk/lowrank \u7236\u8282\u70b9\uff0c\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u7528\u4e00\u6b21\u66f4\u4f4e selection_cost \u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 probe \u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u5269\u4f59\u7684\u5173\u952e\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u6781\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5355\u5e93\u8def\u7ebf\u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u4ef7\u503c\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0123.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其中 U(Vx) 可导出为静态 trunk 向量库，{c_m} 为静态 soft-codebook 库，{b_i} 为静态 residual 字典库，最终仍是多个静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，因此兼容性为扩展兼容。当前 EF=2 下该 family 的 selection_cost 约 1.25x，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束；而 signum 的 LR 细扫结果显示 3.0e-3 仍优于 2.7e-3 和 2.4e-3，说明 signum 轴基本洗净。本轮只回答一个问题：在保持 family/K/EF 不变的前提下，切换到 adam 并联动使用更保守的 1.0e-3 学习率，测试是否能改善收敛质量，而不是继续在 signum 上做低收益细扫。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 adam@1.0e-3 明显落后且曲线无额外改善趋势，则恢复 signum 为主线并停止继续扫 optimizer。","若 adam@1.0e-3 曲线更平滑但收敛偏慢，可在同一 optimizer 下补一个更高 LR 点如 1.5e-3。","若 adam 与 signum 的最终 FVU 接近但训练时间更长，则把 adam 视为负面信号并回到 K 轴比较 96 vs 128 的系统性价比。"],"notes_to_memory":["family 与导出路径不变，兼容性仍为扩展兼容：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + residual 字典库。","signum 在 K=128、EF=2 下的 LR 细扫已给出负面信号：2.4e-3 和 2.7e-3 都未超过 3.0e-3，因此本轮转入 optimizer 轴。","评估本轮时必须同时记录 FVU、总耗时、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens，判断收益是否来自更优优化而非更长训练。"],"primary_variable":"optimizer","self_review":"遵守了主线推进与兼容性约束，family/K/EF 均保持不变。此轮把 optimizer 作为主变量，并按运行时允许的例外联动 LR 以避免对 adam 使用明显失配的 signum 学习率；风险是 adam 可能在该 regime 下更慢，但这是当前比继续细扫 signum 更有信息量的一步。","summary":"停止继续细扫 signum 学习率，转而在同一可行主线 family 上测试 optimizer 轴：固定 K=128、EF=2，仅切到 adam 并配 1.0e-3 学习率，验证是否存在更好的收敛质量/成本权衡。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0132.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002low-rank trunk \u57fa\u5e93 U\u3001soft codebook \u5e93 {c_m}\u3001\u4e24\u9636\u6bb5 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93 {b_i} \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u7684\u56fa\u5b9a\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u65f6 encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.25x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002\u7531\u4e8e r131 \u7684 optimizer \u5206\u652f\u88ab policy_reject\uff0c\u5148\u505c\u6b62\u7ee7\u7eed\u626b optimizer\uff1b\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u56de\u7b54\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u4e3b\u7ebf baseline\uff08signum, LR=3.0e-3\uff09\u4e0a\u53bb\u6389 auxiliary K loss\uff08AUXK_ALPHA=0.0\uff09\u540e\uff0c\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u6539\u5584\u8bad\u7ec3\u672b\u6bb5\u6536\u655b\u5f62\u72b6\u5e76\u5728\u4e0d\u589e\u52a0\u9009\u62e9\u6210\u672c\u3001\u4e0d\u8fc7\u5ea6\u62d6\u6162 tokens_per_sec/\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\u964d\u4f4e FVU\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0132.json:56:      "EF=2 \u7ee7\u7eed\u6ee1\u8db3 selection_cost \u9884\u7b97\uff1bK \u4fdd\u6301 128\uff0c\u907f\u514d\u628a\u90e8\u7f72\u67e5\u8868\u6210\u672c\u53d8\u5316\u4e0e loss \u8f74\u6df7\u6742\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0164.json:17:    "hypothesis": "Matched architecture probe on lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual with K=128, EF=2, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3 unchanged. Final reconstruction remains x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j, where U(Vx) is a static low-rank trunk library, {c_m} is a static codebook library, and {b_i} is a static residual dictionary; only the stage-1/stage-2 budget split changes to a front-loaded 75/25 allocation. This is \u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9 and exports cleanly to LUTurbo as trunk lookup + codebook lookup + two residual sparse lookups. Because this variant reuses the parent encoder modules, its selection-cost profile should stay matched to the mainline EF=2 point instead of introducing extra router/bucket scorer cost; the probe asks whether front-loading support budget improves low-EF reconstruction enough to justify future tuning.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0164.json:18:    "summary": "Run one matched architecture probe with ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_asymmetric_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual and keep the mainline recipe otherwise unchanged. It preserves LUTurbo-exportable static-library reconstruction and mainline-like selection cost, so the result will answer whether asymmetric budget allocation is worth any continued attention in the current low-EF regime.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0164.json:23:    "self_review": "Upside is bounded because this family only changes a fixed stage split and was not strong historically at higher-EF regimes, so a null result is plausible. Still, it is the cleanest policy-safe matched probe that isolates architecture without confounding cost increases.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0164.json:34:      "Probe choice rationale: matched to the current mainline formula class and likely budget-safe at EF=2, unlike routed/bucketed matched probes which add extra selector layers and risk policy rejection on selection cost.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0087.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0087.json:52:      "Judge this run strictly as a family-worthiness test for a simpler low-rank single-stage gated selector with potentially lower LUTurbo online cost; return to the `lowrank_two_stage_residual` mainline next round regardless of outcome."
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0225.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family: jumprelu。最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i α_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 来自单个静态向量库；JumpReLU 只改变单样本在线侧的阈值化支持形成与系数计算，不改变 decoder 端的单库有限加权和形式，因此可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。r223 已确认 `topk@EF1,K248` 的向上 LR 分支没有收益，r224 也确认 lowrank_factorized_residual 的 scorer 压缩在 <0.5x 目标区仍落后于同成本 topk；因此当前最有信息量的下一步，不是继续清洗已饱和 family 的 recipe，而是在不增加 total_cost 的前提下测试新的同成本 selector 机制。严格锚定 r222，只改一个 env 参数 `ARCHITECTURE=jumprelu`，保留 `EF=1,K=248,signum,LR=3.0e-3,AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 不变，验证 learned-threshold 支持塑形能否在相同 `total_cost≈0.49x` 下，把 <0.5x 区域 FVU 压到当前 topk 最佳 0.1462 以下，或者至少给出比 topk 更有希望的曲线形状而不拖慢训练。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `jumprelu@EF1,K248` 在相同 0.49x 成本下优于 `topk@K248` 的 FVU=0.1462，且 tokens_per_sec / duration_sec 没有明显恶化，则下一轮基于本轮做一次 clean repeat，确认它是否能成为新的 <0.5x 直接兼容锚点。","如果 `jumprelu` 与 topk 质量接近但运行代价更差，则将其仅记录为历史参考，不继续占用低开销主线轮次。","如果 `jumprelu` 明显差于 topk，则关闭这条 plain-selector thresholding 支线，下一轮转向另一条同成本或近邻成本的新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地 `selection_cost_estimate()` 显示 `jumprelu@EF1,K248` 与 `topk@EF1,K248` 的 combined_ratio 同为约 0.49x，因此这是一次纯 selector 机制比较，而不是成本变化导致的混杂实验。","r223 与 r224 分别对 topk recipe 继续清洗、以及 lowrank_factorized_residual scorer 压缩给出负面信号；当前应优先测试新的同成本 family，而不是继续沿这两条线做局部小修。","`jumprelu` 保持单静态库导出契约，属于直接兼容 family；若它也失败，则说明当前 <0.5x 区域里 plain single-library selector 的主导瓶颈更可能是表示容量而非支持塑形规则。"],"reference_round":222,"self_review":"该提案严格遵守单变量原则：相对有效参考轮 r222 只改 `ARCHITECTURE` 一个 env 参数，K、EF、optimizer、LR、AUXK_ALPHA 和所有运行时参数全部保持不变。选择 `jumprelu` 而不是继续回到 topk/group_topk，是因为它在历史上虽未成为主线，但比纯 grouped 竞争更接近“同成本下改变支持塑形”的独立问题，同时不会额外抬高部署或选择成本。","summary":"相对 r222 的 `topk@EF1,K248,AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` 做一次严格 param_only architecture probe，仅切换到 `jumprelu`，测试在相同 0.49x 成本下，阈值化支持塑形是否能把 <0.5x 前沿继续压低。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0155.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002\u5176\u4e2d U(Vx) \u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{c_m} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 soft-codebook \u5e93\uff0c{b_i} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u6700\u7ec8\u4ecd\u662f\u591a\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.25x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002r154 \u5df2\u5728\u6b63\u5e38\u8fd0\u884c\u4ee3\u4ef7\u4e0b\u628a LR=3.3e-3 \u590d\u73b0\u5230 FVU=0.0579389\uff0c\u4f18\u4e8e 3.0e-3 baseline \u7684 0.0581065\uff0c\u4e14\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u4ec5 264s\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u8fd9\u6b21\u6539\u5584\u4e0d\u518d\u4f9d\u8d56\u5f02\u5e38\u6162\u901f\u6837\u672c\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u56de\u7b54\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff1a3.3e-3 \u7684\u6536\u76ca\u662f\u5426\u8db3\u591f\u7a33\u5b9a\u5230\u53ef\u4ee5\u6b63\u5f0f\u66ff\u4ee3 3.0e-3 \u6210\u4e3a\u8be5 family \u7684 signum \u4e3b\u7ebf LR\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u518d\u505a\u4e00\u8f6e\u540c\u914d\u65b9 clean repeat\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u4e0a\u63a2\u6216\u5207 optimizer\u3002",
research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0021.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`lowrank_residual` with `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32` improved both K=64 and K=32, so the next clean stabilization move is to complete this capacity sweep at the quality anchor. Increasing only `EXPANSION_FACTOR` from 16 to 32 at K=128 may further lower FVU on the best-quality point if the residual branch is still capacity-limited there.","summary":"Run a proxy `lowrank_residual` stabilization pass at `K=128` with `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32`, keeping the rest of the winning recipe fixed (`OPTIMIZER=signum`, `LR=1.6e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`). This closes the family-specific capacity sweep across the tested K values.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"lowrank_residual","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This keeps one variable isolated and follows the strongest available stabilization signal: EF=32 has already helped at lower K, so K=128 is the remaining missing point in the same coherent sweep. The main risk is that K=128 is already saturated at EF=16 and EF=32 only increases cost, but finishing this axis is higher value than switching to aux before the capacity pattern is complete.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"32"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"HOOKPOINTS","value":"layers.[3].self_attn.o_proj"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 21 completes the `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32` stabilization sweep for `lowrank_residual` by testing the remaining anchor at K=128.","Because EF=32 already improved full frontier points at K=32 and K=64, K=128 is the highest-value missing read before moving to a different stabilization axis."],"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_residual` with `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32` improves proxy FVU at K=128, promote it to full and adopt EF=32 as the likely new family default.","If EF=32 is flat or worse at K=128, keep a mixed frontier with EF=32 for lower K and EF=16 for K=128, then test a different single stabilization axis such as `AUXK_ALPHA=0.01`.","If EF=32 improves K=128 quality but causes clear runtime or memory regression, follow with a narrow performance-oriented code pass rather than discarding the higher-capacity variant outright."],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0170.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"matched_probe","hypothesis":"Matched architecture probe on `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` with `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` fixed. Final reconstruction formula is `x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i b_i`, where `U(Vx)` is a static low-rank trunk library, `{c_m}` is a static soft-codebook library, and `{b_i}` is a static residual dictionary. This is `扩展兼容`: LUTurbo/Lottable can export it as one trunk lookup plus one codebook lookup plus one sparse residual lookup over fixed vector libraries; the online path remains finite weighted sums over static libraries. At EF=2 its encoder selection cost stays within the `≤ 1.5×h×n` hard budget and is materially lower than the current two-stage soft-codebook mainline. The single question is whether dropping the second residual refinement stage preserves enough quality and runtime efficiency to remain worth continuing as a cheaper LUTurbo-compatible branch, or whether the second stage is clearly necessary.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` is clearly worse than the two-stage mainline in both FVU and runtime metrics, close this parent branch for the current low-EF regime and return to `lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual` next round.","If it is modestly worse in FVU but materially better in throughput or total runtime, keep it as a cheaper compatible Pareto branch, but still return to the mainline next round per probe policy.","If it is unexpectedly very close to the mainline at lower selection cost, allow at most one later family-specific follow-up after the required return to the mainline."],"notes_to_memory":["Compatibility: `扩展兼容`. Export path is static trunk library + static soft-codebook library + static residual dictionary; no decoder branch depends on dynamic weights.","This round is a strict matched architecture probe: keep `K=128`, `EXPANSION_FACTOR=2`, `OPTIMIZER=signum`, and `LR=3.0e-3` explicitly pinned, and change only `ARCHITECTURE`.","Evaluate with `tokens_per_sec`, total duration, and `final_total_tokens` alongside FVU, because LUTurbo cares about total online/runtime cost rather than FVU alone; a tiny quality change with slower runtime is negative."],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"This obeys the single-variable rule by changing only `architecture` and explicitly pinning the current mainline recipe fields. After the recent asymmetric, gated, and jumprelu probes failed to pressure the mainline, the highest-value remaining matched probe is the strongest cheaper parent `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual`: it preserves the same formula class except for removing the second residual stage, stays within the EF=2 budget, and directly tests whether that extra stage is actually earning its cost in the current deployable regime. The main risk is limited novelty because this family is already known historically, but it is still the cleanest remaining architecture-worthiness question under the forced probe policy.","summary":"Run one valid matched architecture probe on `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` while keeping the `K=128`, `EF=2`, `signum`, `LR=3.0e-3` mainline recipe fixed. This cleanly tests whether the cheaper one-stage soft-codebook parent is still worth continued attention under LUTurbo-compatible low-EF constraints.","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0062.json:25:    "self_review": "This respects the Round 62 policy: one probe only, one main variable only, and the full mainline recipe stays matched except for architecture. `group_topk` is a better probe than heavier multi-branch variants because it is directly LUTurbo-compatible and has a plausible path to lower online selection cost rather than only improving training-side expressiveness.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0062.json:78:    "self_review": "This respects the Round 62 policy: one probe only, one main variable only, and the full mainline recipe stays matched except for architecture. `group_topk` is a better probe than heavier multi-branch variants because it is directly LUTurbo-compatible and has a plausible path to lower online selection cost rather than only improving training-side expressiveness.",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0185.json:17:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\uff1b\u5176\u4e2d low-rank trunk \u5e93 U\u3001\u9759\u6001 soft-codebook \u5e93 {c_m}\u3001\u4ee5\u53ca\u4e24\u9636\u6bb5 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93 {b_i} \u90fd\u53ef\u9759\u6001\u5bfc\u51fa\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u6620\u5c04\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf\u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b encoder selection_cost \u4ecd\u5728 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u5185\uff0c\u4e14\u8fde\u7eed 3 \u8f6e\u56f4\u7ed5 `NUM_CODES` \u538b\u7f29\u90fd\u6ca1\u6709\u6539\u53d8\u66f2\u7ebf\u7ec8\u70b9\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u74f6\u9888\u66f4\u53ef\u80fd\u5728\u4f18\u5316\u52a8\u6001\u800c\u4e0d\u662f coarse codebook \u5bb9\u91cf\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u56de\u7b54\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u628a\u4e3b\u53d8\u91cf\u5207\u5230 `optimizer`\uff0c\u5e76\u4f7f\u7528\u66f4\u4fdd\u5b88\u7684 `adam@1.0e-3`\uff0c\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u4e0d\u6539\u53d8 family/EF/K \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\u6539\u5584\u8bad\u7ec3\u66f2\u7ebf\u5f62\u72b6\u6216\u7ec8\u70b9 FVU\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 signum \u914d\u65b9\u5468\u56f4\u5f97\u5230\u540c\u6837\u7684 plateau\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0163.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"gated","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，alpha_i 是单样本门控后选出的稀疏系数，因此最终表示是单静态向量库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 1.0x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束，且仍低于当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x。本轮严格保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主要 recipe 不变，只将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 改为 gated，回答唯一问题：在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下，增加简单门控是否足以让单库路线更接近主线质量，还是它仍会明显落后于带 trunk、soft-codebook 和 staged refinement 的主线结构。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 gated 明显落后于当前主线，则说明简单门控单库路线在当前 regime 下不值得继续，下一轮回到主线。","若 gated 与当前主线差距小于预期且运行代价更优，则记录其为低成本直接兼容备选，但下一轮仍按要求回到主线。","若 gated 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 的系统级收益需要重新审视，但本轮仅做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["gated 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为直接兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","r159-r162 已覆盖 lowrank_soft_codebook_residual、lowrank_residual、factorized_topk、topk；本轮补充 gated 这一剩余可行直接兼容低成本路线。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把质量差异与吞吐波动混淆。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 gated 是因为它是当前尚未在这一严格 matched 配方下补齐的可行直接兼容单库对照，能回答简单门控是否足以弥补纯 topk 路线表达不足这一剩余问题。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为 gated，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断这种简单门控的直接兼容单库架构是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
