research/history_archive/12_20260323_013532/logs/agent_action_0012.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`multi_branch_gated` produced the strongest new non-winning proxy signal since `two_stage_residual`, so the next informative move is a family-specific stabilization pass rather than pivoting away immediately. Increasing `EXPANSION_FACTOR` from 16 to 32 at K=128 tests whether the multi-branch gated encoder is capacity-limited under the current strong signum recipe and can close more of the remaining quality gap without changing architecture or optimization.","summary":"Run a `multi_branch_gated` proxy stabilization pass at K=128 with `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32`, keeping the current signum/aux-free recipe fixed and changing only expansion factor.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"quality_improve","family_name":"multi_branch_gated","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows the new family after a genuinely competitive prototype result and changes only one generic variable on the same architecture. Risk: the prototype may not be width-limited and EF=32 may regress or add cost, but this is the cleanest first stabilization probe before considering promotion or broader family-local changes.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"multi_branch_gated"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"32"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`multi_branch_gated` prototype at K=128 reached proxy FVU 0.15793968923389912, making it a competitive incubating family worth stabilization rather than immediate discard.","This round tests whether the new family is capacity-limited by increasing only `EXPANSION_FACTOR` from 16 to 32 at the K=128 anchor."],"next_hypotheses":["If `multi_branch_gated` with `EXPANSION_FACTOR=32` improves materially, promote it to full and continue stabilizing the family.","If EF=32 is flat or worse, test a family-specific branch-allocation or branch-count parameter next rather than continuing generic width sweeps.","If quality is promising but runtime regresses materially, follow with a targeted performance-focused code pass."],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0163.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 probe family \u7684\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_i} \u662f\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u56fa\u5b9a\u5411\u91cf\uff0calpha_i \u662f\u5355\u6837\u672c\u95e8\u63a7\u540e\u9009\u51fa\u7684\u7a00\u758f\u7cfb\u6570\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u6700\u7ec8\u8868\u793a\u662f\u5355\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.0x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\uff0c\u4e14\u4ecd\u4f4e\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u7ebf lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual \u7684\u7ea6 1.25x\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u4fdd\u6301 K=128\u3001EXPANSION_FACTOR=2\u3001OPTIMIZER=signum\u3001LR=3.0e-3 \u4e0e\u4e3b\u8981 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u53ea\u5c06 architecture \u4ece lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual \u6539\u4e3a gated\uff0c\u56de\u7b54\u552f\u4e00\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e EF \u53ef\u90e8\u7f72 regime \u4e0b\uff0c\u589e\u52a0\u7b80\u5355\u95e8\u63a7\u662f\u5426\u8db3\u4ee5\u8ba9\u5355\u5e93\u8def\u7ebf\u66f4\u63a5\u8fd1\u4e3b\u7ebf\u8d28\u91cf\uff0c\u8fd8\u662f\u5b83\u4ecd\u4f1a\u660e\u663e\u843d\u540e\u4e8e\u5e26 trunk\u3001soft-codebook \u548c staged refinement \u7684\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7ed3\u6784\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0187.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j；其中 low-rank trunk 库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m}、两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都可静态导出，因此可直接映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判断为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 仍满足 ≤1.5×h×n 硬约束。r133 的 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 与 r186 的 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 都未伤害终点 FVU，说明 trunk 容量可能仍有可压缩冗余。本轮只回答一个问题：将 `TRUNK_RANK` 进一步下调到 8，是否仍能保持接近当前主线的训练曲线与终点 FVU，同时继续降低 trunk 相关的 encoder 选择成本与部署查表成本，从而把兼容 Pareto 点继续推向更低总成本。",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0125.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"96"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。其可导出为静态 trunk 向量库 U、静态 soft-codebook 库 {c_m} 与静态 residual 字典库 {b_i} 上的有限加权和，因此可映射到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的‘查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿’推理链路，兼容性为扩展兼容。当前 family 在 EF=2 下 selection_cost 约为 1.16x 到 1.25x，满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。r124 表明 adam@3.0e-3 在该主线下直接爆炸，optimizer 轴已给出明确负面信号，因此本轮只回答一个问题：在恢复稳定主线 signum@3.0e-3 后，K=96 相对 K=128 的更低部署查表成本是否值得以少量 FVU 退化换取更好的系统性价比与训练耗时。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 K=96 曲线与最终 FVU 基本复现 r120，则可将 96 作为低 deploy 成本保守前沿点并暂停继续扫 K。","若 K=96 本轮明显优于 r120，则说明先前结果可能受随机性影响，可继续在 K 轴补中间点如 112。","若 K=96 仍显著差于 K=128 且时间收益有限，则回到 K=128 signum 主线，后续考虑 loss/preprocess 而不是继续降 K。"],"notes_to_memory":["family 不变，兼容性仍为扩展兼容，导出路径不变：trunk 库 + soft-codebook 库 + residual 字典库。","adam@3.0e-3 在 r124 爆炸，optimizer 轴暂时停止，恢复 signum 作为稳定主线。","本轮改 K 是因为 signum LR 轴和 optimizer 轴都已基本给出信号，且当前策略明确要求同时考虑 deploy 成本与训练耗时。","评估时必须同时比较 FVU、总耗时、tokens_per_sec、final_total_tokens，判断 K=96 的时间收益是否真实。"],"primary_variable":"k","self_review":"本轮只改 K，遵守单变量原则，并且在 optimizer 轴出现明确负面信号后转向更贴近 LUTurbo 总成本目标的 deploy 维度。缺点是 K 轴优先级低于 loss/preprocess，但当前已有两个现成 frontier 点可直接比较，信息回报更高且更接近系统目标。","summary":"停止继续追 adam，恢复稳定主线 signum，并测试更低 deploy 成本的 K=96 是否在可接受的 FVU 损失下带来更好的 LUTurbo 系统性价比。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0016.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"JumpReLU at K=128 appears limited more by encoder capacity than by auxk tuning, so increasing expansion_factor from 8 to 16 while holding the improved LR=1.6e-3 and AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125 fixed may reduce proxy FVU below the current JumpReLU proxy anchor.","summary":"Keep the best K=128 JumpReLU quality anchor fixed and begin the expansion-factor sweep with EXPANSION_FACTOR=16, since the recent auxk sweep underperformed and capacity is the next clean one-parameter probe.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"lower_fvu","family_name":"jumprelu","family_stage":"stabilize","self_review":"This follows the runtime exploitation guidance and changes exactly one primary variable after two auxk reductions both degraded proxy quality. The main risk is extra capacity may not help at fixed optimization settings, but EF=16 is the most justified next test before broader architecture changes.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"jumprelu"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_INIT_THRESHOLD","value":"0.15"},{"key":"JUMPRELU_BANDWIDTH","value":"0.1"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Rounds 14-15 showed AUXK_ALPHA=0 and 0.01 both worsening proxy FVU versus the K=128 JumpReLU anchor, so auxk reduction is not the near-term path to lower FVU.","This round shifts the single-variable sweep from regularization to capacity by testing EXPANSION_FACTOR=16 at the established K=128 JumpReLU baseline.","If EF=16 improves proxy quality without a major throughput drop, promote to full before considering smaller K or cost-focused follow-ups."],"next_hypotheses":["If EXPANSION_FACTOR=16 improves proxy FVU, promote to full and then decide whether to stabilize EF further or tune LR on the higher-capacity model.","If EXPANSION_FACTOR=16 is worse or neutral, test EXPANSION_FACTOR=4 to map whether the current EF=8 is already near-optimal.","If both EF=16 and EF=4 fail, conclude local JumpReLU capacity sweeps are exhausted and return to architecture exploration or a fresh optimizer-level change."],"primary_variable":"expansion_factor"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0154.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + \u03a3_j alpha_j^(2) b_j\u3002\u5176\u4e2d U(Vx) \u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{c_m} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 soft-codebook \u5e93\uff0c{b_i} \u4e3a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b57\u5178\u5e93\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u6700\u7ec8\u4ecd\u662f\u591a\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201c\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff1b\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u8be5 family \u5728 EF=2 \u4e0b encoder selection_cost \u7ea6 1.25x h\u00d7n\uff0c\u6ee1\u8db3 \u22641.5x \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002r153 \u5df2\u7528 clean baseline \u91cd\u65b0\u786e\u8ba4\u4e3b\u7ebf\u53c2\u8003\u914d\u65b9\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u8fd0\u884c\u73af\u5883\u4e0b\u80fd\u7a33\u5b9a\u56de\u5230 FVU\u22480.058106 \u4e14\u603b\u8017\u65f6\u964d\u56de 294s\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u8fd1\u671f\u6162\u901f\u6837\u672c\u66f4\u50cf\u541e\u5410\u6ce2\u52a8\u800c\u975e family \u9000\u5316\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u56de\u7b54\u4e00\u4e2a\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5728\u4e3b\u7ebf family\u3001K\u3001EF\u3001optimizer \u4e0e\u5bfc\u51fa\u5f62\u5f0f\u4e0d\u53d8\u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a LR \u4ece 3.0e-3 \u4e0a\u8c03\u5230\u6b64\u524d\u4e24\u6b21\u51fa\u73b0\u66f4\u4f4e\u7ec8\u70b9\u7684 3.3e-3\uff0c\u80fd\u5426\u5728\u6b63\u5e38\u541e\u5410\u533a\u95f4\u5185\u7a33\u5b9a\u590d\u73b0\u66f4\u597d\u7684\u4e2d\u540e\u6bb5\u6536\u655b\u4e0e\u66f4\u4f4e FVU\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u4ec5\u4ec5\u4f9d\u8d56\u5f02\u5e38\u6162\u901f\u8fd0\u884c\u3002",
