research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0115.json:52:      "EF=2 \u5df2\u6ee1\u8db3\u9009\u62e9\u6210\u672c\u786c\u7ea6\u675f\uff0c\u5f53\u524d frontier \u53ef\u884c\u70b9\u4e3a cost\u22481.25x\u3001FVU\u22480.05811\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0130.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"stability_signal","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = U(Vx) + Σ_m pi_m c_m + Σ_i alpha_i^(1) b_i + Σ_j alpha_j^(2) b_j。这里 low-rank trunk 的基向量库 U、soft codebook 库 {c_m}、以及两阶段 residual 字典库 {b_i} 都是静态可导出的，因此可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为扩展兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 时 selection_cost 约 1.25x h×n，满足 ≤1.5x 的硬约束。本轮只回答一个问题：在最近训练耗时波动上升且 LR=2.4e-3 已经验证无收益后，参考配方 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, EF=2, K=128, OPTIMIZER=signum, LR=3.0e-3 是否仍然稳定复现当前 feasible frontier，并给出干净的 tokens_per_sec、总耗时、final_total_tokens 参照点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 clean baseline 复现 fvu≈0.0581 且吞吐恢复正常，则说明最近退化主要来自 recipe 变更，下一轮主变量切到 optimizer 并联动 LR。","若 clean baseline 本身吞吐继续变慢或结果漂移，则优先调查训练链路/数据窗口的运行时漂移，而不是继续做 recipe 搜索。","若 clean baseline 复现稳定但仍无改进空间，再在同 family/EF=2/K=128 上测试 optimizer=adam 并配套较小 LR。"],"notes_to_memory":["LUTurbo 导出形式未变：trunk + codebook + two-stage residual 仍是静态向量库上的有限加权和，family 维持扩展兼容。","EF=2 的 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 仍在选择成本预算内；本轮不改 K，避免把部署查表成本混入运行时复验。","r129 已表明将 LR 从 3.0e-3 下调到 2.4e-3 不能改善该主线，因此按优先顺序回补 clean baseline。"],"primary_variable":"clean_baseline","self_review":"遵守单变量原则，没有新开 family，也没有同时改 optimizer/LR/K。该动作不是为了直接刷新 FVU，而是为后续 recipe 决策重新建立可信吞吐和收敛基线，符合当前“主线推进但先看运行代价”的要求。","summary":"回到当前主线参考配方做一次 clean baseline 复验：固定 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual, EF=2, K=128, signum, LR=3.0e-3，不引入新结构或新 recipe，只确认当前 feasible 主线的 FVU、训练曲线与 tokens_per_sec/总耗时是否稳定可复现。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0235.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family: codebook_topk\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_m \u03c0_m c_m + \u03a3_i \u03b1_i b_i\uff1b\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u5b9e\u73b0\u91cc\u524d\u5411\u4e3b\u8def\u5f84\u7b49\u4ef7\u4e8e x_hat = c_m* + \u03a3_i \u03b1_i b_i\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {c_m} \u662f\u9759\u6001 coarse codebook\uff0c{b_i} \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u65f6\uff0c\u53ef\u5b9e\u73b0\u4e3a\u4e00\u6b21 coarse \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u4e00\u6b21 residual \u7a00\u758f\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\uff0c\u6700\u7ec8\u4ecd\u662f\u591a\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 reference_round=r233 \u53ea\u6539\u4e00\u4e2a env \u53c2\u6570 `ARCHITECTURE=codebook_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=signum`\u3001`LR=0.003`\u3001`AUXK_ALPHA=0.03125` \u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u914d\u7f6e\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001 coarse codebook + \u5c0f K residual\u201d\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u7ea6 0.38x \u603b\u6210\u672c\u5904\uff0c\u663e\u8457\u4f18\u4e8e\u540c\u6210\u672c plain topk \u7684 FVU\uff0c\u5e76\u6bd4\u6700\u8fd1\u5df2\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u7684 factorized/grouped/JumpReLU \u5c0f\u4fee\u7ebf\u66f4\u6709\u7ed3\u6784\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u3002\u9009\u62e9\u8fd9\u4e00\u6b65\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6cbf JumpReLU bandwidth \u5fae\u8c03\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a r234 \u867d\u628a FVU \u538b\u5230 0.14545\uff0c\u4f46\u603b\u65f6\u957f\u66b4\u6da8\u5230 899s\uff0c\u5df2\u6784\u6210\u660e\u786e\u8d1f\u9762\u7cfb\u7edf\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1b\u800c `codebook_topk@EF1,K32` \u6839\u636e\u672c\u5730 `selection_cost_estimate()` \u7ea6\u4e3a sel=0.28x\u3001deploy=0.09x\u3001total=0.38x\uff0c\u6b63\u843d\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u6218\u533a\u95f4\u3002",
