research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/logs/agent_action_0042.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"After multiple rounds dominated by gated-local tuning and unresolved crash recovery, the most informative next move is to advance an already-incubating alternate family rather than spend another round near the current gated anchor. A clean `topk` K=128 proxy run under the current strongest gated training regime tests whether simpler support selection benefits more from the improved optimizer and regularization settings than it did in earlier comparisons.","summary":"Run a fresh `topk` K=128 proxy mainline comparison using the current strongest signum gated regime to see whether the improved training setup materially closes the quality gap for the incubating top-k family.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"proxy","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"topk","family_stage":"mainline_comparison","self_review":"This is a better use of the round than another gated-adjacent parameter tweak because the search has gone too long without advancing a distinct family, and `topk` already has working runs that can cleanly absorb the stronger regime. The main risk is that top-k remains well behind gated on FVU, but that negative result is still useful because it would retire a lingering incumbent alternative and narrow future exploration toward more novel architectures.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"16"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"1.6e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.01"},{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["The search has now gone eight rounds without advancing a new family, so architecture exploration should take priority over more local gated tuning.","`topk` remains incubating with older K=128 proxy evidence taken under weaker regimes, so it deserves one clean comparison against the current strongest training setup before being retired or promoted.","This round keeps the regime fixed to the current gated anchor settings and changes only architecture, giving a direct read on whether simpler global top-k selection benefits from the newer training recipe."],"next_hypotheses":["If `topk` improves materially over its prior proxy results and is competitive with gated at K=128, promote it to full and begin family-specific stabilization from this stronger anchor.","If `topk` runs normally but remains clearly worse than gated, retire it from near-term focus and move to a more expressive new architecture family.","If `topk` is still worse on FVU but shows meaningfully better runtime or memory behavior, keep it alive as a cost-quality tradeoff family rather than a main quality contender."],"primary_variable":"architecture"}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/logs/agent_action_0161.json:1:{"change_type":"architecture","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"factorized_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"2"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.0e-3"}],"expected_win":"information_gain","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"factorized_topk","family_stage":"probe","hypothesis":"候选 probe family 的最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_i alpha_i b_i，其中 {b_i} 是单个静态字典库上的固定向量，alpha_i 是单样本稀疏系数，因此最终表示是单库上的有限加权和，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路；兼容性判断为直接兼容。该 family 在 EF=2 下 encoder selection_cost 约 0.38x h×n，显著低于当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 的约 1.25x，且满足 ≤1.5x 硬约束。本轮严格保持 K=128、EXPANSION_FACTOR=2、OPTIMIZER=signum、LR=3.0e-3 与主要 recipe 不变，只将 architecture 从 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 改为 factorized_topk，回答唯一问题：这种更激进的低秩单库选择机制在当前低 EF 可部署 regime 下是否仍值得继续，还是其表示能力会明显落后于保留 trunk + codebook + staged refinement 的主线结构。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["若 factorized_topk 明显落后于当前主线，则说明极低选择成本单库路线在当前 regime 下不值得继续，下一轮回到主线。","若 factorized_topk 与当前主线差距小于预期且运行代价更优，则记录其为更激进低成本备选，但下一轮仍按要求回到主线。","若 factorized_topk 意外优于当前主线，则说明当前主线 family 的系统级成本收益需要重新审视，但本轮仅做架构价值判断，不连续展开新 family。"],"notes_to_memory":["factorized_topk 满足 LUTurbo 导出契约，兼容性为直接兼容。","本轮严格是 matched architecture probe：EF、K、optimizer、LR 与主要 recipe 全部固定，只改 architecture。","r159-r160 已说明去掉 second stage 和去掉 soft-codebook coarse branch 都会明显恶化；本轮补充检验更低成本的直接兼容单库路线是否还有继续价值。","评估时必须同时检查 FVU、tokens_per_sec、总耗时和 final_total_tokens，避免把更低成本或更差质量误判为吞吐波动。"],"primary_variable":"architecture","self_review":"这轮遵守架构探针规则，只改一个主变量 architecture，并保持主线的 K、EF、optimizer、LR 不变。选择 factorized_topk 而不是再次重复已测过的 topk/lowrank 父节点，是为了用一次更低 selection_cost 的直接兼容 probe 回答当前剩余的关键问题：极低成本单库路线是否还有继续价值。","summary":"插入一个严格匹配的架构探针：将当前主线 lowrank_two_stage_soft_codebook_residual 替换为 factorized_topk，其余 K=128、EF=2、signum、LR=3.0e-3 全部保持不变，用一轮干净对照判断这种更低成本的直接兼容单库架构是否值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0192.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 probe family \u7684\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = U(Vx) + \u03a3_m pi_m c_m + \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i\uff1b\u5176\u4e2d low-rank trunk \u9879 U(Vx) \u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0csoft codebook \u5206\u652f \u03a3_m pi_m c_m \u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 codebook \u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0cresidual \u5206\u652f \u03a3_i alpha_i b_i \u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u9759\u6001 residual \u5b57\u5178\u4e0a\u7684\u7a00\u758f\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u80fd\u591f\u6620\u5c04\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u2018\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u2019\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 K=128\u3001EXPANSION_FACTOR=2\u3001OPTIMIZER=signum\u3001LR=3.0e-3 \u5b8c\u5168 matched \u7684\u6761\u4ef6\u4e0b\uff0clowrank_soft_codebook_residual \u4ee5\u66f4\u4f4e encoder selection cost\uff08frontier \u5df2\u663e\u793a\u7ea6 0.75x vs \u4e3b\u7ebf 1.25x\uff09\u6709\u671b\u63d0\u4f9b\u503c\u5f97\u4fdd\u7559\u7684 cost/FVU \u70b9\uff1b\u82e5\u5176 FVU \u660e\u663e\u843d\u540e\uff0c\u5219\u8bf4\u660e two-stage refinement \u672c\u8eab\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u4fdd\u7559\u3002",
research/history_archive/16_20260328_220351/round_summaries/round_0192.json:22:    "expected_win": "lower_cost",
