research/history_archive/11_20260322_021455/round_summaries/round_0060.json:91:    "summary": "Run a gated proxy comparison at `K=64` with the recovered `AUXK_ALPHA=0`, EF=16, signum, LR=1.6e-3 recipe to test whether the stable aux-free regime improves the lower-cost frontier.",
